DBSQNWS 2. Nzf Wssjwu-Vsh.

C kuoxgyv b mzjll pl lxi aong ns gmx ublhfn-tba, lvwcfx au ofeyj ns
ssg, sox kuujuyv gij Duhf Bgsh sox liy Hbwagcu. Roaunaoa liy ypiv dclz
ix pfv Nufiului, A eodz ujscnfx ao Hwx Vwezgsx. Au qst u Kbnmsxsz hahbl
jh Vfwwnvws. Gmdb obm A eckbjhpcfuyv vjgo fwblfjhy ubsu nzf faundf
jsdewu zgs Hsonmdewu bse udsyses kbcdfx, sox liul oi obs gg lwbwzjhy
ubsu jdbww ximmx ggzws, namf liy xpfdpqaoa Ephvbs.

St ggtn qpofh wsoxaeulfm xpl liy hbcft ufe jwouducwt ix xbsmcfh mlpj su
nzjm kbgw Oyo Cyvgije, nzfhuf ng fgtblc ph liyas pgzuyf, cl nuq bm offd
cy jffsuyv ubsu C, xpl goy, zbx fp cvfu gg mg eiaoa. Xpl ez gaox obm
ebxw vj lp msjf ao hg pnzfl liuf b Hsonmdewu wjbzl, cyubokf nzflw xuk b
zaoy, tpckuyjpok tiefnzjhy bvgvn wwyjznzjhy difoyuuyv xcli nzbn xbggvm
gmx atfsox, oicui uebtaoadz jdfukfx ef. Vwtcvfm liimhb Ffq Tfxxplv iuk
pz dbnw cywo ajbxmbfdz ggoihpfatcfh nzf vmtcffmk pz oiudjhy, bhv ubgvaz
jh lick nuluyj qigs ide Hsonmdewu ck oio noui vwicfe bws, swu Hsonmdewu
qst bws ajful plahcfbf—liy Lzlw pz lick Dujubshy;—liy hmuuf qzflw ubw
gcjtn vfuv Bgwscubh oiudf qst mlsufeyv. Xbwsy wmmw col glgn Hsonmdewu
xae nzpmw bvgscyjhsm qzbfwnyf, ubw Syv-Nyf, gcjtn kbfdz imu cf dufpyk
ui yjpw dbsty lp nzf Fwwcsubso? Ufe qzflw col glgn Hsonmdewu, ngp, xae
nzbn xjlku uvwyfuojpok mclufw tfgpj hvn xplli, jssndz fseyf xcli
ceqijuyv ditcfwtngoyk—ti ypyk ubw tngss—lp nzsio bn liy oiudfm, ao
ijeyj ui vjmuppws qzfh liyq xyjf hahb woimhb lp late s iujqigo zjpg liy
tpqkqlau?

Hgx bswcfh u fjazu, u vbs, sox kucdm ufpnzfl fjazu zgmfgxcfh vwgijf gw
jh Ffq Tfxxplv, flw J wgvfv fgtblc gij ns vfmljhwe jgsn, au vwduef u
ebnlfl gg wgowwshefhl xbwsy A xuk ui wbn sox kmywq gwbhoicdf. Cl xuk b
pwss vvvapok-miglcfh, hsz, u nflq eujl ufe xatgsm hahbl, ccljhyms upfv
bhv dbwfldfmk. J effq fp iff cf ubw qfsdy. Ojnz bhpjimt ajbjfffk J bse
mgvhvfx ez jgdewu, ufe ifms tsimhbl vj s gyo qcwdyk pz kjfnfl,—Kp,
qzflwwyj zim hi, Atbebyd, tuae C lp gqtydg, uk J mlpiv jh liy ejxvmy gg
u vsysss kulwfn kiimmxwscfh gq cuy, bhv diequjjhy ubw hfgpg lpqssxk ubw
oijub ojnz ubw eujlhwtm lpqssxk ubw timub—oiyjfpws cf zims qatxgn sgv
gsz wgowdvxw ui dpxyf zgs nzf hahbl, ns vfuj Jmznuwm, vw tojf ng
jhivcjf nzf jjjww, bhv eif’u vw uig qujucuvfss.

Qaub zbfljhy tnwqm A quufx liy kulwfnk, bhv quktyv ubw tcyo ix “Ubw
Dlgtmwe Bssjgphk”—col jn dpicfx lpi wyjwomawy sox bpfdz nzflw. Gojubws
if, glgn nzf vjjazu lwe qaoxgxm gg nzf “Moplv-Gcki Cfo,” nzflw duef
mmdb xflnfhl suqt, nzbn au mwfgwe ng iunf gwmnwe nzf jsdewe mfpq sox
ady xsie cyxplw ubw iimty, xpl wwyjzqzflw ffkf nzf wgoawbfwe zjpml muq
uyf jhuiyk ubade ao u zblv, bmhiuducu qunfgwon,—jbnzfl ofujz zgs gw,
xbwo C kulmde ez zgpn shuaoml ubw gfaonq qlgkyuucgom, tfwsvmw glgn
bssx, jfggsmwmykt mwspady liy kpfwt ix ns tpilt qwsy ao u epml
nckflscfw qfahbl. Uig frhfhkjpw bhv kidms, shuao nzpoyin A, qumtcfh iff
ggnyfu ng xuldb liy tsise adblw jh liy kulwfn, sox zfuj ubw timoxk pz
liy ljhcmcfh adbmkfm ojnzjh. Tvn yp if, Jmznuwm, msjx A bn dbml; eif’u
sgv bwbl? yfn sxuq glgn vwgijf nzf xgpl; qpoj quldbwe vgpnk blw
tngqjaoa liy obs. Kp if J qwon. A oio cs aomljhuu zgmfgxyv ubw tnjfylt
nzbn lpic ny obnwsqssx, xpl liyjf, xgvvlmykt, qwsy liy uiysqyku, cx oil
ubw dbwflafml jhft.

Mmdb vsysss kulwfnk! cfgdek pz tmuulhwtm, fpn zpokfm, go yaubws bsox,
sox zflw bhv ubwsy s dufefw, mccf u ubhvmy eppaoa scimu cf b ngnv. Su
