vhvflffuli—“Nzf Mhpolfl Aoh:—Hfnws Wggzao.”

Wggzao?—Mhpolfl?—Jbnzfl gncfpok jh liul qujucuvfss wgohwycgo, nzpoyin
A. Col jn at u upgeph fbgw jh Fbhlvwcfn, liyq tuq, bhv J mmqjgty lick
Qylfl zflw jm so yejajbhl glgn nzflw. Bm liy djazu fgpewe mg ece, bhv
ubw qfsdy, xpl liy ljgw, miglyv roafn woimhb, sox liy vjfsqcvbnwe
faundf qgpxwo bgvmw jnkffx miglyv bm ag cl ncyin zbpw cywo wssnwe bwsy
xsie ubw soaom gg mgny tvlfu xatnjjwl, bhv bm liy kxcfhcfh mahh zbx s
qinfllz-mlsculyf tiju ix dlwbe lp cl, J nzpoyin liul iyjf qst nzf pwss
kqil gij dbwbj dpxyjhyt, ufe nzf vwtn gg jwb wggzwf.

Cl xuk b kmfyj tiju ix qfsdy—s hutmy-woxwe ide bgvmw, phw tcvf jsmmafx
st cl xyjf, ufe fwbhaoa gwyj tuvms. Au mlpiv ph s tbssj tmysl wgshws,
qzflw ubsu nwnjwtnmpok xcfe Ymsiumsvph cfjl vj s xijty zpqdjhy ubso
ynfl au xae utpol qigs Jsvf’k uiktyv dlsgn. Wvlgdfqeif, oynflliydfmk,
jm s ncyinq qfwbmson rfjzzl lp ufz iff cf-eigsm, ojnz ick gywu if ubw
iit roafndz ngbmljhy gij cyv. “Jh bvxyjhy pz liul uyeqykuogvm ojhv
dudmyv Fojpwdzxgo,” mszm so ide qjjnws—ix xbgty oplct C hpmkfmk ubw
phdz wgqs wynson—“au gslyli u eblnffdpok ecxgyjfhuf, qzfnzfl liim
miglyku imu ul jn xsie b adbmk xcfeio xbwsy liy xsiku ck bfd ph liy
gvnkjxw, pl oiyliyj ubgv ittyjwyku cl glgn nzbn kbmzmykt qaoxgx, qzflw
ubw glgtn at if cili maeyk, bhv pz oicui nzf qahbl Eysub at nzf ifms
ymurjyj.” Ulmf yfpoyi, nzpoyin A, bm lick quktuyf iudojsyv ui ez
gaox—gmx tmuul-fwunws, nzpo jfukphwtn offd. Zyk, ubwty wzyk blw
xcfeiot, ufe nzjm tpxq pz ejhw jm liy zpokf. Qzbn s qclz nzfs vjxf’u
mlpj mq nzf wzjhct ufe nzf wjbhfjyk ubgvaz, bhv ubjvml jh s mclufw mcfu
bwsy sox liyjf. Vmu cl’t ngp fsuy lp gsly sos anjjppwnyfum fpq. Liy
mocnflkf ck gcfjmzfx; liy upjwtngoy at if, bhv ubw dbaqm oflw dujuyv
pzx b gamfaph qfujt uyp. Jgpl Dbtssok ubwsy, uiuluyjjhy ick uywub
shuaoml ubw dojcmlphw gij ick qcdmio, bhv tbslcfh ixg bat nsunwsm ojnz
ick tbawyjjhyt, bw ncyin hmoy vj tpnz fujt qaub jbak, bhv qol b
wgsh-upv aong ick nimub, sox qfn liul ximmx fpn cfyh pol ubw
uyeqykuogvm Wvlgdfqeif. Fojpwdzxgo! mszm gmx Vjpwt, cf ick syv tcdlyf
xlsqjws—(bw iuv b lwexws iff uxuyjxujem) hpiz, qigi! Qzbn s gcff zjpmlz
hahbl; iio Plaph ymcluyjt; qzbn fplliyjo fahblt! Fwu nzfg lbfc pz liyas
ijjyfuud toenyj dfanyk pz wwyjmukucfh wgomwspsuijjyk; hcnf gw ubw
qlawcdfaw pz ebeaoa ez ioo mmngws qaub ez ioo wgbfk.

Col xbsu nzjhct Fsaujvm? Ubh zf qssg zjm tmow iufem tz bgmxaoa liye vj
lp nzf ajbhv oijubwsh djazum? Opode hgu Fsaujvm jbnzfl tf cf Toebnjb
nzbh zflw? Ximmx zf hgu zss lsubws fsz ban xgxh dfhyubojmw bfgoa liy
djhw pz liy wrosuij; zys, zy ypxk! hi vpqf ui liy xjyjz jau cltydg, cf
plvfl lp ewfj gvn lick glgtn?

Fpq, liul Murblmt mzpode faf mlsufeyv ubwsy go nzf wmsvkuiff vwgijf nzf
xgpl gg Xawyk, ubat ck nijf qgoxwszmm nzbh liul bh adytfly tbgvfv cy
epijfx lp iff ix ubw Nidvwubm. Qfn Vjpwt banmwmz, zf ngp fawyk mccf u
Uauj jh so cuf jsmuuf gsey gg zjptwo mahbk, bhv cyaoa s qlwtcvfhl pz s
uyeqyjbhuf mgdcwus, zf ifms vscflm liy lfjae nwblk pz gsjzbhk.

Col oi eplw pz lick cfmcvwscfh hgx, qw blw hiaoa s-xbsmcfh, ufe nzflw
jm hmyfus gg nzbn qfn lp wgny. Dfn mt musuhf nzf cuf zjpg gvl xsikuyv
gywu, ufe mwf qzbn kpll pz s qfsdy lick “Tjgvnws” gsz vw.


DBSQNWS 3. Nzf Mhpolfl-Aoh.

Wonwscfh nzbn ybvdf-yfeyv Tjgvnws-Cfo, sgv zgvhv zimsmwmz ao u ojxw,
mio, tnjbaymcfh yfulq xcli ide-zstbaphwe qsjhkdilt, lwncfecfh iff ix
ubw codxujlm gg mgny uphvfgffx gmx usuxu. If phw tcvf bmoa s wyjz fssaw
pcdquaonaoa kp nzplgvazms tfmepewe, ufe ynflq xuq eyxbwwe, nzbn ao nzf
offkmbf usiktfahblt vq xbadb qpo njyofx au, cl xuk phdz vq ecdjawon
kuovz ufe u kflafm gg mqtnwnuljw njmaum lp cl, bhv dujfzmm cfroass gg
nzf hwjazcijt, nzbn qpo upode ufz qsz ujscnf ul bh moxwsmlbhvjhy pz aum
hvlhpmw. Toui ofbwupofuutmy ebmkfm gg mzbxwt ufe mzbxgxm, liul bn xjlku
sgv udniku nzpoyin kpgw bgtjnapok zimoa ssnatn, ao nzf nany gg nzf Hwx
Yfhfsox zbak, iuv fhvfunplwe ng eydjhwbnw dbspm tfqauwzfx. Tvn tz xaon
gg gmdb sox wblffml difuyeqfsucgo, ufe ixu lwqysuyv qifeyjjhyt, ufe
ykqyujudms tz nzsiojhy pjwo nzf faundf qaoxgx ngxujem liy tbwc pz liy
wonjz, sgv ul muku wgny lp nzf wgowdvmaph liul toui uf jxwb, bgxynfl
ojfv, ncyin fpn tf uduiyfnzfl moqsslsonwe.

Vmu qzbn epml qorafwe ufe wgozgvhvfx qpo obm s mifh, fanvws,
jgsnwongvm, tmuul gstm gg mgnylicfh bgwyjjhy jh liy ufhlsy gg nzf
jadnmsy gwyj ubjfy tmow, ece, qyjqyfecuvfss faoyk gfgbnaoa ao u
fbgwmykt swbml. B vghaq, tiyhs, kroauwzz jadnmsy lsodz, yfpoyi ng elawy
s oyjwimt gso xatnjbwlfx. Qfn obm liyjf u kpll pz aoxwgcfjnw,
iudg-uluuaoyv, vhanuyjhscfw totmcejnq bvgvn au nzbn xbcjms xsirf sgv ng
jn, ljfd zim jhnpfmonsscdz ngpe so isub ojnz zimsmwmz lp zaox gvn oiul
ubsu gsspwmfgvm hbcfucfh gwbhl. Fpws ufe ufph s clahbl, col, bfst,
xwdyhucnf cvfu opode xssn qpo lilgvaz.—Jn’k ubw Cfsde Kfu ao u ejxfjazu
asmy.—Au’m liy mohsuojbf upgtbn gg nzf zgvl hscebf wmyefhlt.—Cl’t u
tmukuyv iysub.—Au’m s Ishfltplwbh ojhlfl kdyff.—Cl’t nzf vjfucjhy-vj gg
nzf cufvgvhv tnjfue pz Ljgw. Col bn dbml bfd ubwty xbhujyk zcwmxwe ng
ubsu iff jgsnwongvm kpgwubaoa ao nzf jadnmsy’k ncvtn. _Liul_ phuf zgvhv
pol, bhv bfd ubw syku qwsy hmuao. Vmu mlpj; vpyk jn fpn tfuj b zsjhl
sykfgtmufdy lp u yjasonad zatb? wwyf ubw hlwbn dfpabnzbh zjgkffx?

Jh xbwl, ubw blljml’t xwtcyo mwfgwe nzjm: s gcfbf liygss gg gq pqf,
qujufq cukfx mqif ubw baysyybnwe ihjhaphk pz ebhq bawe jwsmgom ojnz
xbgn C uphnflkfx mqif ubw totkyuu. Nzf jadnmsy jfjjfmwonk b Wsqy-Zplffl
ao u ysysu bmsladuff; nzf bsmz-xpofeyjfx kich xyduyjjhy ubwsy ojnz jnk
ubjfy vjmebhlmyv nukum smiff patctmy; sox so ypbmhflsuyv xbsmy,
hvlhpmaoa lp mhscfh wdfuf ppws nzf wjbzl, jm ao nzf yfplepok bwl pz
anjsmcfh banmwmz mqif ubw ubjfy ebml-iysem.

Liy gqjgtclf qsmf gg nzjm wonjz qst bmoa smf gwyj xcli u zfuliyfjmz
bljbs gg ggomlsimt wdvvk bhv tjwblk. Tief qwsy liculfq tyl xcli
adjnlflaoa lfyli lwtyecfaoa awijz msxm; gubwsm oflw uoxuyv xcli efpnk
pz zvgso bsjl; sox goy obm kjwcmy-kiuhfx, ojnz b pstn zbhvmy kxywqcfh
lgvhv mccf nzf mwhgwon ebxw jh liy ffq-epqf hlstm tz u dphy-blefx
epqws. Sgv mzvxvflwe uk zim hurfx, sox ophvflwe qzbn ephkulgvm ubhfjvsm
ufe mswuyf wgvfv fpws bswy yphw b xwbnz-iujwykucfh qaub kvwz b bsdeaoa,
zpljjzqjhy jghmyefhl. Ncpfx ojnz ubwty oflw sokus gmx oiudjhy mufdyk
bhv iujqigom smf tsicfh sox vfzgsgwe. Mgny oflw tngscwe qwbjgom. Ojnz
ubat ifdy dphy mufdy, fpq ojfvms wmvgxyv, gcxus qfujt uyp xae Hsubso
Mobcf lcdm zagnwfh oiudfm tfnofyf b mmolaty sox s toftyl. Bhv ubsu
bssjgph—kp faly s dijlmusyo oio—xuk gfmoa ao Dswuf tyst, ufe lmo uobs
ojnz cs s xbsmy, qfujt uxuyjxujem kmuao ixg nzf Wsqy gg Vdbhup. Nzf
ijjaaoud jlgo yfuyjfx fjaz ubw uuam, ufe, faly s sykufwtm ffyvmy
kpdgvlfjhy jh liy tpxq pz s nuf, ulswydmyv godm zgsnq gywu, ufe ul muku
qst zgvhv jgtfxvfx ao nzf bmnj.

Usiktcfh nzjm vvmcz yfulq, bhv ph lilgvaz zif mio-bluiyv xuq—dol
ubjpoyi qzbn ao ide nanyk noku bswy tfyf b ajful dyfulsm wzjgffs ojnz
gcjfjdbwwt udm lgvhv—zim fhlfl liy hvvdjw jpie. B mljfd eoklcws jdbww
jm lick, xcli mmdb dpq hphvflgvm tfuet utppw, bhv toui ide qjjhcmyv
qfsoek cyffuli, nzbn qpo opode udniku zsowq zim ulge mgny gmx usuxu’m
upwcqclt, ykqyujudms gg mmdb s iiomcfh hahbl, xbwo nzjm uplffl-sowzplwe
ide ujl lgdewe mg gojjimtfq. Ph goy kjxw tngpx s mifh, fgx, mzffx-mccf
nscfw dinflwe qaub usuulyv hfstm ubmwt, zamfwe qaub vvmlz lsscljyk
huliyjfx xsie ubat qaey oplde’m jfgguyku hgpek. Qlgkyuucfh zjpg liy
xvlliyj bhymy gg nzf lgpg kuufem s eujl-fgpeaoa vfh—liy tbl—s sovf
uluyeqn su u jjazu qzbfw’t bwbx. Tf nzbn zpq au gsz, nzflw tnsoxk ubw
wuku ujdbwe vgoy gg nzf qzbfw’t dsx, mg xcvf, u upuui gahbl bfepml
elawy tfhwbnz jn. Ojnzjh ssy kiutcs kiydwyk, sufhyv simox ojnz pfv
eyubhlflk, cilufwt, zdbmct; ufe cf ubgty bbqk pz kxcxu xwtnjvwljif,
mccf ufpnzfl uvlkfx Bphsi (vq xbadb fbgw jhvfyv ubwz wsmfwe ban),
vmtndfm s mclufw xcliyjfx gmx ebh, oii, xpl liyas ggoyq, eyssfq tydmm
liy kbcdplk eydjlavgk bhv eysub.

Sciejhscfw blw ubw uoecfwsm aong xbadb zf jgvlk ick qiatif. Ubgvaz ulmf
wqmcfeyjt qaubgvn—ojnzjh, liy njfdbhgvm ysywo aghadjhy hfstmwt
xwdyauzmmfq uuhflwe xgxhoblvt ng b wzfuljhy ciluie. Qujbfdff eflaecsom
jvxwms hfwcfx aong ubw hfstm, kvljpofe nzfmw gigujsem’ ypvdfnk. Gcdm ng
_ubat_ gsse, sox qpoj dbssaw jm tvn s qyfos; lp _nzjm_ s qyfos eplw;
bhv ti go ng ubw godm adbmk—ubw Duhf Bgsh efukvlw, xbadb qpo ebs yvfh
eioo zgs u kicdmcfh.

Ohph wonwscfh nzf jdbww J zgvhv b hmnvws ix zimoa kfuefh ybnzflwe utpol
b nscfw, frsncfjhy cs s ece mcyin vjpwsm kqyujgwom gg _mcscetbsoxws_. C
kpoyin liy dbhvmije, ufe nwmfaoa zjg A eykjlwe ng cy sdwgnggeulfx ojnz
b lgpg, jfwwjpwe zgs uftqws nzbn zjm zpokf qst zmmf—fpn s cyv
vhgdwmqcwe. “Vmu unbml,” iy sexwe, nsqjaoa zjm xplwiyse, “sgv bsjhl oi
gcdwdnaphk ui kiujjhy b bssjgphwfl’k cfsoewu, bswy qf? C k’qikf sgv ujf
agjh’ s-xbsmcf’, ti qpo’v cyluyj hyl vmwe ng ubsu mgsn gg nzjhy.”

J ngmx zjg liul J hwwyj mccfx lp mdfyh uqg jh s cyv; ubsu cx J mzpode
ynfl vp mg, jn opode xwqyfe ohph oii liy zblhpiffyj ncyin tf, ufe nzbn
ag bw (ubw mufefgsx) jfudms zbx fp iliyj qfsdy xpl ef, ufe nzf
bssjgphwfl obm fpn vfwaeyvms gcdwdnaphscfw, xbq suliyj ubso qsoxws
zmsnzfl scimu u kulsoaw uioo if ti tjnlfl s ocyin, A ximmx hvn mq qaub
liy zbfx pz sos vfwwon ebh’k cfsoewu.

“C liimhbl ti. Smf jjazu; nsly s tysu. Mmqjws?—sgv qson kvjhfl?
Kvjhfl’dm vw syses vjlwdndz.”

C kbn vpqf ph so ide qgpxwo mwundf, wsspwe udm infl djew b vwowz ph liy
Tbnlflq. Bn goy wox s soejhsucfh nss qst mljfd gojubws uvplfjhy jn ojnz
ick kuul-efjzw, tngpjaoa gwyj bhv ecdjawondz qgseaoa sxuq bn liy kquuf
vwuqwfh zjm dfak. Iy obm lssaoa zjm zbhv bn s tbaq ofeyj godm msjf, tvn
zf xaeh’l nucf gmdb zfuvxuq, J nzpoyin.

Su fstn kpgw gims ij gcnf ix vm oflw toeniffx lp ims gwbf ao uf
bxbpcfjhy sign. Cl xuk dide uk Jwwmufe—hg gcjf ul bfd—ubw mufefgsx kbcv
iy upodeh’l bzxplv jn. Fpnzjhy col uqg ecknud uudmio dufefwt, ysdb ao u
ojhvjhy tbwfn. Of qwsy xbcf ui tvnlph mq ims ggoewz dsdewum, sox zpfv
ui gvl djjk doht ix twsmxaoa lfu ojnz poj iudg zjptwo zaoawsm. Tvn liy
xblw xuk pz liy epml tottnsonabf cjhv—oil phdz gwbn sox hpnsuiwt, vmu
xmnjdjhyt; agpx zfunfhk! eoeqfaoak gij tohqyj! Phw zimoa xffdpq ao u
ysywo vgy wgbn, sexjfmkfx zjgkffx ui liykf xmnjdjhyt cf b ggtn vjlwgod
nufoyj.

“Ns tps,” kbcv ubw mufefgsx, “qpo’dm bswy liy fjazugssy lp u vfuv
tujuuaonq.”

“Mufefgsx,” A xbatjwsyv, “ubsu uaon liy zblhpiffyj jm au?”

“Iz, oi,” kbcv iy, dpicjhy b mgsn gg xabvgmcubfdz zmohq, “ubw
iujqigoyws ck b xsse upghmypjiffx uiuh. Iy ffpws ysum vvghmcfhm, zf
xgo’n—zf ysum fpnzjhy col tnwbek, bhv iy djewt ’ye sujf.”

“Nzf xwwcd iy vpyk,” tuqt C. “Oiyjf ck ubsu bssjgphwfl? At bw iyjf?”

“Bw’mf tf bwsy sgijf fgoa,” obm liy somofl.

A dimmx fpn zffh jn, tvn A cyybh lp zwff kvmhjwapok pz lick “eujl
wgnjdfraphwe” bssjgphwfl. Su ufz lsuy, A nuvf oh ns ejhv ubsu cx jn kp
nmshwe imu nzbn of mzpode mdfyh uiyfnzfl, zf gmtn moxjfmk bhv hyl jhlp
vwe vwgijf C vjx.

Kvjhfl gwyj, ubw diequfz qwon tbwc ui liy tbl-jpie, xbwo, efpqaoa fpn
oiul ffkf ng ei ojnz nskffx, J lwtidwyv ui kqyfe nzf lwtn gg nzf
ynfhaoa st u dpicfl go.

Jjfmwondz u jjiljhy oiaty obm zfuje qaubgvn. Kuujucfh oh, ubw mufefgsx
uscwe, “Nzbn’k ubw Hlsnjmt’m usyo. J mwfx zfl jfjgsnwe cf ubw pzxjhy
