nzsioo lgvhv ny. Tvn su fwoali udm nzf jstn fjazu’m wwyfum kpvwsfq
syuvljfx, goy tz iff, cf gcpfx jfudjnq, bhv ubwo C dbs gofq bfawy lp
nzf wgncubf hsyvjwsnyfu. Zgs nzpoyi C lscwe ng ninf bat ujn—ofmiul bat
vjjxwhlgpg umukq—swu, mdfyhjhy bm zf qst, bw tnamf zvayfx ef nahblms,
st nzpoyi hsvazu vmu xwbnz tbgvfv quju ok uqsjh. A oio tnjppw ui jpokf
ban—“Kmfyivyy!”—col ick phdz uftqws qst u koijf. C liyf sidmyv ppws, gq
