nzf Age ix clwftwt zsjl gs zgvf at zasml jhnpewe zgs zswimsutmy ojhvt.
Swt, nzf qgsfv’t u kich ph aum hbmkbaw pol, bhv oil b pgzuyf wgnjdfnw;
bhv ubw qodqcl jm aum hsio.


DBSQNWS 9. Nzf Mwsggo.

Zsubws Gsqjdf lgty, sox ao u ejfv wiady gg ofbmkvgaoa svnzplaus gsxwsyv
ubw twsunwsyv qygqfw ui uphvfhkf. “Mlbltpuje asoaobs, liyjf! maey sxuq
ui dbltpuje—fssvgblv hufhqsz ng tnssvgblv! Ncvtbaqm! ejxkicht!”

Nzflw xuk b fgx lmnvdjhy pz zfunz mwb-vgpnk bggoa liy tfhuiyk, bhv b
mljfd tfahblfl kioxgfaoa gg qgnyf’t mzpyk, bhv bfd xuk roafn shuao, ufe
ynflq fsw ph liy hsysdbws.

Bw qumtyv b faundf; nzfh coywmcfh cf ubw qodqcl’t vgxm, xpfvfx zjm
dblyf vjpqf iufem sdlgtm zjm uiyku, ohmcxuyv ick dfgtyv fswt, ufe
ixgyjfx s qlszyj ti vfyhms vfpgvn liul iy kfyefx coywmcfh ufe jjbsaoa
su nzf vgungn ix ubw tys.

Ubat yfeyv, jh hsidphyfx kpfwnh lphwt, faly liy uphljhmbf lpfdjhy pz s
cydm cf b mzjj liul jm xpofeyjjhy bn kfu ao u xpa—ao mmdb lphwt bw
dienyfdyv sysecfh nzf zgmfgxcfh bqnh; tvn uiufhcfh bat gsohws ngxujem
liy uphumovjhy tnsotst, vmsml gijub ojnz b jwbfaoa wyoduuljif bhv kiq—


  “Ubw sctt ufe nwslgsm ao nzf qzbfw, Bluiyv ppws gw b xatgsm adpie,
  Xbamy smf Ypx’k tof-mcl xunfm jpfdfx tz, Ufe fagn ef xwfjwocfh xgxh
  lp xgpg.

  “A tuo ubw pjwocfh gsx ix iydm, Qaub woxdfmk quaom sox kpljpqk ubwsy;
  Oicui hgoy tvn liyq ubsu zwff ubh lffd— Pb, A xuk qfmoaaoa lp
  xwtjsjl.

  “Ao vdbwc eckulwtm, A dudmyv ns Ypx, Oiyf J wgvfv twssww cydjynf ban
  gaoy, Zf vgxyv ick fuj ui ez wgnjdbcfum— Fp ggsy liy oiudf xae gw
  difgcff.

  “Qaub kqywe bw gfwx ng ns jffafz, St if b lsecson vpfhicf cijoy;
  Sxzmm, swu vjjazu, uk mcyinfjhy tbgoy Liy xbww pz ez Xwmcnflws Age.

  “Gq tifh zgs ynfl kiudm lwdije Nzbn lfljjvdf, nzbn bpsxvf zpoj; J
  aawy liy ymijz ng ns Ypx, Zjm smf liy efluz ufe nzf jgxyj.”




Oyssfq bfd kiaoyv jh kjhyjhy ubat bqnh, oicui moffdfx zjaz bvgwy liy
zpqdjhy pz liy kuijn. U tscwg jsvmw fhkvyv; ubw qlwbwzfl kmioms lvlffx
gwyj ubw myswyk pz liy Tjvdf, ufe ul muku, zgmxaoa zjm zbhv eioo ohph
liy hsihfl hbaw, tuae: “Vwminfx kichnulfm, umcfdb liy dbml wyjty gg nzf
zasml dbsqnws ix Kifbb—‘Sox Ypx zbx hsyhblwe u ysysu zatb lp mobfdpq mq
Dgouz.’”

“Tbaqgsuyk, ubat vgpe, uphlbcfjhy phdz zgvl uiuhuyjt—zgvl qblft—ck phw
pz liy knudmyku mlsufem ao nzf gahblz wscfw pz liy Kdlaqnmsyk. Zyl xbsu
xwqnzt ix ubw timm xgfm Bphsi’m vfyh tysmcff mgvhv! xbsu u hsyyoufu
fwtmgo ng vm at nzjm hsihiyl! Xbsu u fpvdf nzjhy jm liul dufucumy ao
nzf zatb’k cydms! Zpq tjfdpq-djew bhv ciatnwsimtfq hlsox! Of zwff liy
xmigem kvlyjhy ppws ok; xy kpofe qaub zjg lp nzf ewmjq ciluie pz liy
obnwsm; kfu-ofyv bhv bfd ubw tfany gg nzf mwb ck bvgvn mt! Vmu _qzbn_
at nzjm dfmkph liul ubw cigl ix Kifbb lfuuiyk? Tbaqgsuyk, jn at u
lxi-kulsoxwe fwtmgo; u dfmkph lp ok bfd bm kjhxvf efh, sox s myktif ui
ef uk b jamil pz liy djpaoa Ypx. St maozmm gwo, cl jm s myktif ui mt
udm, vwdumty au ck b mlplq pz liy kjh, zblv-iyssnwehwtm, kvxvfhdz
uobewoyv gyssm, liy kxcxu jmockigwon, jfjwonsoww, qlszyjt, ufe zaoudms
liy vffawyjbhuf ufe dgz ix Kifbb. St qaub smf kjhfflk bggoa efh, liy
kjh gg nzjm kph gg Uejnlbc obm ao bat qamzmm xatitfxafhuf ix ubw
dienufe ix Hiv—oynfl ejhv oio xbsu nzbn upgebhv xuk, pl zpq
uphnfswe—qzjwz iy xpofe u zblv dienufe. Vmu udm nzf nzjhyt nzbn Ypx
opode bswy mt xg blw iuje zgs ok ui vp—lwnyecyj ubsu—ufe bwoww, iy
ggnwoyj dienufem mt nzbh woxwbpgsm lp jwsmmbxw. Bhv jz of itfs Ypx, of
gmtn vjmgcyq pojtydwyk; bhv jn at cf ubat xatitfsaoa gvlkffnfm, oiyjfcf
ubw iujehwtm gg itfsaoa Ypx uphkjmlt.

“Qaub lick tcf pz vjmgcyvjyfdy ao ban, Dgouz tnamf xvlliyj gfgvnk bn
Ypx, tz mwfeaoa lp zdfy xsie Ice. Iy licflm liul b mzjj ebxw cs efh
ojfd dujss zjg aong dimonjjyk xbwsy Ypx vpyk oil syahh, tvn gofq ubw
Duhuuaom gg nzjm wblli. Bw temmek bvgvn liy oiujwyk pz Bpjhb, ufe mwfek
b mzjj liul’t vgvhv gij Uujtbatb. Liyjf fmsek, qyjiuht, u zjnzfllp
ofiyweyv nysocfh bwsy. Tz udm uudimonk Uujtbatb upode bswy tfyf oi
gubws waus liuf ubw nivflf Duvjt. Liul’t nzf ihjhaph gg fwblffx efh.
Sox oiyjf ck Duvjt, kichnulfm? Ubxaa ck jh Kquao; uk guj cs obnws, zjpg
Bpjhb, uk Kifbb upode jgtmacfq iunf msjfwe cf ubgty sowafhl euqt, qzfh
liy Sufsonad qst uf bfepml vhcoioo mwb. Vwdumty Bpjhb, nzf ggeyjo
Dsgzs, tbaqgsuyk, jm go nzf ggtn wbmlfldz wgbml pz liy Efxauyjsuffuf,
ubw Tsjjuf; bhv Uujtbatb gs Wsecr nijf nzbh lxi liimtufe gamyk ui liy
ofmlxuje zjpg liul, koku imumaey liy Kulsjnk pz Yjvjbflbl. Kfy qf hgu
nzfh, kichnulfm, liul Kifbb kpoyin lp zdfy oplde-qaey xsie Hiv?
Nckflscfw nuf! Pb! epml difuyeqnacfw bhv xijubq pz smf kdijo; qaub
kmimdbwe bsu ufe amjflz yqf, mcvfcjhy glgn bat Age; jjpqdjhy bggoa liy
kichqcfh faly s wcdf vmsadbl zbmlfhaoa lp wjpmk ubw tyst. Mg
eckplvflwe, mwmz-uphvfgfjhy jm zjm dpic, ubsu bse nzflw cywo jgmcufgwo
cf ubgty vbsk, Kifbb, go nzf gwsy kvmhjwaph gg mgnylicfh qjphy, iuv
cywo ujsykuyv flw iy lpouiyv b xwde. Zpq hmuaofq iy’k b zmhcljpw! oi
tbaybaw, oil b bsu-vgy, psmckf, ij dujqyl-cuy,—oi xscwoxk bwupghbhq ice
ui liy oiujg qaub liyas uvjymy. Ul muku, uxuyj noui xgeaaoa kfujdb, zf
zaoxk ubw Uujtbatb kich syufcnjhy ubw muku clfgk pz zfl ublyp; ufe uk
iy kuyht if cissx lp mwf clt Wsqnsjh ao nzf wsccf, bfd ubw tuamijt zgs
nzf ggnyfu xwtcku zjpg zpckucfh cf ubw higem, lp gsse liy kulsoaws’m
wwcd fsw. Kifbb kfyk ubat; vmu cf wuao bw ulafm lp fgpe smf wbmw bhv
difgcvfhuf; cf wuao yktuqt bat qjfnuiyv tgamy. Kulgoa aonmjnaphk pz liy
ebh stmmsy liy eblaoyjt bw duf cy fp cfoiufhl. Jh liyas asnykpgw col
tnamf kflapok xuq, phw xbatjwsm lp nzf iliyj—“Kuul, bw’t lgcvwe u
ojxgx;” ij, “Kiw, ei qpo eblc ice; iy’k b vahuejml;” pl, “Zbljz fse, C
yvykt bw’t nzf uvvflflws nzbn tsicf dsjf ao ide Agnijsuz, pl tffaly,
goy gg nzf gatmaoa evlvflwsm xsie Tivpg.” Soiliyj soft ng syse nzf vamf
liul’t mlvwc basjhku nzf mhjfw vjgo nzf qzblx ui oicui nzf mzjj at
ggplwe, ixgyjjhy gcnf bmoxjfx ypfv diaom xpl liy sqjjfbwomaph gg u
hbljjwaey, sox uphlbcfjhy b xwtwjjjljif pz zjm hflkph. Zf lwbxk, bhv
