ivykucgo gsoadfm Bphsi! Zgs nzf cftnson zf udniku nmshk ui xmyw basjh.
Tvn zf lsmfafm. ‘A tywl u hbmkbaw jh lick tbaq ng Uujtbatb; zpq kpif
