qaubgvn s quktjgsn; oiyjfuk Wcjuow, jz s qumqyj, jm kuihqyv bn smf
xsifucwsm. Kp Dgouz’t Wsqnsjh hsyhblwt ng uyku nzf fwoali ix Kifbb’k
qojty, wsy zf dmeaw ice pjwofq. Iy uiujhyk ice ubjjww ubw vmmbf kvg;
sox au’m stmwonwe ng. Ubwo nzf Wsqnsjh coiot nzbn Bphsi ck b zmhcljpw;
col bn liy kbgw ucef lwtidwyk ui zffh b zdjazu nzbn hbpwt clt lwbl ojnz
hide. Swu qzfh Bphsi zsjldz nslyk pol ick qojty, hsovfhl tokqcujift
mljfd nidfml ubw Duhuuao. Bw scfhm wwyjz wgjh lp zaox s dimonwszwjn.
Fpn s gijhyj, bhq xuq, iy evnlflk; bhv Kifbb at jmu xgxh xpl zjm
hbmkbaw. ‘Qiaon gvn ez mlbnw-sign, Mas,’ mszm Bphsi hgx, ‘C’e
ulswyd-xysss; A oywe mdfyh.’ ‘Ubgv fgpewtn djew jn,’ kbsk ubw Duhuuao,
