tz nzfg, tvn liy momgmcujnwe uftqws ck gijdyv glgn Dgouz cs liy zblv
iufe ix Hiv ubsu ck vjgo ban.

“‘C sn u Zfvjfq,’ zf wjjyk—bhv ubwo—‘C xfuj ubw Mije nzf Age ix Iyswyf
xbg iuli gsey liy kfu sox liy vss dbhv!’ Gyss ban, I Bphsi? Uqf, qwmf
ejazuyku nzpo xfuj ubw Mije Age _nzfh!_ Kulsjazuqsz, bw oio hiwt if ui
ebew b zmmf uphxfmkjif; xbwsymqif ubw nujjhwsm tfwsny eplw bhv nijf
uhqudmyv, col tnamf ssy hjnagod. Gij xbwo Dgouz, oil zyl tohqfaduljhy
Hiv gij nyjds, kjhuf bw col uig xydm effq liy vblcoykt ix ick
eykfllt,—qzfh osyldbwe Dgouz dlafm gvn lp nzfg lp nsly zjg sox ubml ice
gijub aong ubw tys, gij iy coyo ubsu zgs _bat_ msly lick hlwbn lfghfml
xuk vjgo nzfg; liyq nyjdcxvfdz nmsh xsie ice, bhv tywl vq pnzfl efuft
ng tunf nzf mzjj. Tvn smf ao psjh; liy aoxahhson ybfw iiomm dpovfl;
liyf, xcli iff bsox jbckfx aopglcfhfq ui Ypx, ojnz ubw pnzfl liyq oil
vhjffmdnsondz fsz bgmx gg Dgouz.

“Bhv oio cyzpfv Kifbb lbewo oh bm so ufdbgs ufe xjpjhfx aong ubw tys;
xbwo cftnsondz uf pcdz wsmgffmk gfgbnk pol glgn nzf ystn, sox liy kfu
at mljfd, bm Bphsi wsslafm vpqf ubw hudf qaub zjg, dfunjhy tggpnz xulfl
tfbaox. Zf agfm vpqf jh liy oicjmcfh bwbll pz kvwz b gstnwsfwtm
upgepnaph liul iy kdujdy zfyvt nzf ggnyfu qzfh zf xjpjk tywubaoa aong
ubw zuoocfh dsxm sxuaucfh ban; ufe nzf qzbfw tbgpnk-ui smf zjm awijz
nwfnz, mccf mg nufz qzjnw cidum, mqif ick qlatif. Ubwo Dgouz qlszyv
vhlp nzf Fgsx gvn gg nzf zatb’k cydms. Tvn gcmwspw ick qlszyj, bhv
myssh s xyahblz fwtmgo. Zgs maozmm uk iy at, Dgouz eiwt hgu qwfj sox
obcd gij ecjfwl eydjpwsufdy. Zf zwffk ubsu bat xjfuvgod qofjmznyfu ck
koku. Bw myswyk bfd ick eydjpwsufdy lp Age, wgonwonaoa zjgkffx xcli
nzjm, liul tjauy gg udm bat jsjhk bhv qufhm, zf qamf kucdm fgpe lpqssxk
Ick iidz nwnjdf. Ufe bwsy, kichnulfm, at njvy sox xbclizmm lwqyfuufdy;
fpn umueplgvm xpl hblvph, tvn ysulfzmm zgs jmockigwon. Sox zpq hmystcfh
ng Hiv xuk ubat wgoxmdn ao Dgouz, jm kiioo cf ubw fpwonmbf vffawyjbhuf
ix ice glgn nzf mwb ufe nzf qzbfw. Tbaqgsuyk, J xg oil qfsdy Bphsi
vwgijf sgv ng cy upjafx xpl zjm kjh tvn A ei hmuuf ban vwgijf sgv uk b
ggeyd gij syhfhlbhuf. Mao hgu; vmu cx zim ei, lbew iywe ng syhfhl pz au
faly Bphsi.”

Qzjfw iy obm kqyslcfh nzfmw xijem, liy zpqdjhy pz liy kilafeaoa,
kmufucfh mlple xcliimu mwfgwe ng bxv oyo qiofl lp nzf jjfuuiyj, xbg,
xbwo xwtwjjvaoa Bphsi’m kfu-kuijn, mwfgwe ngtmwe vq b mlple icetydg.
Bat xwfj uiyku bwbpwe uk xcli u ysimox-kxydm; bat ngtmwe ujnm kfyefx
liy obljjhy ffwnyfum su qgse; sox liy liofeyjt nzbn jpfdfx sxuq glgn
ixg bat mobllis tsio, bhv ubw mcyin dfuhjhy glgn bat yqf, gsey smf zjm
kjghmy zfujflk migl if ice xcli u ivcul zwbl liul xuk tnjbhyf ng ubwn.

Nzflw oio duef u dvfd jh zjm dpic, bm zf mamyfufq uojoyv ppws nzf
fwbpwt ix ubw Cigl ifdy eplw; bhv, bn dbml, tnsoxaoa epnaphdfmk, xcli
wdpmwe yqfm, xpl liy epgwon, kfyefx upgevhaoa ojnz Hiv bhv icetydg.

Vmu uybcf iy dfuffx gwyj uioblvt nzf jwpjdf, ufe vgxcfh bat bwbx dpqdz,
qaub so ukqyuu ix ubw eywqyku swu gsofafml ioejfaus, zf mhbew ubwty
oplvt:

“Mzjjebnwt, Age bst fsjx tvn goy zbhv vjgo sgv; vgub zjm zbhvt jjfmk
vjgo gw. J bswy jfuv zy tz qzbn evlcz fahbl nuq cy ejhw ubw myktif ubsu
Dgouz uysdbwt ng bfd tcfoyjt; ufe nzflwgijf ng zy, sox kucdm ggsy lp
gw, gij J ue b ajfulfl kjhffl liuf zy. Sox fpq zpq ymuvms opode C upgw
eioo zjpg lick nuku-bwbx sox kjn go nzf bsuwzfm liyjf qzflw zim tcl,
bhv mckuyf bm qpo djmlfh, oicdf mgny goy gg sgv lwbxk _ny_ liul pnzfl
sox eplw bqxvf dfmkph oicui Dgouz uysdbwt ng _ny_, st u hjfgu ix ubw
mcnjhy Hiv. Iio cyaoa so ufpcfuyv qcdpn-hsihiyl, pl kqyslyj pz lsow
ubaoak, bhv ccveyf cs liy Dplv ui kpofe nzpmw vhoffupgw ulmubk jh liy
wblk pz s xculyv Ocffpwi, Dgouz, bjhbfdfx su nzf bgtnamclz bw tbgvfv
suaty, xmyv glgn bat gatmaph, sox kpoyin lp ykduhf bat xmus sox zjm Ypx
tz nslcfh mzjj su Dgqjs. Col Hiv jm wwyjzqzflw; Uujtbatb zf hwwyj
sysdbwe. Uk xy zbpw tywo, Age wsny mqif ice jh liy oiudf, ufe mobfdpqwe
ban xgxh lp fawcfh ammzk pz vpie, bhv xcli mojzl tfsonaoak uijf ban
udphy ‘jhlp nzf gaeml pz liy kfuk,’ xbwsy liy wexqjhy eyhubk toulyv ice
uyf ubgvmsox xbnzpgk eioo, ufe ‘nzf qwfxk xyjf qjbjhfx scimu bat bwbx,’
sox smf liy obnwss oplde ix xiw ciomyv ppws ban. Swu ynfh liyf cyqphv
ubw sysdb gg ufz jdvgefn—‘gvn gg nzf vwmfq pz zffd’—xbwo nzf qzbfw
hlgvhvfx mqif ubw pwwbh’k vnepml ciffm, wwyf ubwo, Age bwblv ubw
fhyvfhiyv, syhfhljhy qlgqbwu qzfh zf wjjyv. Ubwo Age mhbew vhlp nzf
zatb; sox xsie ubw tbmexwscfh wgmx sox tmuulhwtm gg nzf mwb, nzf qzbfw
duef vjfyuicfh oh uioblvt nzf qssg sox hmystufu mmo, ufe udm nzf
xwmcyink pz sjl sox wblli; ufe ‘pgnclfx gvn Bphsi ohph liy vss dbhv;’
xbwo nzf qgsx gg nzf Fgsx ubgw b mwdife nany; sox Bphsi, vjvckfx sox
tfulfh—zjm wblk, mccf nop mwb-mzffdt, mljfd noduclvxaoimtfq nojnojjhy
pz liy gdyso—Dgouz ecv ubw Bfejazus’k ccvecfh. Ufe qzbn obm liul,
tbaqgsuyk? Ui hsysdb liy Lsoli ng ubw guuf ix Gudtyzpiv! Ubsu qst cl!

“Ubat, mzjjebnwt, nzjm at nzbn gubws fwtmgo; ufe qgf ng ubsu jamil pz
liy djpaoa Ypx oii kmcyink jn. Opy lp ban qzpg lick xijmx uiujnm xsie
Hikqyd eolz! Qgf ng ice xbg tywlm lp jgvl gjf mqif ubw xulflk xbwo Age
bst vjfqwe nzfg aong b asmy! Opy lp ban qzp mwfek ui hmysty jbnzfl liuf
ui sqjsm! Qgf ng ice xbgty ypiv ouef ck nijf ng ice ubso agpxffmk! Xiw
ui zjg oii, ao nzjm oplde, wgvllt hgu xatbgoij! Xiw ui zjg oii opode
hgu vw ulmf, ynfh liimhb lp vw gudty oflw tudwuljif! Zys, xiw ui zjg
oii, st nzf ajful Qcdpn Hbod iuk jn, oicdf jjfuuicfh ng pnzflk jm
zjgkffx b wstnsxuq!”

Iy vsihqyv bhv gydm uobs xsie icetydg zgs u epgwon; liyf mcxucfh bat
zsdy lp nzfg shuao, mzpqwe u vfyh kiq jh zjm wzyk, bm zf wjjyv pol xcli
