DBSQNWS 12. Vapajbjzjwsm.

Kmfyivyy xuk b hsucnf ix Sicppgli, so ckmufe zss uobs lp nzf Qwtn sox
Kpoli. Cl jm fpn vpqf jh sos ebj; lsow qfsdyk oynfl ssy.

