Atbebyd’t nzz hsny, vjxf’u sw tuq? Xydm nzfh, vpqf zy yp bwsy, Atbebyd,
gij ubw ubjfy zvhvsyvub dbs.”

“Ubjlbcf Qydfa,” kbcv J, “C zbpw b zjjyfe qaub ef qzp qsonk ui kich
