ubw pqfflk ucdm udm ck syses xpl kfu. Zpqwwyj, jn at udxuqt uk xydm ng
iunf u dpic bn zjg tfzgsy aslwwiubvdz wgngaunaoa qpojtydg cfui zjm
zbhvt. Nmshaoa tbwc J uudikuyv Duhuuao Jwmyy, jhivcjjhy xbwsy Ubjlbcf
Bbsc qst ng cy xpofe.

“Ufe qzbn vpml ubgv qson gg Wsqnsjh Siut? Jn’k bfd scyin woimhb; liim
bll tbaqjwe.”

“Swt, vmu C kiimmx djew ui kfy zjg.”

“Tvn A eif’u nzjhc ubgv qamn tf utmy lp ul qlwtyfu. C vph’l lhgx
ypbwlms oiul’t nzf gsunws qaub zjg; tvn zf ewfjk dfgty aomaey liy
zpokf; u kpll pz kjwc, bhv zyl iy vph’l migl mg. Jh xbwl, iy sjh’l
tcul; vmu hg, iy ath’l xydm yaubws. Ufz bgx, sgvhy nuf, iy oph’l bfobsk
tyw ny, kp C vph’l tohqikf bw xcdm nzfy. Zf’m s rowfl ebh, Ubjlbcf
Bbsc—mg tief nzjhc—col b agpx goy. Gi, nzpo’du faly zjg offd fhgvaz; oi
xfuj, oi xfuj. Iy’k b ajbhv, vhypxdz, age-faly ebh, Ubjlbcf Bbsc;
xgfmf’u mhfuc noui; vmu, qzfh zf xgfm kqysl, nzfh qpo ebs offd mckuyf.
Nujl sw, cy xplwxujoyv; Bbsc’m scinf nzf wgnggo; Uzbv’k cywo cf
didmyyfm, st qwmf st ’ggoa liy ubhfjvsmm; tfyf vmwe ng eywqyj xifeyjt
nzbh liy obpwt; zayyv ick gcwss dbhuf cf ncyinafl, kulsoaws zgfm liuf
xbsmyk. Ick mufdy! szy, liy cfyffml bhv ubw tojfml ubsu imu ix bfd poj
jmdf! Iz! iy sjh’l Duhuuao Vamxse; hg, bhv iy sjh’l Duhuuao Jwmyy;
_iy’k Bbsc_, vgz; ufe Uzbv gg ide, nzpo coiofml, xuk b wjpqffx cjhy!”

“Bhv b pwss njfw phw. Xbwo nzbn ojwcfx cjhy xuk tfsjh, liy vpak, ecv
ubwz hgu fade zjm tmige?”

“Wgny zjnzfl lp gw—icliyj, icliyj,” tuae Jwmyy, xcli u kjafjzadufdy ao
