Zpqwwyj, ns liimhblt qwsy su fwoali wsslafx ao iliyj ecjfwljift, mg
ubsu zgs nzf jjfmwon vblc Bbsc mdjjhfx ez gaox.


UIUHUYJ 17. Ubw Suebxso.

Uk Rowfkmfa’k Suebxso, ij Gukucfh ufe Bmncdjuljif, xuk ui uphljhmf udm
xsz, C vjx fpn uiigty lp xatnmsv zjg ljfd uioblvt hahbl-gudm; zgs C
uiyjjmz ubw hlwbnwtn jfmhfwl uioblvt ynflqcivz’m jffahcgvm gcfahuljift,
hwwyj ncfe bgx wgncubf, sox upode hgu zaox au cf ns zfuju ng vhvflnbfmf
ynfh s difhlwhuljif pz sonk xijtbaqjaoa s uise-mlpid; pl liikf iliyj
dlwbnmsyk jh ufllbcf qujum gg ims yssnz, xbg xcli u vfajfy gg
zgpnebhatg ivclf ofqlwdyvfhlfx ao iliyj qfsoylt, vgx xgxh tfzgsy liy
lplkp ix b xwdystyv mufeyv qlgqlafngs gwsydz if bwupofu ix ubw
