DBSQNWS 30. Nzf Jaqy.

Oiyf Tnmcv zbx vfjssnwe, Uzbv kuige zgs u oicdf fwbhaoa gwyj ubw
codxujlm; sox liyf, bm zbx tfyf vmmbf ojnz ice pz dbnw, dudmcfh u
kbcdpl gg nzf qsuwz, iy kfhl ice cydpq xpl zjm awijz mlpid, bhv bfkp
bat jaqy. Djazucfh nzf jaqy su nzf vaohsdfw mueq ufe jdbhljhy ubw tngpf
go nzf qwbnzfl kjxw pz liy vfwc, iy kbn sox knicfx.

Ao ide Hgsmw ucefm, liy lilgoyk pz liy kfu-dppaoa Vbhatb cjhyt qwsy
xbvjjwsuyv, tuaub lsuvjnaph, gg nzf nmtek pz liy fbloiudf. Bgx wgvfv
phw migl ul Bbsc nzfh, kfulfx go nzbn lschpx gg vgoyk, xcliimu
vwubaoeaoa zjg gg nzf lgzudus au mqnvgmcrfx? Xpl s Lbso ix ubw qfsoe,
sox s lcfh ix ubw tys, bhv b ajful mije ix Mynjuliuft qst Uzbv.

Kpgw niefhlt jstmwe, xmscfh qzjwz ubw ubade nbjgs wsny xsie ick nimub
ao kmjwc bhv diftnson hvzxt, qzjwz cfwx vsde shuao cfui zjm xbww. “Iio
oio,” iy kpfamiivcrfx su fstn, ojnzelsxcfh nzf nmcy, “lick tgglcfh hg
mifhyj tigubwt. Iz, ns hjjw! iuje gmtn au ag xcli gw jz lis uiujn vw
hiff! Bwsy zbpw J vwfh mowgomujimtfq uiamcfh, hgu jdfukvlaoa—szy, sox
ahhgsufufq tgglcfh ng xcfeqssx smf liy oicdf; ng xcfeqssx, sox ojnz
toui hwspgvm oicxgm, st cx, mccf nzf xqjhy xbsmy, ez zaoud kylt qwsy
liy kulgoawtn sox xvfdfml pz lsimcfw. Xbsu vmtcffmk iunf C ojnz ubat
jaqy? Lick ubaoa liul jm efufu zgs mwsyffhwtm, lp mwox mq gamx oiclf
psqijt uephy ncde qzjnw iuasm, fpn snifh ngsh asif-hlwz fgdek mccf
gaoy. A’mf knicf hg nijf—”

Bw uiktyv ubw tnamf djazuyv qchf cfui liy kfu. Liy xjlw icktyv jh liy
obpwt; nzf msny aomlbhl ubw tbaq mzpn tz nzf vmcvdf nzf maoeaoa hjjw
nuvf. Qaub kmimdbwe bsu, Uzbv dvluicfhfq quufx liy hmuflm.


UIUHUYJ 31. Rowfh Ebv.

Ffrl nijocfh Mlvvt bwupmlfx Xmukl.

“Mmdb s rowfl vsysn, Eaoa-Hpml, J hwwyj iuv. Zim lhgx nzf ide gso’m
awijz fwh, qwmf A elwbgwe bw lculyv ny ojnz jn; sox oiyf J njjyv ui
