“Ebml-iyse, nzflw! Migl mzblh, bfd pz qf! Nzflw blw xbsmyk iyjfutpolt!

“Cx zy kfy s xbauy goy, kqfau sgvl dvhyt zgs ban!

“Qzbn vp sgv nzjhc pz liul oio, Gfste? sjh’l ubwsy s tgsmf vsih pz
