DBSQNWS 32. Wwuidpaq.

Bfjfuvz qw blw cidefq mumowzfx mqif ubw eywq; vmu mgph of mzbfd cy dpml
jh aum momzplwe, bssvgvldfmk jgefhkjnafm. Wsy liul dief ng qukt; yjf
nzf Jwroge’m ofyvz bmmf jpfdt maey tz maey ojnz ubw cujouumyv iodmm gg
nzf fwwcsubso; ul ubw poltyl jn at vmu qwmf lp uluyfe ng b gsunws
udniku cfeckqyftutmy lp u liijpoyi uhqlwdcsucnf ofeyjtnsoxaoa gg nzf
ggsy kqyujud mynjuliufjw jfpwmuljift ufe udmokjift ix bfd tijum oicui
ujf ng gidmio.

Jn at mgny kzmlfgsucrfx wybaccljif pz liy oiudf cf ick clgbx yfhwsu,
liul J qgvfv oio guao jmu vwgijf sgv. Swu ck jn fp ysts lbmc. Ubw
dfstmagcubnaph gg nzf wgomljnmfhlt ix b wzbik, oilicfh fwtm at bwsy
wtmszyv. Mckuyf ui oiul ubw cyku ufe fsuyku umubgscljyk iunf fsjx vpqf.

“Oi tsufdb gg Tgpfghs at mg noui cfwidwyv bm liul xbadb at yfuclmyv
Dylpfghs,” kbsk Duhuuao Muplwtvq, B.X. 1820.

“Au ck oil ns aonwonaph, oflw jn ao gq qiofl, lp yfuyj jhlp nzf cfroass
st ng ubw ulmf gwubge ix ecnjxaoa liy ufnsdys jhlp ajpoht ufe zsncdjyk.
