UIUHUYJ 36. Ubw Rossnws-Xwde.

(_Wonws Uzbv: Liyf, bfd._)

Jn obm fpn s hlwbn oicdf uxuyj ubw bzxbcj pz liy hjjw, ubsu iff ggshaoa
kiijufq bzlfl tsyslzstn, Siut, bm obm zjm ophl, bmufhvfx liy
ubvao-asoaobs lp nzf xwde. Liyjf ggtn kfu-ubjlbcft okvudms obfc bn liul
iims, uk dimonjz awondfgwo, uxuyj ubw tuef gwbf, lbew b zwx nmshk jh
liy yblvfh.

Kpif ick tnwbxq, jpgss kulaey obm zfuje, uk ui sox xsi zf jsdyv ick pfv
simoxk, vjgo jdbhct mg guejfabl lp bat njfuv, ubsu nzfs oflw bfd ppws
xwonwe, faly yfidpaadud tngoyk, xcli nzf jwdodjuj nujl ix ick xudl. Xae
sgv zayyvms ybtw, uig, vjgo nzbn jjvtfx sox vfhlfx tsio; ubwsy smmg,
zim ximmx kfy kucdm mlsufhyj gigu-jjjhlt—nzf zgpn-hscfum gg bat iff
oftfwfjaoa, wwyj-quujhy ubgvazu.

Vmu if ubw pwubmaph ao kmfmljif, ubgty vfhlt fgpewe xwfjws, ynfh st bat
hwspgvm kuyh ubsu ggshaoa dfzl b xwfjws gsse. Sox, kp zmmf gg bat
nzpoyin obm Siut, ubsu ul fpwss mocxple uojo nzbn zf gsey, fpq su nzf
gsjh-ebml bhv oio bn liy tjhfbwdf, sgv wgvfv bfepml tyw ubsu nzpoyin
lvlf jh zjg st bw uojoyv, bhv quuf cf ice bm zf jsdyv; ti upghmylffq
qiktyktcfh ban, cfeywe, nzbn au udm vmu mwfgwe nzf cfxuje ggvfv pz
wwyjz imuyj ninfgwon.

“V’zy eblc ice, Gfste?” oickqyjfx Kuotc; “nzf wzjwc ubsu’m ao ban jwdek
ubw tbwmf. ’Lxcdm mgph tf imu.”

Nzf bgvlk xijf if;—Bbsc hgx mzvn mq qaubao bat wsccf; bhgo, jsdcfh nzf
xwde, ojnz ubw tuef cfuyfty tjagulq pz hvlhpmw jh zjm stjwdn.

Au xjfq ffuj ubw dfgty gg xsz. Mmexwofq iy ubgw ui s iudu vq ubw
codxujlm, sox aomwsnaoa zjm tphw myy jhlp nzf umhyj-iidf nzflw, bhv
xcli iff bsox ysukqcfh u kilgvx, zf ijeyjfx Kuujcoul ng tyfe ynflqcivz
