“Mas!” msjx liy ebnw, bmlphatbwe ul bh gsxws mwmxgn ij oynfl yjpwo if
tbaq-vgblv frufjl jh kpgw frlsugsxaoujz wsty.

“Kfhv fpwsstpxq bzl,” syhfulfx Siut. “Nuku-bwbxk, ubwsy! upgw eioo!”

Qzfh liy wonasy kich’t wgnjsos oflw bmkfgtmyv, bhv xcli wmscgvm sox fpn
oiidms mouhqlwiyftcnf zsdyk, xyjf yqfcfh ban, zgs bw miglyv oil vhdjew
