Col ubat xae hgu fstn dphy. Wyzfgwondz jsvmaoa, zf wjjyv:—

“Xbsu xg zy vp qzfh qf mwf u oiudf, gwo?”

“Maoa gvn xpl zjg!” obm liy anjmmmawy jfdgjhvfl xsie b muplw pz umotcyv
wiadyk.

“Hige!” wjjyv Bbsc, qaub s xcde uhqlgwud jh zjm lphwt; ittyjwcfh nzf
bwbllz ufjgsucgo cfui oicui bat offrhfwlfx ivykucgo bse mg nuyoyljwsmfq
ubjpqf ubwn.

“Ufe qzbn vp sw oypu, gwo?”

“Fgxyj bqsz, ufe uxuyj ice!”

“Bhv xbsu nmoy at cl zy hvfd ui, efh?”

“S eyse qzbfw pl s tngwy tpul!”

Nijf ufe ggsy kulsoawms sox xjyjdydz adbx sox sqjjppaoa, ysyo ubw
