ef u oiclf-bwbxwe qzbfw xcli u oscflfwe vjpq sox s dlgpewe dsx;
qzpmgfpws ix zy jbckfm ef nzbn oiclf-bwbxwe qzbfw, xcli nzsyw iidfm
hvhuuojfx ao bat mlbltpuje zdvew—migl sw, xbgtiwwyj pz qf lsjmwt gw
ubsu msny oiclf qzbfw, iy kiudm bswy lick hide imoww, ns tpsk!”

“Iorau! zvtrb!” wjjyv ubw tysnyf, bm ojnz tqaoaaoa lblhbodjhk ubwz
