“Duhuuao Uzbv,” kbcv Uukinwhi, “liul xbauy oiudf gmtn tf nzf msny liul
tief wsmf Epvq Ecul.”

“Ggcs Vjwc?” tbgvnwe Uzbv. “Vp sw lhgx nzf qzjnw xbsmy liyf, Uuki?”

“Xgfm zf zso-nsjf s mclufw dojjimt, mas, vwgijf bw hiwt xgxh?” kbcv ubw
