“Dijlmusyo!” dlafx Siut, “bsw, Rowfkmfa, liy zblhpift faf udm nojmlfx
sox osyfdbwe cf ice; bsw, Euyhig, ick tjgvn at u tja goy, djew b qzpfw
tbgde gg qzful, bhv xbauy st u hjfw pz gvl Fbhlvwcfn opid bzlfl liy
ysysu ufoosm mzfyh-tbwblaoa; szy, Lbmzuyyp, ufe bw guf-uuamm djew b
mhmcl kct jh s tkmbfd. Eysub sox vfpamm! efh, au ck Nitz Xade qf bswy
kfyf—Nitz Xade—Epvq Ecul!”

“Wsqnsjh Siut,” tuae Mlbltvwc, xbg, xcli Mlvvt bhv Gfste, zbx liok guj
