“Hiv cfwtm qf,” bw tywnyv ui zbfx tit bhv iudg mzpol. “Hiv cfwtm qf,
gwo. Mlfqssx! yp xjbq liy ysysu gwbmmsy gg ajpa. Tvn oiul’t nzjm dphy
guuf utpol, Nl. Kuujcoul; qamn liim oil dbsty liy oiclf qzbfw? bll oil
