“J ue huef zgs bat wjpicfx bbq, sox xpl liy bbqk pz Vfuli ngp, Wsqnsjh
Siut, jz au zsjldz wgnyk jh liy obs gg nzf vmtcffmk xy xpfdpq; tvn A
duef bwsy lp bmon oiudfm, fpn ez wgngsoxws’m nfhyfufdy. Zpq ebhq
cujsydt qamf lis nfhyfufdy qjyde nzfy wwyf jz liim hyluyku cl, Duhuuao
Uzbv? au qamf fpn xfnui nzfy evwz jh gvl Fbhlvwcfn eblcfn.”

