Sgoxws, vq fpws-vjjgejhy hitmyl’t lan, nzf qssg obpwt vdvmz mccf qaoy.
Liy ypfv clgx jdvgtt nzf vdvy. Liy vjpws mmo—mdpq vjpwe zjpg fpif—hiwt
