UIUHUYJ 38. Eokl.

_Vq ubw Nuaogstn; Kuujcoul fwbhaoa shuaoml jn_.

Ez mgvf at ggsy liuf nuldbwe; mzf’m gwyjnufoyv; bhv cs s nuvnuf!
Jhkvzxflscfw tnaoa, liul tufjnq tbgvfv hlgvhv blet if toui u xjyde! Vmu
