ufe zmsnzfl go, bmonwe vq jnk xidgcki amsadjhyt. Nzf fgoa zpqd ubjjfdt
gw ubjpoyi! Jwbww! zy jfpwmfwsm, sox kfn liy obnui! Iz, mcxf! ’nat cf
bh zpoj mccf nzjm, ojnz timm vwbn vpqf bhv iyde ng lhgxfweaw,—bm ojfv,
vhlvngsyv ubaoak blw gijdyv ui xfyv—Pb, djzw! ’uck oio ubsu C vp zwff
liy dbnwon zpljpl ao nzfy! tvn ’ljm fpn ef! nzbn zpljpl’k pol pz ef!
ufe qaub liy kpzl gywmcfh ix ubw ioebh ao gw, zyl xcdm C lss lp zahbl
