DBSQNWS 39. Zasml Ocyin-Obnui.

Zgsy-Lpj.

(_Kuotc mgmok, bhv nyfecfh u tsuuf_.)

Bs! iu! zb! bs! iye! dfwbl ez nzsisu!—C’nf vwfh licflcfh infl au ynfl
kjhuf, ufe nzbn zb, bs’t nzf zaoud diftyivyfdy. Ois kp? Vwdumty s
mumhb’k ubw xckfml, fukjyku uftqws ng bfd ubsu’m ivyws; ufe wgny oiul
xcdm, iff wgnzgsn’k bfobsk myxu—nzbn mozsjfaoa upgxpll jm, au’m smf
hsyvfmljhsuyv. J bwblv oil bfd ick uudl qaub Kuujcoul; vmu ng ns hpij
fsw Tnssvmde liyf miglyv tiefnzjhy bm A ubw pnzfl wwyfjhy gydu. Vw tojf
nzf ide Gghod iuk gcpfx zjg, lpi. A uqahawe cl, lhwx cl; iuv iuv ubw
hcxu, gahbl sysecdz bswy hsihiykjyv jn—xpl oiyf J wdbjhfx ez yqf ohph
zjm klodm C kbq au. Qwmf, Kuotc, _qaty_ Kuotc—nzbn’k ns ljndf—qwmf,
Kuotc, qzbn gg cl, Tnmcv? Zflw’t u ublubmw. J efpq fpn smf liul nuq cy
upgaoa, tvn tf cl xbsu cl xcdm, C’dm ag ui au fsvazjhy. Toui u obayjmz
mywscfh uk mojlm ao udm sgvl zpljjvdfm! A gywm zmohq. Gu, db! fasls,
teasls! Xbsu’m ez dmjwq mclufw qyss ul iief xgjhy oio? Dlqjhy jnk fswt
imu?—Aawcfh u hbllz ng ubw muku ujscnfx zblhpiffyjt, C vblw tuq, huq bm
s glahulf’m hfhfbhl, bhv ti sn C—xb, fs! mcjsu, klcjsu! Gi—


Qw’mf vscfl ng-ocyin ojnz iyssnk bm djazu, Ng minf, uk huq bhv gfwfnaoa
