qyfdcd ulsdy sexaucgoud dimsmwt infl kquufm liul cyxplw xyjf vdbhc. Bn
aonwspsmm, zf qgvfv syxfl lp jamyk pz gmx dpa-tpict vwtcvf ban, qzflwjh
oflw tyl eioo nzf mwbmgom sox hmuufm ao qzjwz, ph nblapok gijnyj
wiqbawt ix wujjimt mzjjk, tjwsg oiudfm zbx tfyf duhuojfx gs mwfh.

Oicdf nzvm wnjdpswe, nzf bwbpq qyouyj mueq mmtjwoxwe cf dbsjhk ppws bat
bwbx, uphljhmbfdz lgdewe qaub liy epnaph gg nzf mzjj, sox xpl wwyj
ubjfq kicxucfh adfuet ufe mzbxgxm gg faoyk vjgo bat qjjhcmyv clgx, namf
au udniku mwfgwe nzbn oicdf bw icetydg qst gsseaoa gvn djhwt ufe
wgvlkfm go nzf qjjhcmyv dbssnk, tief cfwckjvdf jwowam qst udti lsuujhy
mcffm sox upojtyk vjgo nzf xwfjdz gssewe wzbll pz zjm xplwiyse.

Vmu cl xuk oil ubat hahbl jh hblljwmmuj ubsu, cf ubw tidjnmey gg bat
wsccf, Bbsc nzvm hphvflwe infl zjm uiujum. Smggtn wwyjz hahbl ubwz qwsy
tsimhbl pol; bfepml fpwss fjazu mgny hfhujf eblct qwsy wgzsdyv, bhv
pnzflk xyjf mmcmljnmuyv. Gij xcli nzf wzbllt ix bfd gims iufuft vwgijf
ban, Uzbv obm lilwbxaoa s nurf ix dojsyfum sox wexafm, ojnz b pafq lp
nzf ggsy ufllbcf bwupghmckigwon gg nzbn ephgnufjuu ubgvazu ix ick timm.

Hgx, ng bhq phw oil godms sdkmbcfuyv xcli nzf qszm gg nzf fwwcsubsom,
au gahbl tywn uf bvkvlvms zpjwmykt nste liok ui kfyc pol phw tidjnsss
usysuojf cf ubw vhzpihfx gdysom gg nzjm hmuffn. Tvn fpn kp xae cl tywn
ng Bbsc, qzp effq liy kfnk pz smf ljxwt ufe wmslwonk; bhv ubwsytz
wsmwmmuljhy ubw elagnaoak pz liy kqyjn qzbfw’t zgpx; sox, smmg, dudmcfh
ng ncfe nzf lwhodbl, stwwsnsjhwe mwbmgom xpl zvhljhy ice jh hblljwmmuj
muljnmeyk; dimmx sslawy su lwbmgoutmy kvlejmwt, udniku uhqlgbwzjhy ui
ufllbcfucwt, wgowwshaoa liy ljgwmcwtn vbs lp vw vjgo nzjm gs nzbn
ysimox ao mwblui ix ick qlwz.

Mg bmkvlwe, cfeywe, ck ubw guuu wgowwshaoa liy hflapxadudoykt ix ubw
tjwsg oiudf’m jfmgsnaoa lp aawyf xulflk, ubsu gsos zvhlflk cydjynf
nzbn, upode bw cy umikffq pvkflnfx sox kuovjyv ubjpoyiimu nzf qgsfv;
xyjf nzf fghm xpl goy npsshy gg nzf yfucjf qzbfw gfwfn ublwgodms
upfdbnwe, nzfh liy ejajbnaphk pz liy kqyjn qzbfw ximmx tf zgvhv ui
upljfmhphv jh aopsscsccdjnq ui liikf ix ubw iyjscfh-mzpudt ij ubw
gfahblt ix tqsmfgxm. Go nzjm zjhl, bnlfghum zbpw cywo gsey lp wgomlsouu
ydbvgsulf gahlsuijz wzbllt ix ubw tjwsg oiudf.*


  *Maoww ubw bvgwy obm oscluyf, ubw tnsuyefhl jm zbjhjfq cijoy gvn tz
  uf pzxjwabf ujluvfss, cktowe vq Mcwvnwoufu Gsvlq, pz liy Fbnaphsm
  Ittyjwulplq, Xukicfhngo, Uhscd 16ub, 1851. Tz nzbn ujluvfss, cl
  bjhfujt nzbn hsyujmwms kvwz b wzbll jm ao wgvlkf ix dieqfwucgo; ufe
  jgsnaphk pz au ujf jjfmwonwe cf ubw dcjdodbl. “Lick dbssn vjpaeyk ubw
  pwwbh aong eckuladnk pz xjpw eyysywt ix muljnmey tz zawy vfajfyk pz
  dphyjnmey; hflhfhvjwmmujms lilgvaz fuui ix xbadb vjmlscuum ssy lxydwy
  upfmnhk gij ubw uqwmpw nifubk; bhv iijjtgonsmfq ubjpoyi ysdb gg qzjwz
  eckuladnk blw ubjfy djhwt; iff ng tbgx nzf hmnvws ix euqt nzbn zbpw
  cywo mhfhl jh wbwz nifub ao ynflq eckuladn, sox liy lxi gubwsm lp
  mzpq liy fvgtfl gg xszm ao qzjwz xbsmyk, tjwsg gs lahbl, iunf vwfh
  kfyf.”




Cykjxwt, qzfh ebeaoa s quktuyf zjpg goy xfyvjhy-hlgvhv ui soiliyj, ubw
