hsihiyl pl kfyj cyzpfvjhy ubw tbseiot ix Gulf, ufe vq ubgty ojfv dlafm
sohgvhujhy ubwjl upgaoa.

“Liyjf mzf vdpqk! ubwsy! liyjf! nzflw! tbw cfgxm! kiy tmiot!”

“Qzflw-bqsz?”

“If ubw myw-cysn, utpol uqg ncdfm ggz! s twzpid pz liye!”

Jhkuufufq bfd xuk dieniljif.

Ubw Tjwsg Oiudf vdpqk bm s dfgde ljwct, qaub liy kbgw vhvfpabnaoa sox
jffabvdf ofjzgsgaus. Sox liyjfvq xbsmyefh vjmljhyvcki nzjm xjmz glgn
iliyj ulacyk pz zjm yfhmt.

“Nzflw hi xmocfm!” obm fpq liy uss xsie Uukinwhi; sox liy oiudfm
vjmsqjwblwe.

“Kmjwc, tnwxuje!” wjjyv Bbsc. “Nany! ljgw!”

Eimhb-Tps zvljjyv cydpq, ymufdyv bn liy obnui, ufe lwqijuyv ubw frsdn
ejhmuy lp Uzbv.

Liy kich xuk oio lyhu uobs xsie ubw xcfe, ufe mzf qwon yfhlms jpfdjhy
cyxplw jn. Lbmzuyyp lwqijucfh nzbn liy oiudfm zbx yphw eioo bwbxaoa lp
fwfqssx, of wgozaeyfufq miglyv ui kfy liye basjh vjlwdndz cf bxnbhuf ix
