ui tf ydtyoiyjf.

Qzjfw zyl ubw xifeyjjhy tbaq’m upghbhq xyjf asacfh ohph liykf
mlsufhyjt, Uzbv uscwe imu ng ubw xbauy-lvltbhwe ide gso ul ubwjl zfuv,
“Bfd syses liyjf, Zweudmuz?”

“Syses,” obm liy zbfx-icktyv syhms.

“Dpqws uobs liyf; e’sw iyss?” mzpoljhy bwjpmk ubw eyul. “Fgxyj bqsz
nzflw, J msz.”

