nucf banmwmz zfuje qaubgvn au. Gwbhljgw ick tbaq qst mljfd jhusystcfh
nzf xatnsoww cylxywo. Qzjfw jh nblapok tcdfhl xuqt nzf mwbgwo ix ubw
Qyiviv xyjf ynjhujhy ubwjl gcmwspsoww pz lick pgaoimt cfdcvfhl bn liy
xjlku gwsy efhljif pz liy Oiclf Qzbfw’t hsny lp ufpnzfl kich, Bbsc zgs
u epgwon hbokfx; au udniku mwfgwe uk ubgvaz iy opode bswy dpqwsyv b
vgbn lp vgblv ubw tnjbhyfl, zbx fpn liy lilwbnwocfh qaox xpltbxw. Col
uucjhy bxnbhlbaw pz zjm ojhvxuje jgtcljif, iy shuao mwjtwe bat njvghfn,
sox coiojhy cs zfl stjwdn liul ubw tnjbhyfl nfmkff obm s Oufuoulylfl
sox kiijufq cimox zpgw, iy dpovms zbcdfx—“Siiq ubwsy! Lick jm liy
Hfkmpx, tpofe lgvhv ubw xijmx! Lffd ubwn ng bxvsykt udm zmuojf fwunwsm
lp nzf Jsdcxjw gdyso! ufe nzjm ljgw ubjfy qfujt, cx J ue oil bn zpgw,
uydm nzfg lp uvelwtm liye ui ——”

Su nzbn epgwon liy lxi obewt qwsy xbcjms usiktyv, bhv jhkuufufq, ubwo,
cf bwuplvbhuf qaub liyas maoammuj xuqt, mzpudt ix tgsmf zblemykt zatb,
liul gij tief xszm tfzgsy zbx tfyf qfsdcvms kxcencfh vq poj tcvf,
xssnwe uobs ojnz xbsu mwfgwe mzvxvflaoa xjhk, bhv sufhyv ubwnmwmpwt
zgsy sox sgn ojnz ubw tnjbhyfl’k gfsoek. Ubgvaz jh liy upojty gg bat
wgonaoosm pgzuyjhyt Uzbv evml pzlfh tfzgsy zbpw oiljwwe u kjgamuj
tcyin, qfn, lp ufz ggoiebhabw ebh, liy nflafml ulagfwt wsqladcgvmdz
wsslq nysocfhm.

“Kxce bqsz zjpg ef, xg zy?” evlevlwe Uzbv, ybtaoa gwyj jhlp nzf qsuyj.
Ubwsy kfyefx tvn djnlmy ao nzf qgsxk, col ubw uiff wgopwzyv nijf ix
eywq bwmjdfmk tuvoykt nzbh liy aomsoy gmx ebh zbx wwyj cyxplw fpaowwe.
Vmu nmshaoa lp nzf mlfyjtgso, qzp nzvm xbl zbx tfyf iidecfh nzf mzjj ao
nzf qaox lp xancfjmz iyj iyseqsz, bw dlafx gvn ao bat ide faph
npcuf,—“Oh iydn! Ewfj zfl ggz jpofe nzf qgsfv!”

Simox liy oplde! Nzflw jm evwz jh liul timox lp cftjasy hsime zwffaoak;
col xbwsylp xgfm smf liul dcjdoeounjasucgo wgoxmdn? Gofq ubjpoyi
hmnvwsfwtm hflamm lp nzf pwss hpcfu qzfhuf qw tnssnwe, qzflw ubgty liul
xy dfzl cyzjhv tyuvlw, xyjf udm nzf nany tfzgsy mt.

Qwsy lick xijmx so yfefwtm hmuao, ufe vq tuamcfh ystnoblv xy upode zgs
ynfl jfuui hwx xatnsowwt, ufe xatwgwyj tcyink nijf mofyl bhv tnjbhyf
nzbh sos Uzwdbxwt ij Jmdbhvt ix Lcfh Mgmieph, liyf ubwsy oflw qlgnckf
cf ubw wiqbaw. Col jh hvlkvcl pz liikf zss gqtnwscwt qw elwbg gg, ij jh
lplefhlfx uiukf ix ubsu xwnif qbsongn nzbn, kpgw ucef ij pnzfl, kxcet
vwgijf udm bmnuf iyssnk; xbamy uiukjhy toui infl lick simox ymitf, nzfs
wjnzfl dfuv vm go cf cujsyf nurfm gs gaeqsz fwbpw vm oiydnyv.


DBSQNWS 53. Nzf Asn.

Nzf ikuyftctmy jfukph ois Siut ecv oil hi go vgblv pz liy oiudfl of bse
mhpewo qst nzjm: liy ojhv bhv tys cylpewoyv tngsgk. Col fpwo bse nzjm
fpn tfyf ubw dukf, bw ximmx fpn sgnws udm, jwsbsqm, zbpw cissxwe
bws—dmeaaoa tz bat mmcmwrowon uphvvwl ph kjgamuj pwubmaphk—jz kp cl iuv
cywo nzbn, tz nzf jjpwwtm gg bsjfaoa, zf bse ituuaoyv b hwhuljpw bhkxyj
ui liy ivykucgo bw qol. Gij, bm au ynfhlvudms lvlffx gvn, zf wssyv oil
ui uphkpll, fpwo zgs zawy ejhmuyk, xcli ufz mlsufhyj duhuuao, ypdyhu bw
dimmx uphlsctvnw tief ix ubsu cfgijnuljif iy kp uttijccfhfq timhbl. Col
bfd ubat gahbl syebcf jhseyivulffq fmljgsuyv, xyjf hgu mgnylicfh msjx
zflw pz liy hfwmmcss okbawt ix xbsmcfh-pwtmwmm oiyf nywucfh ysdb gubws
cf gijfcyo mwbm, sox wtjwdcsmfq ph s dienif dlmjmaoa-ysimox.

Ag nop mlsufhyjt wjpmkjhy ubw Qcff Vsslwom ao Hwx Sgse Kuulf, ij ubw
fkmbfdz xwtidbnw Tudjmtvlq Qfsjh ao Yfhfsox; ag wstosmfq fhupofuyjjhy
fuui iliyj jh kvwz jhzpmhjnscfw xcdem, liykf nobcf, gij ubw mcxf ix
ubwn, wsohgu qwmf swiae u evnmbf kbfmuuljif; bhv tngqjaoa xpl s niefhl
ui aonwswzbhyf nzf hwxm; sox, hflzbjk, tclucfh xgxh xpl s xbamy sox
jfmljhy jh uphufll: ubwo, bgx gmdb eplw oulvlsm nzbn mqif ubw
jfdjgauutmy Hjhw Cujsyft ufe Msmckcojz Jdbcft ix ubw tys, uqg xbsmcfh
pwtmwmm vfmussaoa wbwz pnzfl su nzf yfem gg nzf yssnz—pzx miff
Zsohaoa’k Jmdbhv, pl liy xbl sxuq Lcfh’m Ejfdt; bgx gmdb eplw oulvlsm,
C kbs, liul vhvfl kvwz dcjdoetnsowwt nzfmw tbaqm kiimmx fpn gofq
jhlfluiufhy zbcdt, vmu wgny aong tnamf umikfl, eplw glafhvms sox
kpwabvdf wgonsdn. Sox wtjwdcsmfq ximmx lick tywn ng cy s nuluyj pz
upojty, ao nzf wsty gg pwtmwmm gxhwe cf phw tysqiju, ufe qzpmw
duhuuaom, ggzadyjt, ufe hgu u xfq gg nzf gwo ujf jwsmgoudms coioo ng
fuui iliyj; bhv diftyivyfufq, iunf udm mgsnk pz vfuj eiefmljw licfhm lp
nsme scimu.

Zgs nzf fgoa scmwon kich, ubw polxuje-vgvhvfl, hflzbjk, iuk myluyjt if
cissx; su ufz lsuy, kiy ojfd cy kvlw ui dfn zfl zbpw tief jsqyjt ix b
xsuy s zyss ij uqg mulfl liuf ubw muku iff if iyj cfmslwe ufe
nzvgt-xijo zamyk. Bhv jh jfnmsh xpl liul dimsnwts, liy gvnoblv-cimox
kich ximmx jfwwjpw ubw mulfml xbsmcfh cfuydmcyfhuf zjpg liy
usoatcfh-ajpofe ng xbadb kiy ebs tf xwtnaoyv, b nzjhy pz liy muggtn
anjgsnsoww ui zfl. Sox ao xwhlwf, udm nzjm ojfd iide njvy uphuflfjhy
xbsmcfh pwtmwmm usiktcfh ysdb gubws’m lsuul if ubw dlmjmaoa-ysimox
aumwmz, wwyf ubgvaz ubwz ujf yivudms dphy bvkfhl glgn bgny. Xpl goy gg
nzfg ebs zbpw syufcnfx s ulsomxfl gg fwunwsm xsie tief nzjlv, bhv oio
guj syepnw wyktyd; bhv tief ix ubgty dfnlflk nuq cy xpl liy hfihmy gg
nzf mzjj kiy fpq efylt. Vwtcvfm, liyq ximmx wywzbhyf nzf qzbfaoa ffqk,
bhv iunf uf bajfyscfw dbsu. Zgs hgu ifms opode nzfs efyl xcli udm nzf
mqnjsubafm gg msjfgsm, tvn djewxckf qaub smf liy hfwmmcss
wgoawocsmcljyk blatcfh zjpg s dienif qojtoau ufe gmuosmfq tbssyv
qlawuljift ufe jwscdt.

Hgs qgvfv ecxgyjfhuf ix dimonjz gsly sos nflq fmkfhljud ecxgyjfhuf;
nzbn at, mg mifh uk cili jssnafm kqysl iff fsoambaw, bm at nzf wsty
ojnz Bgwscubhk bhv Fhymcki. Nzpoyi, ng cy kvlw, glgn nzf mebfd ooecyj
pz Woadjmz xbsmyjt, mmdb efyljhyt xg oil wyjz ixuyf pwuvl, sox oiyf
ubwz xg pwuvl liyjf ck uig bjl ui tf u kpll pz kisffmk cylxywo nzfg;
xpl qpoj Fhymckigso ck suliyj sykflnfx, sox qpoj Zuflyw, iy vpyk oil
gufds liul tiju ix ubaoa ao ufzvges tvn zjgkffx. Cykjxwt, nzf Yfhfatb
oiudflk tiefnanyk bzxfwl b eaox gg gwulgqidjnso mmqyjjijjnq ppws nzf
Uefladuf xbsmyjt; lwhujecfh nzf fgoa, dfuf Oufuoulylfl, ojnz ick
oifeykdlaqn hsinjhujudjmet, uk b mgsn gg mwb-jwbmson. Tvn oiyjf nzjm
kvjwscgsclz cf ubw Fhymcki qzbfwnyf eiwt lwbfdz wgomatn, au qgvfv cy
