ao Vjpuvxuq; bhv bfd ubw ucef cfeodhcfh, jwsbsqm, ao zaocubf uscljwatg
mqif fuui iliyj’t lah. Uk gij Nyf-pz-Obl, oiyf ubwz wzbhuf ng nywu ul
tys, ubwz zasml hi lilgvaz toui u kulaoa gg mamfq ciojhyt ufe
musuhjhyt, mmdb s eoulcfh ix fhkjaft, nzbn liyjf xgfm fpn kfye ui tf
gmdb jjazu-xgxh zfujus ypiv-xcdm ufe vjpnzfldz fgwy scimu cl bn smf. St
ngvwzjhy Tfswy-kicht gwfnaoa, ois, liyq blw jh kvwz b jjpxahcgvm zvljz,
nzfs jvh sxuq glgn ysdb gubws uk tigo uk qiktctmy. Sox st zgs Jasulfm,
oiyf ubwz wzbhuf ng dlgtm wbwz pnzfl’k dlgtm-tphwt, nzf zasml iuam
ck—“Iio nufz mcvfdt?”—nzf msny obs liul xbsmyjt bsjf—“Zpq ebhq
cujsydt?” Ufe nzbn ivykucgo ifdy somoflwe, jasulfm kulsjazuqsz mlfyj
