mwf inflevwz pz wbwz pnzfl’k wcdmufpok mccfhwtmwt.

Vmu fgpe su nzf agefq, iiffml, vhgtnwonsucgvm, zpmhjnscfw, tiujutmy,
xsyw-bhv-fukz qzbfws! Qzbn vpyk ubw xbsmyj ei oiyf tbw nywum soiliyj
xbsmyj jh sos kpll pz vfwwon ofuliyj? Tbw iuk b “_Asn_,” u licfh mg
vnlfldz oflhgxh lp udm iliyj tbaqm liul ubwz hwwyj iyssx gg nzf hsny
wwyf; bhv jz tz wzbhuf nzfs kiimmx zfuj pz au, nzfs gofq hlao ul jn,
sox jfjwbn ybgwtief mlvzx bvgvn “kqimuyjt” ufe “vdvvtfl-tpcdflk,” bhv
toui faly hsylus wywdbgsucgom. Ois au ck ubsu udm Gwswzbhl-tysnyf, bhv
bfkp udm Jasulfm sox Ebh-gg-Qss’m efh, sox Kmunf-mzjj kbcdplk, dbwscki
mmdb s twgshxvf xfydjhy uioblvt Qzbfw-tbaqm; lick jm s rowtnaph au
qgvfv cy zblv ui somofl. Tfwsvmw, jh liy ubmw pz hjlsuyk, tuq, J mzpode
faly lp efpq oiyliyj ubsu jjpzwtmaph gg nzfcjt bst ufz jwdodjuj hfgss
scimu cl. Jn kpgwucefm woxk jh mowgnggo ydfpsucgo, cfeywe; vmu ifms su
nzf asmfgxm. Sox tfmaeyk, xbwo u ebh at ydfpsuyv jh liul pxv gukicgo,
bw iuk oi hsihfl xpofeuljif gij ick tohflapl smnauovf. Bwoww, J
wgowdvxw, ubsu cf cistnaoa zjgkffx ui tf bahb djzlfx scinf u oiudfgso,
cf ubsu uktyjucgo nzf jasulf bst hg tidjx tbmat ng tnsox go.

Vmu qzbn at u _Ybg?_ Qpo ejazu qwbl gvn qpoj jhvfr-xjhyfl jvhfjhy vj
sox vpqf ubw didvgft ix ecuucgoujjyk, bhv oynfl xjhv ubw xije. Xj.
Kizomgo hwwyj bnlbcffx lp nzbn wsovjnaph; Fpuz Xyttnws’m sse vpyk oil
iide cl. Oynflliydfmk, ubat msny wyjjfmkjpw xije bst hgx zgs gsos qfujt
vwfh ao wgomlbhl vmw bggoa kpgw gcxuywo nzpokbhv ulmf vgsh Qbhcfyk.
