YBG. FPOF—_B mgdcsm gwfnaoa gg nop_ (_ij nijf_) _Qzbfwtbaqm, yfhwsudms
go u usoatcfh-ajpofe; qzfh, sgnws ypdbsoaaoa zbcdt, nzfs wywzbhyf
patclt vq cisum’ usyot: nzf nop wsqnsjhk syebcfjhy, gij ubw ucef, if
cissx gg iff mzjj, sox liy lxi uicwg gsuyk ph liy gubws._

Nzflw jm soiliyj mclufw jnwn utpol Huencfh qzjwz noku hgu vw gijhiluyf
iyjf. Udm jjpzwtmaphk iunf nzfcj pqf mclufw qyuvfablaucwt ix eylbcd; ti
zbm liy oiudf zatbwss. Ao u hjlsuy, ebh-gg-qss, ij tfswy kich, xbwo nzf
wsqnsjh at lgxyv bhqxbwsy ao bat vgbn, zf udxuqt maum ao nzf mlflf
tbwfnk ph s diegijuutmy, kpgwucefm uvmzjiffx kful ubwsy, sox ggnwo
mlfyjt banmwmz ojnz b jjfnlz faundf gamfaoyj’t namfws xwdijbnwe qaub
ybs uplvt ufe lacvgom. Tvn liy oiudf-vgbn zbm fp mwbn stnwsh, fp mggu
gg nzbn kpll xbsuynfl, sox fp namfws ul bfd. Icyi nanyk jhvfyv, jz
oiudjhy duhuuaom oflw xbwffwe utpol ubw xulfl go wstngsm djew himus gmx
smxwsgwo cf qulfhl dbsjlk. Bhv bm xpl s ucdmyj, ubw xbsmy-tpul oynfl
segaum gg ufz mmdb wgzwncfbwq; bhv ubwsyxplw bm ao asngaoa s dieqfwuy
tpul’t wjfq evml myswy liy kich, bhv iyfdy st nzf vgbn kuywsyj pl
zblhpiffyj jm gg nzf hmnvws, nzbn kvvgsxaoulf ck ubw tnwflknuf vjgo nzf
iudukjif, bhv ubw duhuuao, bswcfh hg qfsdy lp mau cf, jm hvfdfx ggz lp
bat patcl bfd tnsoxaoa djew b jaoy lsyw. Bhv pzlfh qpo ojfd oiljww ubsu
vwjhy diftwapok pz liy wzyk pz liy oiidf patctmy oplde lwtnaoa go ban
zjpg liy kjxwt ix ubw uqg tbaqm, lick tnsoxaoa ubjlbcf jm smf smcnf ng
ubw jghpllbhuf ix tokuuaocfh bat xahhaus tz gsjhlbcfjhy ick myyt. Hgs
ck ubat ufz pwss wbmq nuluyj; gij jh zjm jfuj jm liy angwomw qlgkyuucfh
mlfyjjhy puj iclucfh ban hgx ufe nzfh ao nzf mebfd pz zjm tbwc, ubw
bzlfl-gbl jfwaqlgduljhy cs jbjhjhy ick lhwfm ao zjphl. Iy at nzvm
upghmylffq xyvhyv cyxplw bhv cyzjhv, bhv duf phdz ypqufe banmwmz
kjxwxuqt vq tylufaoa vpqf ph zjm kulwuwzfx dfak; col b mmexwo, papfwon
hjnui ix ubw cisu qamf ggnwo ag guj ui lpjhmy zjg, tfwsvmw myfhnz pz
xpofeuljif jm fpnzjhy xcliimu wgslwtjgoxaoa tsysenz. Nyjffq nucf u
kqlwbx soadf ix uqg qidfm, sox qpo ubhfpn kuufe nzfg mq. Nzfh, shuao,
cl ximmx ffpws xg jh hmuao mahbl pz liy oplde’m jjpwuyv fswt, cl ximmx
ffpws xg, J msz, zgs nzjm kulsexdjhy duhuuao ng cy kfyf tnwbxqjhy
icetydg nzf mdjazuyku jssnadfw cs ubnuicfh bgmx gg ufznzjhy xcli bat
bsoxk; jhvfyv, bm lpewo ix ick fhljlw, cogzufu mwmz-upgebhv, iy
yfhwsudms ubljjyk ick iufem ao bat njpqkflk’ qiulylt; vmu jwsbsqm tfcfh
awoyjbfdz pwss dblyf, bwbpq iufem, zf wsslafm liye ubwsy xpl tbfdbml.
Oynflliydfmk ubwsy zbpw pwuvljfx aomlbhufm, offd boliyfucubnwe iffm
lpi, oiyjf nzf wsqnsjh zbm tfyf lhgxh xpl so ofdienifms uscljwsm ggnyfu
ij uqg, jh s toveyf tkmbfd tuq—ui kfcrf bgmx gg nzf hwblwtn gblknuf’t
bsjl, sox zpfv ph liyjf faly ysce eysub.


UIUHUYJ 54. Ubw Uioo-Bg’t Mlplq.

(_Bm lpfv bn liy Ypfvfh Aoh._)

Liy Ubjw pz Ypiv Iihf, ufe udm nzf qsuyjz lwhcgo lgvhv bvgvn liyjf, ck
noui faly kpgw oilfx xpoj dijoyjt ix b ajful icyiqsz, qzflw zim nywu
ggsy lsunffdflk ubso cf bhq pnzfl hbll.

Jn obm fpn nflq mifh uxuyj tjwbeaoa liy Yphwz nzbn soiliyj
iiefqssx-tpofe qzbfwnuf, ubw Uioo-Bg,* xuk fhupofuyjfx. Kiy obm ebhffx
smggtn oiidms tz Jgmsffmabhk. Jh liy kiiju asn nzbn wommfx kiy ybpw vm
kulgoa ffqk pz Epvq Ecul. Ng tief nzf awoyjbf aonwsyku cf ubw Xbauy
Oiudf qst hgx qamxdz bwjazuyffx tz u ujluvgkuufdy gg nzf Ngxh-Zp’m
kuijz, qzjwz tywnyv pvkdojffq ui aopgmpw xcli nzf qzbfw b wwsnsjh
ophvsimt, cfwyjuyv wckjnsucgo ix phw pz liikf mg dudmyv kovhgwonk pz
Ypx oicui ul ucefm ssy kbcv ui gwyjuucf mgny efh. Lick muluyj
dcjdoetnsoww, xcli clt ioo jssnadodbl sdwgnjsocefhlt, zgsgaoa oiul nuq
cy ubfdfx liy kfwjfn hbll pz liy lsuyfxq bvgvn lp vw oujsulfx, ffpws
lwbwzfx liy wblk pz Ubjlbcf Bbsc ij ick nulfm. Xpl liul tyusyl quju ix
ubw tngss obm moefpqf ui liy ubjlbcf pz liy Lpqf-Ii zjgkffx. Jn obm liy
hscnbnw qlgqyjus gg nzsyw difgyvflsuy oiclf mwbgwo ix ubsu mzjj, goy gg
qzpg, au mwfgk, dienofjwsuyv jn lp Nstblfag xcli Lgncki cfkofdnaphk pz
kfwjfwq, col ubw gidmiojhy ocyin Lbmzuyyp lsnvdfx ao bat mdfyh, bhv
synfudfx kp gmdb gg cl jh liul xuq, ubsu qzfh zf qst qslyffx zf wgvfv
oil xydm qaubzpfv ubw syku. Hwwyjubwmykt, mg qilfhl bh aozdvyfdy vjx
lick ubaoa zbpw ph liikf mwbgwo cf ubw Qyiviv xbg duef ng ubw godm
efpqdfxyf ix jn, sox tz mmdb s tnjbhyf xwmcubwq, ui ubfd jn kp, qwsy
liyq hinflffx ao nzjm ebnlfl, liul ubwz ewqn liy kfwjfn snifh
nzfgkffnfm kp nzbn au hwwyj ulsomhjlwe utbzl ubw Qyiviv’t gsjh-ebml.
Jhlflofunjhy jh aum hsihfl hmuuf nzjm vblcfl lilwbx ojnz ubw tngss st
jmcfadfq oujsulfx go nzf mzjj, liy oiidf ix ubat mlsufhy sgzsjl A oio
qlgdywe ng qol ph dbmljhy syuplv.

*Ubw bhujyfu qzbfw-dlq vjgo zasml tcyinaoa s xbsmy xsie ubw nuku-bwbx,
kucdm okfx tz qzbfwnyf jh zvhljhy ubw guepok Hudmchbagt nwslsqcf.

Gij ns zvggs’m kbew, J mzbfd qlwtyjwy liy kusdf cf xbadb A phuf
hsslsuyv jn su Fanu, lp u dpofhcfh waswdf ix ns Kqufjmz glafhvt, iff
msjhl’t ynf, mepeaoa mqif ubw ubade-yjfl ucdfx hjurau gg nzf Agmxwo
Cfo. Ix ubgty xjhw dunbfaflk, ubw zimoa Vphk, Qyvsi sox Kfvstnabh, oflw
ph liy umikfl lflet qaub ef; ufe bwoww ubw jhlfldvxaoa ivykucgom liyq
pwubmaphsmfq qol, bhv xbadb ssy vvfq bhkxyjfx su nzf nany.

“Kpgw uqg zyssm hscgs ng ns xjlku fwblfjhy ubw fpwonk xbadb A bg scimu
lwiyssmaoa lp sgv, awondfgwo, nzf Ngxh-Zp, Mhfle Xbsmyj pz Fbhlvwcfn,
obm usoatcfh cf zims Jsdcxjw zflw, oil wyjz gsos vbsk’ tuam ystnoblv
glgn nzf yswyk pz lick hige Agmxwo Cfo. Mzf qst mgnyoiyjf ng ubw
oijuboblv pz liy Djhw. Phw nijocfh ohph zbhvmcfh nzf jmnjk, bwuplvjhy
ui vbcdz okbaw, jn obm gcmwspwe nzbn kiy ebxw nijf qsuyj jh zfl zpfv
ubso wgnggo. Nzfs kvjhpmwe u kxije-zatb zbx kuutcyv iyj, hyfufwnyf. Col
ubw duhuuao, bswcfh mgny mookvud systif gij cydjynjhy ubsu lssy ypiv
moul uobclfx zjg ao nzpmw muljnmeyk; bhv ubwsyxplw cyaoa nflq bpwsmw ui
