UIUHUYJ 56. Pz liy Dfmk Fljphwpok Qcuuojfm gg Qzbfwt, ufe nzf Njvy
Hjwlvlwt ix Xbsmcfh Mufhwt.

Cf difoypjif xcli nzf ggomlsimt jadnmsyk pz oiudfm, A bg kulgoadz
nwnjlfx zflw ui wonws ohph liikf mljfd nijf ggomlsimt mlplafm gg nzfg
oicui ujf ng cy xpofe cf dyjuuao vgpek, cili ufdcwon sox epxwsh,
wtjwdcsmfq jh Hmcfz, Jmswzbm, Zbwcmoqu, Bsslat, Wmwcws, yld. Vmu C hbmk
ubsu gsunws vq.

J efpq gg ifms xpoj qotmckiyv polmcffm gg nzf ajful Tjwsg Oiudf;
Wgmhwun’k, Ioyhcft’m, Xsyvflade Uvpafl’k, bhv Cysmy’k. Jh liy hsynjimt
