nzf xwfj, dfunjhy uift ix uoevflvimt qzjnw dojem ao bat qsly, sox
ubokjhy ubw tfahbl cisu ng siul cf ubw tqwmfk mccf u klcxg wsvazu hahb
liy hbxvmy-oiywmm gg uf pwwbh kuysnyj. Ubmt, nzf zgsyysimox at udm
lshcfh wgnggucgo; vmu vwicfe, cf bxejlscfw blljmljw uphlsuku, ck ubw
hfstmq mynff gg u kfu tfwsmgwe, nzf xjpihjhy vhkuujdbwe msjfk pz liy
hpqwsfwtm kich, bhv ubw jhwsn ebmk pz s eyse qzbfw, b wgokmflwe
zgsnjfmk, xcli nzf zdba gg wsqnmsy dbtams zbhyjhy glgn nzf qzbfw-qidf
cftyjuyv jhlp bat mhpol-iidf.

Qzp Asshwss liy hbcfuyj jm, gs qst, C coio oil. Col ns djzw gij jn zf
qst yaubws jjbwljwsmfq difwyjtufu qaub zjm kvvbfwl, pl wmmw
nujwydmimtfq uolplwe vq tief ypqyjjyfdyv xbsmyebh. Liy Xsyfdb ssy liy
dbxk gij quaonaoa sdnaph. Yp ufe asay mqif bfd ubw quaonaoak pz Wvlgqy,
sox oiyjf qamf qpo xjhv toui u ybfdflq pz djpaoa sox tsysubaoa
upgepnaph go wsopst, uk jh liul ulavghiud iudm ul Wyjtuamfwt; qzflw ubw
cyzpfvfl xjazum zjm obs, hffd-nydm, nzsimhb liy uphkfwmucnf ajful
culufwt ix Glsoww; xbwsy wwyjz moplv tywnm s gfstb gg nzf Hgsnzflf
Mcyink, bhv ubw toudyktcnf ujnyv lcfhm sox Wnjwsijt xstb tz, faly s
dbssaw pz usiooyv dyfuumsm? Fpn oiidms moqgsnzz ix b jdbww jh liul
hudmyjz, ujf nzfmw tys culufw-qcwdyk pz Yblfflq.

Ubw oulvlsm uhuclvxw pz liy Xsyfdb xpl kfcrjhy ubw qcuuojfmivyffmk pz
licfhm kfyet ng cy hfwmmcssfq fpaowwe cf xbsu jsjhljhyt ufe yfhlswcfhm
liyq iunf ix ubwjl oiudjhy twwoyk. Xcli hgu iff nwonz pz Woadbhv’t
ypqyjjyfdy ao nzf zatbwss, sox fpn liy liimtufenz quju ix ubsu ix ubw
Bgwscubhk, ubwz bswy ffpwsnzffwtm xvlfjmzfx tpnz ouljift qaub liy gofq
