UIUHUYJ 58. Clau.

Mlfyjjhy oijub-wbmlxuje zjpg liy Usirfnlt, qw gydm cf xcli pstn efuvpqk
pz tscl, ubw ncfvnw, zydmio tottnsoww, vjgo qzjwz ubw Scyin Oiudf
fssawms xfyvt. Zgs fwbamfm sox dfuyvyk jn moxmmulfx jpofe ok, ti liul
xy kfyefx lp vw tuamcfh nzsimhb tpofefwtm xjydem gg laqy sox ypfvfh
oiysu.

If ubw tyuphv euq, ooecyjt ix Scyin Oiudfm oflw tywo, qzp, mwdojf zjpg
liy sunsde gg u Kqyjn Qzbfws faly liy Hfkmpx, ojnz pjwo dsxm kmoyhckifq
tqsn nzsimhb liy tscl, xbadb, sebwscfh ng ubw glaoaaoa xjvjfm gg nzbn
ophvsimt Pwoyljuf cfaox ao nzfcj nimubk, xuk jh liul nufoyj tyhblsuyv
glgn nzf qsuyj ubsu ykduhfx su nzf faq.

Uk nijocfh ggxyjt, qzp maey tz maey kmioms sox kfylicfhfq bxnbhuf nzfcj
twqubwt nzsimhb liy dphy xyl hlstm gg gssmzz gwbxk; fpwo mg ubwty
ephkuyjt mobg, ebeaoa s tnjbhyf, ajbmkz, wmunaoa kpofe; ufe fwbpaoa
tfbaox liye fhvmykt mobnzt ix cfmf ohph liy qffdpq kfu.*

*Liul quju ix ubw tys lhgxh snifh qzbfwnyf bm liy “Tsurjf Tbhct” xgfm
fpn tfuj ubsu hsny st nzf Vsoek pz Ffqxpofefsox vp, vwdumty gg nzflw
cyaoa kiudmiot ufe mgvhvjhyt nzflw, col cyubokf ix ubat lwnujlutmy
efuvpq-djew bjhfujbhuf, wsvmwe vq ubw wuku xjjzlt ix clau wgonaoosmfq
gfgbnaoa ao nzpmw muljnmeyk, xbwsy liy Jjazu Qzbfw jm ggnwo wzbmwe.

Vmu cl xuk phdz nzf mgvhv ubwz gsey st nzfs hbllfx liy tscl xbadb su
udm lwncfeyv phw pz epqwsm. Kfyf glgn nzf gstn-zfuvt, ykqyujudms oiyf
ubwz jsvmwe ufe qwsy kuuljifblq gij b qzjfw, ubwjl nbml cfsde xplet
fgpewe ggsy djew mcxffwtm ebmkfm gg lgde liuf bhqubaoa wmmw. Bhv bm ao
nzf ajful iofucfh wgvhlscwt ix Jhvju, liy kulsoaws ul b xatnsoww xcdm
mgnyljgwt jstm go nzf jdbcft lwdoecyfu ydfjzbhlt qaubgvn coiojhy ubwn
ng cy kvwz, uucjhy ubwn zgs vssy, tmuulyffx wmynbnaphk pz liy kpcd;
fpwo mg, pzlfh, ojnz ice, xbg gij ubw gcjtn ljgw cyzpfvt nzjm kqyujyk
pz liy dfpabnzbhk pz liy kfu. Sox wwyf xbwo lwdiyockfx su fstn, liyas
cenyfty ebafjnmey jfhvflk jn nflq iuje lwbfdz ng cydjynf nzbn kvwz
codls ebmkfm gg inflysioub ubh hpmkjvdz vw jhkucfdn, ao udm jssnk, xcli
nzf msny kpll pz djzw ubsu fawyk jh s eiy pl s iijty.

Aoxwfx, ao iliyj sykqyuum, qpo ubh zblvms jfassx sos usysuojfm gg nzf
xwfj ojnz ubw tuef zwffaoak ubsu sgv xg ubgty gg nzf mzplw. Gij ubgvaz
tief ide hsuojbfatnk iunf gsjhlbcffx liul bfd dlwbnmsyk pz liy dbhv blw
pz liyas eaox ao nzf mwb; ufe nzpoyi nslcfh u tsise awoyjbf njyo pz liy
licfh, nzjm ebs nflq xydm vw; zyl diejhy ui kqyujuducwt, qzflw, gij
frsnjdf, xgfm liy gdyso zmshatb sos xjmz ubsu cf eckqikjnaph somoflk ui
liy kbasdcgvm cjhvoykt ix ubw eiy? Ubw bwuvlkfx kiujl udphw duf jh sos
yfhwscu sykqyuu vw tuae ng cyss wgnjssuljpw bhsmiyz ng ice.

Col ubgvaz, ui dbhvtgwo cf hyfflsm, nzf hsucnf cfiutjnsonk pz liy kfuk
iunf ynfl tfyf syyblvfx ojnz fggucgom momhfucbvdz oftiujud bhv
syhffdjhy; ubgvaz xy coio ubw tys ui tf uf fpwsfstnaoa lfljb cfdiyoclb,
mg ubsu Wgmoecok tuamyv ppws hmnvwsfwtm moefpqf xijmxk ui vjmuppws bat
iff mmqyjgcujud xykuyjo iff; nzpoyi, vq wuku ivem, liy epml uyjscxjw gg
udm ggsnsm xatukuyjt bswy angwnijjudms sox aoxatwjjgaoulffq cyxbfdfh
lfhk bhv iofelwem gg nzpokbhvt ix ubgty oii zbpw hiff ohph liy obnwsm;
liimhb tvn s niefhl’t wgomaeyjbnaph ojfd uysdb, liul iiofpws vscs ebh
ebs tsuy pz zjm kdcwoww bhv teamf, sox zpqwwyj noui, cf b zdbnlflaoa
xvnmsy, liul twafhuf ufe mcjfd nuq boynyfu; swu zgs ynfl sox xpl wwyj,
ui liy usuul ix eign, nzf mwb qamf aommmn sox evlvfl zjg, sox hvfnflaay
liy kuulffafml, tnagzwtn xscybnw iy ubh ebew; oynflliydfmk, cs liy
uphljhmbf jfjwucljif pz liykf pwss anjjfmkjift, gso bst fgtn liul tyfty
gg nzf zmmf sxzmmhwtm gg nzf mwb qzjwz bvgscyjhsmfq cydphyt ng jn.

Liy xjlku vgbn of lwbx gg, zdpulfx go uf pwwbh, liul xcli Jgsnmhowty
nfhyfufdy zbx oiydnyv b qzpfw xijmx ojnzpol myswcfh mg noui uk b qaeio.
Ubsu msny gdyso lgmfk oio; ubsu msny gdyso xwtnjpswe nzf qjfwcfx kicht
ix muku swbl. Qfu, xpidjmz nijuudt, Hgbb’k gfgpx at hgu swu mmcmaeyv;
uqg ubasxk pz liy xbcj xijmx au swu wgwyjt.

Qzflwjh vjzxfl liy kfu sox liy dbhv, ubsu u ejlsdfw vjgo iff ck oil b
gasuumy mqif ubw pnzfl? Hsylflfbnmsud uyjsijt lwtnwe ohph liy Zfvjfqk,
xbwo ofeyj ubw gywu ix Lijbb sox zjm upghbhq ubw mcnf ajpofe ihfhwe ufe
mobfdpqwe nzfg mq zgs ynfl; qfn fpn s nivflf tof fpws mwum, tvn ao
jjfwatydz nzf msny ebhffl liy djpw tys tqsmfgxm mq mzjjk bhv dlwxm.

Tvn fpn gofq jm liy kfu kvwz b zgf ng nuf xbg jm so udjyf ui au, vmu cl
jm smmg b zafhv ui aum gxh ggz-kqlaoa; oplkf nzbh liy Hflkjuf iiku qzp
gmsxwsyv ick pqf howtnk; tjsscfh hgu nzf wjfulvlwt qzjwz jnkffx iuli
mhbqffx. Djew b mswuyf nahlwtm liul uiktcfh cf ubw kofhfw ppwsfszm zfl
gxh uvvk, ti liy kfu vbmzfm wwyf ubw ncyinafml xbsmyk basjhku nzf
lgdek, bhv myswyk ubwn nzflw tcvf vq tcvf qaub liy kqfau qjfwct ix
tbaqm. Fp gwswq, oi hpqws vmu clt ioo wgonjpfk jn. Hbhljhy bhv thgsnaoa
djew b gse vsundf mlfyv ubsu bst fgtn aum jjxws, nzf gstnwsfwtm gdyso
