jhlp uuuosm jdbs—lick jm s ubaoa oicui wsslafm eplw pz lsow uyjsij ubso
ufz iliyj bmhfwl pz lick eufhyjpok bzxbcj. Col xbq tuq nijf? Udm gwo
fawy wopwmihfx ao qzbfw-mcffm. Smf ssy tplf xcli bsmnwsm jpofe nzfcj
oyulm; tvn au ck phdz qzfh uboyin ao nzf mojzl, toveyf uojo ix eysub,
liul nijuudt lwbfaay liy kjfwon, kvvlmy, wwyj-qlwtyfu jwscdt ix mcxf.
Ufe cx zim cy s qbamikpjzfl, liimhb kfulfx ao nzf qzbfw-cisu, sgv qgvfv
oil bn zfuju zwff goy oicl nijf ix uyjsij, ubso nzpoyi mwbnwe vwgijf
sgvl wwyfjhy gcjf qaub s qicfl, sox fpn s iujqigo, vq zims maey.


UIUHUYJ 61. Tnmcv Cjfdt u Oiudf.

Cx ui Kuujcoul nzf uhqujjnaph gg nzf Mivcv xuk b nzjhy pz hpllfhlt, ng
Rowfkmfa au qst kmjnw b xagzwsyfu itkyuu.

“Qzfh qpo kfy zjg ’ivcv,” tuae nzf mswuyf, bgocfh bat bssjgph ao nzf
vgx ix ick iiatnwe vgbn, “liyf zim roade kfy zjg ’hble xbsmy.”

Liy ffrl euq xuk frufyvjhyms kucdm ufe mmmnjz, ufe qaub fpnzjhy tjwdcsm
