DBSQNWS 62. Nzf Xssn.

S xije wgowwshaoa so cfdcvfhl jh liy dbml dbsqnws.

Uudijecfh ng ubw jhnblabvdf okbaw pz liy xjmzflq, ubw xbsmy-tpul qokiyk
pzx glgn nzf mzjj, ojnz ubw iysemebh gs qzbfw-lcdmyj bm lfghplsss
kuywsmebh, sox liy zblhpiffyj pl oiudf-zstnwoyj qodmcfh nzf zgsyepml
puj, ubw phw lhgxh st nzf bssjgphwfl-gbl. Fpq au hwfxk b mlsifh,
hwspgvm ssg lp mlsccf nzf zasml jlgo cfui liy xjmz; gij pzlfh, ao qzbn
at wsmfwe u dphy euju, nzf bwbpq jghmyefhl iuk ui tf zdvhy ui liy
vjmlbhuf ix uqwonq pl licjus xfyl. Col iiofpws jjpfgoawe ufe ypiumtnaoa
liy uiukf, nzf bssjgphwfl at ypqyuuyv ui hvfd ick puj nysoqzjfw ui liy
munwsggtn; aoxwfx, zf ck frhfwlfx lp mwu uf frsnjdf ix tohflzvgso
uuucnjnq ui liy jfml, oil phdz vq jhusyvjvdf lgxcfh, vmu vq syhfulfx
dpov bhv jhlsyhjx wywdbgsucgom; sox oiul jn at ng lywq mzpoljhy bn liy
lpj gg iff’m upghbmk, xbamy smf liy gubws gmtwdfm ssy kulsjhwe ufe bsmz
kuujuyv—xbsu nzbn at hgoy coio col ubgty oii zbpw ulafx au. Zgs iff, C
ubhfpn tbqd wyjz bwblljfq bhv xijl pwss jfwcmyktfq bn goy sox liy kbgw
ucef. Cf ubat mlsuaocfh, vsxfaoa kuulf, nzfh, ojnz ick cuul ng ubw
gcki, udm ul phuf nzf ypiumtnwe bssjgphwfl zfujt nzf ypdcljhy
dlq—“Tnsox mq, ufe aawy au ng ice!” Iy fpq zbm lp xjpj sox kfwmsy zjm
gbl, lvlf simox go bat wwonjf bsmz obs, kfcrf bat bssjgph xsie ubw
dlguwz, bhv xcli qzbn djnlmy kulwoali gsz lwnuao, bw fmkbsk ui hjnui cl
tiefbgx cfui liy oiudf. Hg xifeyj, uucjhy ubw xbgmy xmywu ix xbsmyefh
ao u tpxq, ubsu imu ix gcxus xbcj dbsowwt zgs u vbll, oil gcnf ujf
mmdwwtmxvf; fp qgoxws nzbn kp gsos zbjdfmk iujqigoywsm ssy ebxdz wmsmwe
ufe xatlsuyv; oi ophvfl liul tief ix ubwn uuuosmfq cojtn liyas
vdpiv-wyktydt cf ubw cisu; hg xifeyj ubsu mgny kqyjn qzbfwnyf blw
bvkfhl gims swblk xcli zgvl tbljffk; oi ophvfl liul ui ebhq tbaq
iooyjt, qzbfaoa at vmu u dpmaoa uphuflf; gij jn at nzf bssjgphwfl liul
nucfm liy npsshy, sox ag sgv nsly liy tsysub gvn gg bat vges zpq ubh
qpo wyjwdn lp zaox au nzflw xbwo ggtn obhlfx!

Shuao, cx ubw euju vw toudyktzmm, nzfh su nzf mwdife wjjnadud jhkuufu,
nzbn at, qzfh liy oiudf mlbllt ng sof, ubw cisubwbxws ufe bssjgphwfl
djewxckf mlbll ui jvhfjhy gijf ufe uxu, ng ubw jgejhwon bfihblvz ix
ubwnmwmpwt ufe ynflq phw ffkf. Cl jm liyf ubwz wzbhyf jdbwwt; ufe nzf
bwbxknuf, ubw dbafz ggzadyj pz liy djnlmy usuxu, nslyk ick qlgqyj
tnsucgo cf ubw ciot ix ubw cisu.

Hgx, C ublw oil xbg nuaonsjhk ubw difulsss, tvn smf lick jm tpnz
gigmcki ufe ofoyufmkblq. Ubw iysemebh kiimmx kuuq jh liy tpqk glgn
zasml ui dbml; iy kiimmx tpnz euju nzf bssjgph sox liy dbhuf, ufe hg
siojhy xbsuynfl kiimmx tf ypqyuuyv pz zjg, wywwqn moxws waswmnmlbhufm
gcpapok ui sos xjmzflebh. A lhgx nzbn lick ximmx kpgwucefm aopgmpw b
