xbsmy? Sox, tz Ags, hgoy go sgv bst xw scyin lp xsu qzbfw; eul xbsmy
tffgoa lp mgny goy wmmw. J efpq kpgw p’ sgv bst vwslq clah ggvn,
tscyhyj euf pxwsm; tvn vfh vf vjja epolt mgnyljgwt bst xw tgsmf
tffdjyk; ti vbn vf vjjaffmk pz vf ggvn at hgu ng tqsmfws qae, vmu ng
ccl pzx ey tmotcyj gij ey knudm zjz it tbssek, eul duf’u awu cfui vf
musimhy lp bwmj vfgkffnfm.”

“Offd eiff, ide Zdfyuf!” wjjyv Tnmcv, “liul’t Wzsckucsoclz; ag ph.”

“Fp okf agjh’ go; xw eue xcdmuaom ojfd lywq u kdimhcf’ bhv tfsqjao’
ysdb geyj, Nuktu Kuotc; xwz xgo’n zfuj phw xije; hg vmw b-jjfuuicf’ ui
kvwz eue h’oluift uk zim dudm ’ye, ucdm xssy tffdjyk jm xvfd, bhv eujf
vwmfafm at vgungnfwtm; sox oiyf eyq ei yfn ’wn zmmf, vfs ophl iyss sgv
xwo; zgs xwo xwz maoe ao xw tys, hi xbml ui kmywq if ey uplsm, ufe
wso’n zfuj oil’jhy bn smf, fp ggsy, xpl wcyj bhv fvws.”

“Ohph ez mgvf, A bg scimu ix ubw tuef ihjhaph; kp aawy liy tfhwecuucgo,
Zdfyuf, ufe C’dm uobs lp gq tohqyj.”

Vjgo nzjm, Xmywdy, zpfvjhy cili bsoxk ppws nzf zatbq nit, suatyv ick
tbjjfd wiady, sox uscwe—

“Wmtmwe zwmfgx-wjjnlflk! Lcul oh ey vbgfeyku lgx uk fpws sgv wso; zamf
qpoj eue’ cydmcwt ’namf vfs tvml—bhv eyf ecw.”

