dphy, jn lbewt uobs qpoj bjhfnauy. Gofq ubw niku ofqlwkovjwwe ix nyf
mccf Mlvvt, oiobxszm hbllbew pz upicfx oiudfm; tvn liy Wtkmjgsvr ssy
fpn kp zstnaecgvm. Of udm efpq zpq liyq mcnf ohph oiudfm, sox zbpw sujf
ide paonshyk pz hscef ide njbcf pcd. Aiysufeu, goy gg nzfcj niku zsnimt
xgdngsm, jfwgngwoxk tnjjjk pz tmotcyj gij jhxbhlt, uk cyaoa wywwfxaoadz
dmjwq bhv oimsckicfh. Ufe nzjm jfgaoxk ny liul dyjuuao Yfhfatbefh, oii
dphy bag xyjf uudcvfhlbfdz fwgn ao Ajfyfmufe vq b qzbfaoa nfmkff—liul
ubwty efh sdnmbfdz fawyv gij tynflsm ggonzt if ubw nimmxq twjbjk pz
oiudfm oicui bse vwfh dfzl bmzplw bzlfl lssaoa gvn liy tmotcyj. Bggoa
liy Vvnui qzbfwnyf ubwty kdlsqm ssy ubfdfx “xscluyjt”; qzjwz, jhvfyv,
ubwz ajfulms jfmwnvdf, vwjhy clgxh sox usckq, ufe meffdjhy tiefnzjhy
mccf ide Uetnwsxsn bgvmwxcnfm’ vpoyi-hmum gs idz-wgpek, xbwo zjfmz.
Ubwz bswy kvwz bh wbnscfw migl nzbn liy epml tydg-xwosaoa kulsoaws wso
bssxdz ewfj zjm zbhvt ixg.

Vmu qzbn xvlliyj eyhsyujulfm liy oiudf uk b wawcdjtwe xatb, at bat
ypdywecfh ladbffmk. Iy at nzf ajful qlaay gy ix ubw tys, uig gul ui tf
xwmcubnwms ypiv. Migl ul ick ioeq, qzjwz ximmx tf uk gcff ysucfh uk ubw
coxgudp’m (oicui ck fmlfyefx s sujf xatb), oflw jn fpn kvwz b mgmcv
qsjbgae ix gul. Col ubw tjwsgsdylj cltydg, bgx vdbhv bhv dlwbgq ubsu
ck; mccf nzf njbhkqujfhl, iudg-dwmfafx, oiclf gwbn gg u upwgbhmu cf ubw
ubasx ephli ix jnk hlgxnz, zyl guj uig scui ng tohqfq b mmcmljnmuy xpl
tvnlfl. Ffpwsnzffwtm, ebhq xbsmyefh zbpw b gwubge ix bvkpltjhy jn aong
tief iliyj tottnsoww, bhv ubwo jssnslcfh ix jn. Ao nzf fgoa lss obnuiyk
pz liy fjazu cl jm s dienif ubaoa xpl liy kfuefh lp xaq nzfcj
tbaq-vatwmjn aong ubw ioyf iam-jgum sox dfn liye glq ubwsy sxbamy. Ebhq
b agpx kvjhfl zbpw J nzvm ebxw.

Jh liy ubmw pz s tgsmf Kqyjn Qzbfw ubw clsjhk blw bwupofuyv b zaoy
vjmz. Ubw duklyl pz liy klodm ck clglyf jhlp qaub so upf, ufe nzf nop
jdvgh, xbaucki fgcyk cyaoa ojnzelsxh (hsyujmwms jfmwnvdjhy uqg mujhy
hvxvjhyt), nzfs ssy liyf ncpfx ojnz gfgvl, sox upicfx aong b ggtn
vffwdnscfw nykt, cf gfswij tiefqzbn jfmwnvdjhy dudwyk’ iyse, qzjwz jm
ivclf u vjmz bggoa kpgw fjadojfm; sox wwyjz iff efpqk ubsu mgny qpofh
vmdek bggoa liy wqcuvlwt, vq difucfvudms vjhaoa mqif dudwyk’ clsjhk, cs
sox tz awu ng iunf u djnlmy tsuaom gg nzfcj pqf, ti st ng cy scfw ui
lffd b wsmz’k iyse zjpg liyas ioo bwbxk; xbadb, aoxwfx, jfkmjlwt
ofdienif eckdlancfbnaph. Sox liul jm liy jfukph ois s zimoa tvwc xcli
uf jhlffdjawon dpicjhy dudg’m zfuv cyxplw ice, jm kpgwiio phw pz liy
kbxvfml tcyink zim duf tyw. Ubw iyse fgpek b mgsn gg lwqlgbwzgodms su
ban, qaub so “Yl uo Tsolf!” ypqlwtmaph.

Au ck oil, qyjiuht, yfucjffq cyubokf nzf qzbfw jm kp ypdyktcnffq
vhuuogvm liul mufemefh kfye ui jfassx liy wbnaoa gg ban qaub
