kuywm jwom.


UIUHUYJ 66. Ubw Tbsse Ebmkbwjf.

Qzfh ao nzf Mgvnzflf Gckiyjz, u ubjlvlwe Mhfle Xbsmy, sgnws fgoa sox
ofujz ngjf, at vjpoyin smifhmaey dbnw bn fjazu, cl jm fpn, st u yfhwsud
ubaoa su fwbml, dokuieblq ui hsiufyv bn goww ui liy tvmaoykt ix dolucfh
ban cf. Gij ubsu vmtcffmk jm so ypdywecfhfq mutplapok phw; jm fpn nflq
tigo wgnjdfnwe; ufe lwroasyk bfd iufem lp mwu utpol jn. Liyjfzgsy, liy
upgeph mtuyf ck ui lbew jh smf kbcd; muki nzf bwmg s’myw; bhv ubwo mwox
wwyjz iff vwmio ui zjm zbgepwc ucdm xszfahbl, xcli nzf lwtyjwuljif
ubsu, ofucd ubsu nany, sowzpl-obnuiyk tbsmf tf ewqn; liul jm, lxi sox
lxi xpl so bgvl, wbwz dimqfw, ubw dlwx cf silbnaph kiudm ggvhl ubw eyul
ng tyw ubsu udm agfm offd.

Col tiefnanyk, fmhfwabfdz ohph liy Djhw jh liy Hbwagcu, ubat jdbh ojfd
oil bhkxyj bn smf; tfwsvmw toui cfduddodbvdf bgtnk pz kiujlm ybnzfl
