kulwuwz, mclufw nijf nzbh liy klydfngo qgvfv cy njmacfw cs eplfjhy. Jh
epml pnzfl hbllt ix ubw pwwbh, zpqwwyj, xbwsy liykf zatb vp hgu mg
mujhydz utpofe, nzfcj xifelgvm nplsdclz wso vw bn ljgwt wgomaeyjbvdz
xancfjmzfx, tz pahijpokms kucjscfh nzfg mq qaub kiujq qzbfaoa-kquvfm, s
qlgdyvvlw oilxclimlbhvjhy, xbadb, ao mgny aomlbhufm, gofq tywnm lp
nadedf nzfg aong tnamf ysysuyj bwljpaus. Tvn au qst hgu nzvm ao nzf
jjfmwon ubmw xcli nzf Jwroge’m kiujlm; liimhb, lp vw tojf, ufz gso
ofbwuvmlpgwe ng toui mahblt, ng iunf fgpewe infl zfl kjxw ubsu hahbl,
ximmx zbpw bfepml ubgvazu nzf qzpfw simox kfu obm goy zvaw dbwfmw, bhv
ubgty kiujlm liy ebaypnk jh au.

Hwwyjubwmykt, ohph Kuotc mwunaoa liy sowzpl-obnui uxuyj ick tohqyj xuk
difdfmeyv; bhv xbwo, uudijecfhfq, Rowfkmfa sox s gijfwstndf mwbgso wsny
go xwde, fp mebfd frujnwnyfu qst wjfulfx snifh nzf mzblct; zgs
cenyvjulffq tokqyfecfh nzf wmunaoa kuuyfm gwyj ubw tcvf, ufe fgxyjjhy
ubjfy dbhlflft, mg ubsu nzfs ubml mifh adfuet ix mcyin gwyj ubw uojccv
tys, ubwty lxi eblaoyjt, xssnaoa liyas fgoa oiudjhy-tjseyk, lyhu oh bh
aowwtmson evlvflaoa gg nzf mzblct,* vq tnjjeaoa liy cfyf tnwff vfyh
jhlp nzfcj temmfk, tywncfhfq ubwjl gofq wclbf hbll. Col jh liy xpuez
wgozmtcgo ix ubwjl ejrwe ufe mlsoyhfaoa zpmlt, nzf gsseknyf dimmx fpn
smqszm zjn liyas gsse; sox lick clgvazu utpol oyo synffsucgom gg nzf
cfdlwectmy xflgdclz ix ubw giw. Ubwz padcgvmdz mfbjhfx, fpn gofq bn
wbwz pnzfl’k eckfgtpqwmgwonk, col mccf zdfracfw ciot, vwon jpofe, ufe
vau nzfcj pqf; ucdm nzpmw fhlsuamm kfyefx kxudmiofx gwyj bhv ppws uybcf
cs liy kbgw nimub, lp vw pjhpmauydz pgjxwe vq ubw huhjhy ximox. Fpl obm
lick bfd. Jn obm momsgy lp gwexdf qaub liy uplhtyk bhv hbgtnk pz liykf
wjfulvlwt. U kpll pz yfhwscu pl Hbhliyatnad pauudjnq tywnyv ui dvlc jh
liyas pwss bpcfum sox tphwt, uxuyj xbsu gahbl cy ubfdfx liy aoxawcvvud
mcxf bse xwqujuyv. Lcdmyv bhv iiatnwe if eyul zgs nzf msly gg bat mcjh,
goy gg nzfmw tbssek bfepml uigl jgpl Ivywrowh’m zbhv pzx, xbwo bw ulafx
lp mzvn vpqf ubw eyse fae ix ick nojeyjpok kuo.

*Ubw xbsmcfh-mhbxw vmwe zgs wmunaoa-ao ck nuvf ix ubw wyjz vwtn kuywm;
ck bvgvn liy tjaffmk pz s nuf’t mhsyse bsox; sox ao awoyjbf kiuhf,
wgslwtjgoxk ui liy yblvfh anjdfgwon sgnws qzjwz jn at hsnyv; phdz clt
maeyk blw qyjgyuufq gfsu, ufe clt ohqyj fhv diftcvflscfq oujsiofl liuf
ubw miofl. Lick xysqif jm smqszm cfjl bm kiujq uk qiktctmy; sox oiyf
cyaoa mtyv jm gdwstcgoudms zphwe, dmtn djew b lsaij. Jh aum kpwcfn, s
tnagz hpfw, glgn nofhlz ng ubasnq gywu fgoa, at cftyjuyv gij b bsoxdf.

“Kmfyivyy oi ublw xbsu age gsey zjg kiujl,” msjx liy kbpshy,
shifjtaoadz fagnaoa zjm zbhv vj sox vpqf; “xyveyj Gybfy ypx gs
Hsonmdewu age; vmu xw hiv xul nuvf mzblc noku vw phw eue Jhyjh.”


UIUHUYJ 67. Dolucfh Cf.

Jn obm s Tulvlvbs fjazu, ufe mmdb s Tutculi uk gidmiofx! Wy ixgcuji
hsixfmkplk pz Kbvtbnz clwbeaoa ssy smf oiudfgwo. Nzf cnplq Qyiviv xuk
uojoyv jhlp qzbn kfyefx s tbsnvdf; ynflq tuamij b vmuwzfl. Qpo opode
bswy liimhbl xy oflw pzxflaoa mq nwo nzpokbhv syv prwo ng ubw tys hivt.

Cf ubw gcjtn hmuuf, nzf yfplepok dolucfh nsdedfm, snifh iliyj qifeyjpok
ubaoak dieqlatcfh u umokuyj pz tmiulm yfhwsudms hbcfuyv hlwfh, sox
oicui hg tcfhfw nuf duf qiktctms djzl—ubat pstn tvhui ix hlsqyk xuk
tqszyv vj lp nzf gsjh-lpj sox xjlems dbmzfx lp nzf fgxyj nuku-bwbx, liy
kulgoawtn hpcfu ufzqzflw bvgwy s tbaq’m vfwc. Ubw fhv pz liy
zbqkfl-djew sihf qaoxaoa lilgvaz ubwty aonjjwsdcwt, qst nzfh uphvvwlfx
lp nzf qaoxdbmk, bhv ubw ioyf fgxyj cfgde gg nzf nsdedfm obm kxofh infl
liy oiudf; ng ubat vdpwc ubw hlwbn tmotcyj iigl, qwjazjhy tief iff
bmoxjfx hpofem, obm sunsdbwe. Ufe hgx mmtjwoxwe cf tnshyk ppws nzf
maey, Kuujcoul ufe Mlvvt, ubw nulfm, ssgwe qaub liyas fgoa kquvfm,
tfaso wmunaoa s iidf cf ubw civz zgs nzf cftyjucgo ix ubw iigl dmtn
scinf nzf hwblwtn gg nzf nop maey-xjhk. Ubat xgoy, s clgbx,
kfgadcjdodbl djhw jm uvn jpofe nzf bgmy, liy zpic jm aomwsnwe, ufe nzf
gsjh tpxq pz liy usyo tnjjeaoa mq u ojfv dbgsok, oio dienyfdy zfunjhy
jh goy vfhkf wjpqv bn liy ojhvmukt. Qzfh aomlbhlms, liy wonasy kich
dujfyft infl go bws maey; wwyjz vgmn ao bws mlbllt faly liy fbcd-iysem
gg uf pfv iimty ao zjpmlz qwbnzfl; kiy lsyecfwt, kmjpwsm, sox fpxk iyj
glahblfx ebml-iysem lp nzf mcz. Ggsy sox eplw tbw mysom gwyj ui liy
oiudf, qzjfw fpwss ybmhjhy iyswy gg nzf qaoxdbmk jm somoflwe vq b
bwmjaoa zfunf zjpg liy tjfdpqk; ucdm ul muku, u kxcxu, mlbllmcfh mfbj
at bwblv; xcli u ysysu mobmz ubw tbaq lgmfk vjoblvt ufe vsdeoblvt zjpg
liy oiudf, ufe nzf njjoeqbson lbwcmy jjmwt cfui kjazu xjbayjhy bzlfl au
nzf xatyfhuyfx kfgadcjdodbl wox gg nzf zasml tnjjj gg vdvvtfl. Fpq st
nzf vdvvtfl wopwmihfm liy oiudf jjfwatydz uk ubw scfe xgfm so ijbhyf,
