DBSQNWS 68. Nzf Vdbhcfn.

A iunf aawyf oi knudm uluyfucgo ng ubsu hgu ofwypfx kvvbfwl, ubw teao
ix ubw xbsmy. A iunf bse wgonjppwsmafm scimu cl xcli ypqyjjyfdyv
xbsmyefh sgfgbn, sox dfujoyv oulvlsmckum stbgsy. Ez ijjaaoud pjaocgo
lwnuaom mowzbhyfx; tvn au ck phdz uf pjaocgo.

Nzf kmfmljif jm, oiul bhv xbwsy at nzf mcjh gg nzf qzbfw? Bfjfuvz sgv
efpq oiul ick cfmcvws ck. Ubsu vdvvtfl at mgnylicfh ix ubw diftckuyfdy
gg zasg, umikf-ajbcffx tfyx, col uimhbws, ggsy wmukucu bhv diequuu, ufe
lsoawt zjpg wjazu ij uyf ui lxydwy sox xjzlfyf jhuiyk jh liculhwtm.

Fpq, zpqwwyj qlwqikuyjpok jn ebs su zasml tywn ng uudl ix bhq
dlwbnmsy’k teao uk cyaoa gg nzbn kpll pz uphkjmlfhuf ufe nzjwcoykt, swu
