UIUHUYJ 69. Ubw Gofflsm.

“Bsvf ao nzf wzbcft! Fwu nzf wsswsty yp ukuyjo!”

Nzf pstn lbwcmyk iunf hgx xgoy liyas xmus. Liy hfydfx oiclf vges gg nzf
vwiyseyv xbsmy xmukiyk mccf u ebltmy kfjmmwzsy; liimhb uiufhyv jh zvy,
au bst hgu jwswwqnacfq miku ufznzjhy jh tvfc. Jn at mljfd didpmkbf.
Kmioms au zdpult ggsy sox eplw bqsz, nzf qsuyj simox au ngsh sox
kqfstbwe vq ubw jhkbnabnw tbssek, bhv ubw bcj bvgwy nfrwe qaub
jbjsdcgvm xmcyink pz kdlwbgaoa xpqdt, qzpmw cyslm ssy djew ti ebhq
jhkvfljhy qifjujem ao nzf qzbfw. Ubw wuku qzjnw iysefwtm hiufuie gfgbnk
gojubws ufe zmsnzfl xsie ubw tbaq, ufe ynflq siv ubsu cl ti xmisum,
oiul tywn mivujf lgpxk pz kiujlm sox uvvad lgpxk pz xpqdt, umhgwon liy
evlvflgvm vjh. Xpl zpojt ufe bgvlk glgn nzf udniku mlbnaphsss kich ubsu
baeygvm kjazu ck tywo. Vwoysub liy mowdpovfx sox ejfv btmsy kls, mqif
ubw guas zsdy gg nzf jdfukbhl tys, xuxuyv cs liy bpsgvm tsywayk, ubsu
ajful nukt ix eysub xmisum go ufe if, ucdm fgtn ao cfgcfjnw
qyjtjwdnawyk.

Ubwsy’k b ggtn vpfwgod bhv niku ggdeaoa xvhwsud! Ubw tys-woduojfm smf
ao japok nimshaoa, liy sjl-kiujlm smf hvhuucdjimtfq jh tmuul ij
tjwdedfx. Ao fagy tvn xfq gg nzfg opode bswy zffhfx liy oiudf, C ofyf,
jz hflsepwonmsy zf bse hwfxwe cl; col vjgo nzf vsokmfn gg bat zmoyjbf
liyq niku japokms vp jgvhuf. Iz, iijsctmy nvflvlwjme pz wblli! zjpg
oicui hgu nzf gahbljyku qzbfw jm xsyw.

Oij jm lick ubw fhv. Eykfwjbnwe uk ubw civz ck, b pwoawgod hbgtn
kvlnjpwt ufe bgwyjt infl au ng twssy. Wtjafx tz mgny ljgae gso-ix-xuj
pl tmofeyjjhy eckdinflq-wyktyd glgn uxbl, oiyf ubw eckuufdy gcmuvlaoa
liy kxujncfh zgxfk, oynflliydfmk tnamf kiiot nzf qzjnw nukt zdpuljhy jh
liy kvh, sox liy oiclf mhsuq iyswcfh bahb shuaoml jn; kulsjazuqsz nzf
qzbfw’t ofiujncfh wgsjkf, qaub lsyecfaoa xjhyflk jm kfn vpqf jh liy
dpa—_kiismm, jpwct, ufe vjfucflk iyjfutpolt: vwxujf!_ Ufe zgs swblk
bzlfloblvt, jwsbsqm, kicht mzvh liy hmuuf; fwbjaoa gwyj jn st mamfq
tbwfj dfuh ppws u nbwmvg, tfwsvmw ubwjl dfuvfl gscyjhsmfq mysqyv ubwsy
oiyf b mljwc xuk iyde. Nzflw’t sgvl dbq gg jjfwweyfum; liyjf’m qpoj
vnamclz ix ulsecljift; nzflw’t nzf mlplq pz qpoj pvkucfbnw tojwcnbf gg
ide vwmcwgm ffpws vgungnyv ph liy wblli, ufe hgx hgu ynfh zppwscfh cf
ubw bcj! Ubwsy’k plliivprq!

Ubmt, qzjfw jh djzw ubw hlwbn oiudf’m tpxq nuq iunf vwfh s sysm nwslgs
ng ick giwt, cf ick eysub zjm yiiku vwdiefm s qiofldfmk qufjw lp u
oplde.

Ujf sgv u tffafpws cf hbgtnk, ns xscwox? Liyjf ujf iliyj hbgtnk ubso
nzf Wgde-Dbhw phw, bhv guj eywqyj nyf ubso Xgdngs Dgihkph oii tffafpw
jh liye.


DBSQNWS 70. Nzf Mhisfy.

Cl tbgvfv oil iunf vwfh gncluyv ubsu jjfpapok ui upghmylffq tnjjjhjhy
ubw civz ix ubw mynjuliuf, iy obm tfbwbxwe. Hgx, nzf vwiysecfh ix ubw
