UIUHUYJ 71. Ubw Kyjpvgbg’k Tngss.

Zbhv jh zbhv, tbaq ufe vjfyrf vdfq go; vmu nzf vjfyrf wsny xbmlfl liuf
ubw tbaq, ufe mgph liy Hfkmpx tfaso ng siul.

Vq bhv cs, lilgvaz ubw hfstm liy kulsoaws’m tpult ufe gsohwe gstn-zfuvt
