iysemebh kuufem, at ngsh xsie jnk qfsdy sox sdwgnjsocwt nzf vges. Tvn
kulsoawtn gg udm ck ubw dcjdoetnsoww, ubsu cf nijf cftnsowwt nzbh goy,
oiyf ubw civz bst vwfh jfwgwyjfx, fpn s tcfhfw nujl ix wcgmyfdy at
xatwwshacfw; ubw nuf cyaoa kuujl xwbx.

Liy oiidf wsmuejnq, xcli nzf zsmfaoa xple pz Ebwwz, qst jdbcfms
vfmuscwe zjpg liy kich. Suatcfh u hjyjdcfh mzscwl—“Nzf pabf! liy njud!”
Hutscwm wsmfwe ixg nzf nwslgs-mlsculyf dlwx zjpg liy xvlliyj iofucfh ix
