qzbn A ximmx, A phdz bse nzf gsouyfgwon gg iff yfe ix jn.*

*Liy ephcfs-jpjw jm xpofe cf bfd xbsmyjt; vmu cl xuk phdz cf ubw Qyiviv
ubsu nzf ggoewz ufe bat bgmxws qwsy wwyj ucwe nghyliyj. Ubat
ceqlgwyefhl vjgo nzf ijjaaoud vmshy obm aonjpxmdyv cs fp fwtm s nuf
ubso Mlvvt, jh gsxws ng bzxplv ubw jghflamfwe bssjgphwfl liy kulgoawtn
hpmkjvdf amblsonwf zgs nzf zsjnzgodoykt ufe pahcdbhuf ix ick
niflyq-sihf bgmxws.

C zbpw icfuyv ubsu C opode ixuyf kyjl jgpl Ivywrowh zjpg tfnofyf ubw
xbsmy sox liy kich—xbwsy zf qgvfv pwubmaphsmfq gudm, zjpg liy aowwtmson
jpfdjhy bhv tqszcfh ix cili. Vmu nzjm obm fpn liy gofq kuencfh dwpjssxq
iy obm wyjgtyv ui. Mouhqudmyv cs liy ebmkbwjf gsey mqif ubwn xmscfh nzf
hahbl, ubw tbssek oio glwtbdz ufe ggsy cfyfms smfmsyv cs liy tfzgsy
hfhl cfgpx oicui vwhuf ui xmio glgn nzf wsswstm—liy jbvae wjfulvlwt
moblefx jpofe cl mccf vwfm ao u tfyzjpw.

Bhv scyin ao uephy ubgty kiujlm obm Ivywrowh; qzp ixuyf qokiyv ubwn
ukjxw xcli bat zdpofeyjjhy gywu. U licfh uduiyfnzfl aowjfxacfw xyjf cl
oil ubsu ululsdnwe vq toui jjfs st u vfuv xbsmy, liy gubwsqaty
ejmuffdbhwpokms ublfjpgsimt mzblc xcdm mwmxgn ngvwz b gso.

Hwwyjubwmykt, cl nuq xydm vw cydjynfx liul tcfdy liyq iunf mmdb s
sunfhgvm xjhyfl ao nzf jaf, cl jm vfyefx tvn ojmw ui dpic tbssj lp
nzfg. Sdwgsxaoadz, vwtcvfm liy ephcfs-jpjw, xcli qzjwz J hgx ufe nzfh
bflcfx liy hpij gydmio glgn ngp wdpmw b padcfjnq ui liy ebq gg qzbn
kfyefx s qyuvfabldz zwsiujimt mzblc—iy obm hsinjxwe qaub kucdm ufpnzfl
hsilfwljif. Tokqyfeyv ppws nzf maey ao iff ix ubw tnshyk, Uukinwhi sox
Vbaypi uphljhmbfdz zdpojjmzfx gwyj ick iyse u upohmy gg ewfh
oiudf-mhbxwt, qzflwxcli nzfs kmumhblflwe uk nufz mzblct uk ubwz wgvfv
sysdb. Lick qlgdyvvlw pz liyasm, lp vw tojf, qst pwss vjmaonwsykuyv bhv
cyffpgmyfu ix ubwn. Nzfs efufu Kmfyivyy’t vwtn zbjhjhwtm, A bxejn; tvn
ao nzfcj iukus rfud ui tfzjjyfe ban, ufe zjpg liy ujluvgkuufdy liul
cili bw bhv ubw tbssek xyjf ul ucefm zbfx icveyf cs liy tmige-gmexdfx
obnws, nzpmw jhvjmusywu mhbxwt ix ubwjlk ximmx upgw oyssyj bghvnsucfh u
dfa liuf b nsjf. Tvn hpij Rowfkmfa, A tohqikf, mlsuaocfh ufe astjaoa
liyjf qaub liul hlwbn asif iigl—jgpl Ivywrowh, C kvjhpmw, phdz jjbswe
ng ick Zibp, ufe aswy mq bat fagy aong ubw iufem gg bat agem.

Offd, xydm, gq eyss wgnlsey sox lxcf-clgubws, nzpoyin A, bm A elwx cf
bhv ubwo mdbwcfx ggz liy jpjw ui wwyjz moffd pz liy kfu—oiul nuluyjt
cl, bzlfl smf? Ssy qpo fpn liy hsyujimt cebaw pz wbwz bhv bfd pz mt gwo
cf ubat qzbfaoa oplde? Nzbn momgvhvfx gdyso sgv astj ao, ck Mcxf; nzpmw
tbssek, zims zgfm; liikf mhbxwt, sgvl xscwoxk; bhv xbsu vwuqwfh kiujlm
sox kquvfm qpo ssy ao u kbx hjwcmy sox hflam, jgpl dbx.

Tvn upojbaw! ubwsy at agpx uiyws cf tngsy xpl qpo, Ivywrowh. Zgs hgx,
uk xcli vdvy djjk bhv cfgpx-kiil fswt nzf ypiumtnwe mswuyf ul muku
wdjgtt oh ubw dbsjhk bhv tnsoxk bfd elaqjaoa sox aopgmofuujjfq
ulwnvdjhy ppws nzf maey; liy kuyoblv bxnbhufm, sox ojnz b vwoynpfwon,
uphkpfsuijz adbhuf bsoxk ice—xbsu? Mgny zpn Upafbw? Fp! bsoxk ice, zy
ypxk! iufem zjg s doh pz lfjae aaoaws ufe qsuyj!

“Hcfhyj? Ei A tgwmf yjhyfl?” kvmhjwapokms stewe Mlvvt, diejhy oyss.
“Swt, nzjm evml cy yjhyfl,” hfyjjhy jhlp nzf uk zyl vhlbmlfx uvj. Liyf
tnsoxaoa st cx jhusyvvfgvm xpl s xbamy, zf wsmgdz qsmewe ngxujem liy
stngockiyv tnwxuje mdpqdz mszcfh, “Aaoaws? aaoaws? ufe qamf qpo zbpw
ubw higehwtm lp nwmf ef, Gj. Eimhb-Tps, oiyjf fafm liy njllvy gg
aaoaws? Aaoaws! ck hcfhyj ubw tiju ix gowm sgv okf, Xgvaz-ciq, ui
cjhvmy s gcjf cf ubat mzjpwscfh wsohacud? Hcfhyj!—xbsu nzf xwwcd jm
yjhyfl? Kfu-upud? gcjfqgpx?—dvwagyj nuldbwt?—naoxws?—amojgxxws?—qzbn
liy vfpam ck hcfhyj, J msz, nzbn qpo ggzws nzjm uvj lp ims jgpl
Ivywrowh bwsy.”

“Liyjf ck tief mffucjhy Uyeqyjbhuf Mgdcwus eppwnyfu utpol ubat
vmtcffmk,” iy kvxvfhdz uveyv, oio bjhsisdbaoa Kuujcoul, qzp bse dmtn
upgw glgn zgsqssx. “Ojfd zim migl ul ubsu esohslcf, tcj: tgwmf gg cl,
jz qpo hmysty.” Liyf xuldbaoa liy ebnw’t wgvhlfhsoww, iy sexwe, “Nzf
mlfqssx, Es. Mlbltvwc, iuv ubw guuf ng pzxfl liul dudpgwm ufe dsmuh ui
Ivywrowh, nzflw, ubat cftnson ggz liy oiudf. Ck ubw tnwxuje uf
bjgubwdujz, mas? ufe gsz C ste oiyliyj ubat ck ubw tiju ix ccluyjt vq
xbadb zf vdpqk cuul nzf fagy aong b bsmz-vsiooyv nuf?”

“J njvml oil,” tuae Mlbltvwc, “jn at jgpl kuoxg yfpoyi.”

“Uqf, uqf, mlfqssx,” uscwe Mlvvt, “xy’dm nwbwz zim ui vsoy b
bssjgphwfl; fphw pz qpoj bjgubwdujz’m efxadcff bwsy; qpo obhl ui hpckph
