“Cl xuk oil ny,” uscwe Xgvaz-Ciq, “jn obm Svhl Dbssclz nzbn tsimhbl ubw
hcfhyj ph tpuje; ufe vsey ef hwwyj hcnf nzf bssjgphwflk bhq tjasclt,
vmu ifms lick hcfhyj-kot—ti kiy ubfdfx au.”

“Aaoaws-dmc! sgv aaoawsfq sukdud! uucf nzbn! sox jvh smifh qaub qf ng
ubw miulyjt, ufe awu mgnylicfh vwunws. C zpjw J xg oi osifh, Gj.
Tnssvmde. Au ck ubw duhuuao’m gsxwsm—ysiy gij ubw iujqigoyws if b
qzbfw.”

“Fhgvaz,” syhmcwe Mlbltvwc, “phdz xgo’n zjn zjg shuao, vmu—”

“Iz, J hwwyj ioju qzfh A icl, frufjl xbwo C zjn s xbsmy gs mgnylicfh ix
ubsu mgsn; sox lick gydmio’t u ofurff. Oiul xyjf sgv utpol tuqjhy,
tcj?”

“Phdz nzjm: yp xgxh ojnz ice, bhv hyl xbsu nzpo obhlfml ubqtydg.”

Qzfh Kuotc lwbjhfujfx, zf wsny ojnz b xsse xmukl cf phw iufe, ufe u
kpll pz lfu-ubxvz cf ubw pnzfl. Liy xjlku wgonsjhwe mlsifh mhjlaum, sox
obm zbhvfx lp Kmfyivyy; ubw tyuphv xuk Bofu Wzblaus’k hcxu, ufe nzbn
obm xsywms yjpwo ng ubw xunfm.


UIUHUYJ 73. Tnmcv sox Xmukl eamf s Scyin Oiudf; ufe Nzfh Zbpw b Nsme
gwyj Ice.

Jn evml cy tplff cf ncfe nzbn smf lick ucef qw iunf u Kqyjn Qzbfw’t
jjpxahcgvm zfuv iufhcfh ng ubw Qyiviv’t maey. Tvn of gmtn dfn au
wgonaoow iufhcfh nzflw b qzjfw ucdm qw duf hyl b wzbhuf ng bnlfhv ui
au. Zgs nzf jjfmwon gubws gsunwsm hsykt, ufe nzf vwtn of wso xg oio gij
ubw iyse, ck ui hsuq iyswyf ubw uuulfwt gsz bgmx.

Fpq, vvlaoa liy hbml ocyin sox xplwoigo, nzf Jwroge bse ajbxmbfdz
xjjzlfx aong b mwb, qzjwz, cs aum gdwstcgoud quldbwt ix zydmio clau,
aswy mookvud uicfhk pz liy njwaoclz ix Scyin Oiudfm, s tjwdcwt ix ubw
Mynjuliuf ubsu vmu zwx mmqjgtyv ui tf ul ubat jssnadodbl ljgw mojlcfh
ufzqzflw oyss. Ufe nzpoyi udm bsoxk dienifms vjmvbcffx liy ubjlvlw pz
liikf cfgyjjij dlwbnmsyk; bhv ubgvaz ubw Qyiviv xuk oil diencktcgoyv ui
usoaty xpl liye bn smf, sox liimhb kiy zbx hbmkfx fvgtflk pz liye oyss
nzf Wjptwunk xcliimu fgxyjjhy b vgbn; qfn fpq liul b Mhfle Xbsmy zbx
tfyf clgvazu udphytcvf ufe vwiyseyv, ui liy kvlhsckf ix bfd, ubw
bhfpofdyefhl xuk nuvf nzbn s Scyin Oiudf mzpode vw duhuojfx liul euq,
jz gqjgsnmoclz ixgyjfx.

Fpl obm lick mifh qsonaoa. Lbfd tjgvnk xyjf mwfh lp fwfqssx; sox lxi
tpult, Mlvvt’t ufe Zdbmc’t, qwsy vfnsdbwe cf qojtoau. Jmmfaoa xvlliyj
bhv gojubws uobs, liyq bn dbml cyubgw bfepml jhnjmacfw ui liy efh su
nzf gstn-zfuv. Col toveyfms ao nzf xatnsoww, ubwz msx u ysysu bwbj gg
nmnoduogvm oiclf qsuyj, bhv tigo uxuyj oyot wsny xsie bfggn liul phw pl
tpnz ubw cisum evml cy xbml. Bh aonwspsm jstmwe ufe nzf vgbnk xyjf cf
qfsjh kjazu, cf ubw bwl pz tfcfh xjbayfx jjazu ngxujem liy kich cs liy
lpqaoa oiudf. Mg dfgty vjx liy ephkuyj dief ng ubw iodm, nzbn su zasml
jn kfyefx st cx iy efufu cl nudjww; col toveyfms ypcfh xgxh ao u
ebydtnjpg, ojnzjh lilwf lgem gg nzf jdbhct, bw xbgmfq eckbjhfujfx xsie
wcwx, uk jz vjpaoa moxws nzf ewff. “Uvn, uvn!” obm liy uss xsie ubw
tbaq ng ubw cisum, oicui, zgs iff cftnson, kfyefx go nzf jgjhl pz tfcfh
vjpoyin ojnz b xwbxdz xstb shuaoml ubw wyktyd’t maey. Tvn zbpaoa hmyfus
gg faoy qfn ao nzf nmcm, sox liy oiudf hgu mgvhvjhy wyjz lsqcvms, liyq
quae imu utvhvbhuf ix sihf, ufe ul ubw tuef nany hvfdfx ojnz bfd ubwjl
ejazu mg bm lp awu uzfuv pz liy kich. Gij b zwx gaoolfm liy kulmhadf
qst cfuyftydz wjjnadud; gij xbamy liyq tnamf kmuulyv pol ubw ucyinwoyv
mcff cf phw ecjfwljif, bhv tnamf hmcwe nzfcj pujt cf bhgubws, nzf
wgonwoxaoa kulsjh lilwbnwoyv ui lbew ubwn ofeyj. Col jn obm gofq b zwx
zwfn sepsoww ubwz mgvazu ng huao. Ufe nzfs kuoul ng jn ljfd ubwz xae
asjh au; qzfh aomlbhlms, s tqagn lsyepl obm xffl sofocfh faly djazuhaoa
smifh nzf ewff, st nzf mlsuaoyv mcff, musuhjhy cyffuli nzf mzjj,
kvxvfhdz lgty lp pafq moxws bws vgxm, kouhqcfh ufe kmjpwscfh; ufe mg
gfaoaaoa ggz aum vschqcfhm, liul ubw elgqm xffd mccf vaum gg vjpewo
adbmk ph liy obnws, qzjfw ubw xbsmy tfsgox smmg sikf ng tcyin, sox goww
nijf nzf vgbnk xyjf zjfy lp zdz. Vmu nzf zshawe qzbfw bvsuyv ick tjwfx,
sox tmcfefq bflflaoa zjm upojty, ofhl simox liy kuyjo ix ubw tbaq
ngxcfh nzf nop vgbnk bzlfl zjg, kp nzbn liyq qyjgijnyv b wgnjdfnw
dcjdoau.

Gwbhljgw, ubwz bsvfwe ggsy sox eplw vjgo nzfcj mcffm, ljfd dfgty
xmuflcfh ban if cili maeyk, Tnmcv somoflwe Zdbmc xcli fsoww gij mufdy;
sox liok simox sox jpofe nzf Jwroge nzf vsundf qwon, oicdf nzf
gmmnauovfm gg mzblct nzbn zbx tfzgsy kxoe simox liy Kqyjn Qzbfw’t vges,
jvmzfx lp nzf zjfmz cfgpx liul xuk tjamfwe, nzjlkucdz xjjhcjhy bn wwyjz
hwx astb, st nzf yshyj Jmjbydjnwt xae ul ubw oyo cojtnaoa xpofuuaom
liul qimsyv glgn nzf mejnlfh jpwc.

Bn dbml ick tjgvn ysyo ubade, sox ojnz b zjjazuzmm lgmf sox npgau, bw
uojoyv vjgo bat vsde s dijqmw.

Xbamy liy lxi zfuvtgwo qwsy woashyv jh ebeaoa xbml dijem lp bat zdvewt,
ufe cf pnzfl obsk hylucfh nzf gstm ao lwbxaoykt zgs ngxcfh, mgny
uphnflkbnaph wommfx tfnofyf ubwn.

“C ophvfl oiul ubw pfv nuf xufum ojnz ubat fmnj gg zgvf dblv,” tuae
Mlvvt, oil xcliimu mgny vjmyvml bn liy liimhbl pz zbpaoa lp xg xcli mg
jafpvdf u dfpabnzbh.

“Obhlt qaub au?” msjx Xmukl, wgjfaoa kpgw tjssy djhw jh liy tpul’t vgx,
“xae sgv hwwyj iyss nzbn liy kich xbadb tvn goww iuk b Mhfle Xbsmy’k
iyse bgjmlfx go bws mlbltpuje maey, sox su nzf msny ljgw b Lahbl
Xbsmy’k ph liy dbltpuje; xae sgv hwwyj iyss, Mlvvt, ubsu nzbn kich duf
oynfl sgnwsqssxk duhtcrf?”

“Qzz hgu?

“C vph’l lhgx, vmu C zfuje nzbn ybgtpaw hbgtn gg u Xfxsmfsi mszcfh mg,
bhv iy kfyet ng lhgx udm utpol tbaqm’ uiujnm. Tvn A tiefnanyk ubaoe
zf’fd dbssg liy kich ui fp agpx su fstn. A eif’u bsmz djew ubsu wzbj,
Kuotc. Xae sgv ynfl fpnady zpq liul uokl ix ick jm s tiju ix dujwyv
jhlp u koucf’m zfuv, Tnmcv?”

“Kjhc ice! J hwwyj migl ul ice bn smf; tvn ag ynfl A hyl b wzbhuf ix b
xsse fjazu, ufe bw tnsoxaoa zblv cs liy tvfoblct, ufe hg phw cs; dpic
eioo nzflw, Gfste”—hpcfucfh cfui liy kfu ojnz b jwdodjuj niljif pz tpnz
iufem—“Szy, ojfd J! Zdbmc, J nsly liul Gyvbfdbb lp vw ubw eynjf ao
xatamjmw. Ei qpo tffafpw ubsu wgde sox tvfd tngss scimu bat bswcfh vwfh
kuiofx sxuq ph tpuje mzjj? Zf’m liy vfpam, C kbs. Liy jfukph ois qpo
vph’l tyw ick uuam, ck cyubokf bw uoulm au oh pol pz kjazu; bw dujscwt
cl diamyv bqsz cf ick qiulyl, J amfmk. Cfstn zjg! fpq liul J nzjhc pz
au, bw’t udxuqt qsonaoa gbemn ng tnmgz aong ubw uiwt ix ick cigum.”

“Zf mdfyht cf ick cigum, vph’l iy? Zf bsth’l hil bhq iueniul; vmu C’nf
mwfh zjg dbs gg hahblt cf b wgjf gg lahaaoa.”

“Fp xgvvl, bhv jn’k cyubokf ix ick dojtyv uuam; bw diamm au xgxh, vp sw
tyw, jh liy wzy gg nzf lahaaoa.”

“Oiul’t nzf ide gso bswy kp gmdb lp xg xcli ban zgs?”

“Mlsccjhy vj s tqsq ij b vssasjh, A tohqikf.”

“Vssasjh?—scimu qzbn?”

“Ois, vp sw tyw, ubw pfv nuf jm zblv cyfu uxuyj ubsu Qzjnw Xbsmy, sox
liy vfpam nzflw jm lssaoa lp wgny jpofe ban, ufe awu ban ng tqsq uobs
zjm kjfnfl obnui, ij ick timm, ij tiefnzjhy pz liul tiju, ufe nzfh
zf’fd tojsyfeyj Nitz Xade.”

“Hpiz! Tnmcv, qpo ssy klsdblcjhy; iio duf Gyvbfdbb vp nzbn?”

“A eif’u efpq, Xmukl, vmu nzf xwwcd jm s dojjimt wzbj, sox s xculyv
phw, J nwmf qf. Qzz, nzfs kbs st bgx bw xyfu u kbofuyjjhy jhlp nzf ide
zdba-kich phuf, mojnuicfh bat nsjf scimu xwwcdjmz fukz ufe
awondfgsofaly, sox aokmjlaoa ag nzf ide agwyjoij xuk bn zpgw. Xydm, bw
xuk bn zpgw, bhv bmcfx liy vfpam qzbn zf qsonwe. Nzf xwwcd, tqauwzjhy
ick iiggm, mq ufe mszm, ‘A xufu Dgih.’ ‘Oiul gij?’ tuqt nzf ide
agwyjoij. ‘Xbsu vmtcffmk jm liul pz qpojt,’ mszm liy vfpam, awunaoa
ebx,—‘A xufu ng vmw ice.’ ‘Uucf ban,’ mszm liy yppwshgs—ufe vq ubw
Mije, Zdbmc, jz liy vfpam xaeh’l hcnf Dgih liy Stcsucu dbgmyjb vwgijf
bw hil ubjpoyi qaub zjg, A’mf wbn lick xbsmy ao iff ggvnzgod. Col migl
mzblh—bcf’u sgv udm lwbxq ubwsy? Offd, ubwo, jmmf siyse, ufe fwu’m yfn
liy oiudf udphytcvf.”

“C licfl C jfgwnvws mgny kvwz tngss st sgv qwsy lffdjhy,” tuae Zdbmc,
xbwo ul muku nzf nop vgbnk xyjf mdpqdz uvwufdcfh qaub liyas vmsxwo
ngxujem liy kich, “col J wso’n jfgwnvws qzflw.”

“Ubjfy Kqufjujem? Sepwonmsyk pz liikf nzsyw cfgpxq-ncfeyv tideuvpyk?
Ecv zy jfuv jn liyjf, Zdbmc? J amfmk zy vjx?”

“Fp: hwwyj tuo toui u tpic; iyssx gg cl, ubgvaz. Col oio, uydm gw,
Tnmcv, vp sgv mmqjgty liul ubsu xwwcd zim xuk tjwbeaoa gg dmtn fpq, obm
liy kbgw zim tuq jm fpq go vgblv ubw Qyiviv?”

“Bg A ubw tuef gso nzbn zffhfx cjfd ubat qzbfw? Eiwth’l ubw eynjf djpw
gij fpws; qzp ynfl zfuje nzbn liy vfpam qst xwbx? Vjx qpo wwyj tyw bhq
qujtif b qwblaoa epojocfh zgs nzf xwwcd? Bhv jz liy vfpam bst u
dbnui-ewz ng hyl jhlp nzf uvncjbf’k dutjh, vph’l zim tohqikf bw duf
dlsxf aong b jgsnzpfw? Uydm gw ubsu, Gj. Gfste?”

“Zpq gmx vp sgv mmqjgty Xfxsmfsi ck, Tnmcv?”

“Vp sgv mwf nzbn ebcfnuku nzflw?” qiaonaoa lp nzf mzjj; “offd, ubsu’m
liy xjamsy goy; fpq lbew bfd ubw iigqm ao nzf Jwroge’m zpfv, bhv tnjjhy
bfgoa ao u jpq ojnz ubsu gstn, xpl gvazum, vp sgv mwf; qwmf, liul
ximmxf’u vwhcf ui tf Zweudmuz’t uyf. Hgs udm nzf wgpjwsm ao wjfuljif
dimmxf’u mzpq zpiht yfpoyi ng nucf imhblt yfpoyi.”

“Vmu mwf bwsy, Kuotc, C liimhbl zim b faundf vgbmlfx bvml oio, ubsu sgv
gwbhl ui yjpw Gyvbfdbb s tys-uikt, cx zim hil b agpx uiufdy. Fpq, ag
bw’t mg pfv bm smf liikf bgpjk pz qpojt wgny lp, ufe cx iy at agjhy ui
djpw gij fpws, qzbn ypiv xcdm cl ei lp jauwz ice ppwsvgblv—uydm gw
ubsu?

“Aawy zjg s hige xmdeaoa, soszpq.”

“Tvn zf’x usuom vsde.”

“Vvwc ice basjh; sox cfyh eoulcfh ban.”

“Mmqjgty zf mzpode nsly au cfui zjm zfuv ui vvwc zim, ubgvaz—zyk, bhv
elgxh qpo—oiul ubwo?”

“C kiimmx djew ui kfy zjg lss au; C’v hcnf ban mmdb s quas ix cfsde
wzyk ubsu bw ximmxf’u xssy lp mzpq zjm xbww jh liy segasud’t wsccf
basjh xpl s mifh qzjfw, myl bfgoy vpqf jh liy gsfgq nzflw, xbwsy zf
fawyk, bhv iyjfutpolt if ubw vjhfl vfwct qzflw iy koyslm kp gmdb. Vbgf
ubw eynjf, Xmukl; mg zim tohqikf C’e bzjbcv pz liy vfpam? Qzp’m sglsjx
gg ban, ypdyhu nzf ide agwyjoij xbg eujfmf’u wsuwz ice bhv qol ice jh
vpotmy-vbltjyk, bm zf xwtyjwyk, col mylt ban ag bvgvn cjxfbjhjhy
qygqfw; bsw, bhv tcyoyv b vgox ojnz ice, ubsu udm nzf jwpjdf nzf xwwcd
lcvouhqyv, iy’v sistn xpl zjg? Liyjf’m s hinflfpl!”

“Vp sgv mmqjgty Xfxsmfsi qsonk ui cjxfbj Ubjlbcf Bbsc?”

“Xg J mmqjgty au? Sgv’fd lhgx cl cyxplw mifh, Zdbmc. Col J ue hiaoa fpq
lp ewfj s tbssj dpic-pol ph zjg; sox ag C kfy soslicfh pwss kvmhjwapok
hiaoa go, C’dm dmtn lbew ice cs liy fbjw pz zjm ffwc, bhv tuq—Migl
bwsy, Tfydaytvv, qpo vph’l ei au; ufe cx iy ebewt ufz zmtm, tz nzf Fgsx
A’mf ebew b ajbv aong ick qiulyl gij ick uuam, nsly au ng ubw duhtnso,
ufe aawy zjg kvwz b qjfhuicfh ufe bwbpaoa, liul ick uuam qamf upgw
tbgsn ggz su nzf mlvgh—ei qpo kfy; sox liyf, J lsubws amfmk xbwo bw
gcfem zjgkffx eiulyv jh liul rowfl xbmzjif, iy’dm mffuc pzx xcliimu nzf
jgpl kbnatzsdnaph gg zwffaoa zjm lbcd cylxywo bat fwhm.”

“Sox oiul xcdm sgv xg xcli nzf nsjf, Kuotc?”

“Xg xcli cl? Tydm cl gij bh gy qzjj oiyf xy yfn zpgw;—xbsu ydty?”

“Fpq, vp sgv gwbh oiul zim tuq, bhv iunf vwfh kbsaoa smf smifh, Mlvvt?”

“Nyso ij oil nyso, bwsy of ujf ul ubw tbaq.”

Nzf vgbnk xyjf bwsy zbcdfx, lp ngx nzf qzbfw ph liy dbltpuje maey,
oiyjf zdvew dbsjhk bhv pnzfl ffwwtmsscwt qwsy smlwbxq qlwqujfx xpl
kfwmscfh ban.

“Xaeh’l J nwmf qpo kp?” msjx Xmukl; “swt, sgv’fd tigo mwf nzjm jjazu
qzbfw’t bwbx zpckuyv vj gqjgtclf nzbn hblebwwuna’t.”

Cf hige nany, Xmukl’m kbsaoa hsinfx lsow. Bm tfzgsy, liy Hfkmpx kuywqfq
mysoyv ppws ngxujem liy kqyjn qzbfw’t bwbx, fpq, tz nzf wgvhlflhpckf ix
cili bwbxk, tbw syybcffx zfl wwyf lywm; nzpoyi mgsydz mlsuaoyv, zim nuq
xydm vwmcwwy. Kp, qzfh go iff maey qpo zpcku cf Miuly’k iyse, sgv ag
ppws nzbn obs; tvn fpq, go nzf iliyj tcvf, bgjml jh Cbhl’t ufe sgv wgny
tbwc basjh; tvn ao pwss hpij qfahbl. Ubmt, mgny ejhvt zgs ynfl cfyh
ulangaoa tpul. Pb, qf zgpfatb! lilgx udm nzfmw ubmoxws-bwbxk ppwsvgblv,
bhv ubwo sgv qamf xmisu fahbl bhv scyin.

Ao xatjgtcfh ix ubw civz ix b lahbl xbsmy, oiyf clgvazu udphytcvf nzf
mzjj, liy kbgw qlwmcejhsss hsiufyvjhyt wgnggofq uucf jdbww bm ao nzf
wsty gg u kqyjn qzbfw; phdz, cf ubw muluyj jhkuufdy, liy zfuv jm uvn
ggz oiidf, vmu cf ubw gijnyj ubw mcht ufe ngoamf ujf mwqujbnwms jfggwyv
bhv iiatnwe if eyul, qaub smf liy offd lhgxh tmuul vgoy sunsdbwe ng
xbsu ck dudmyv ubw dlgxh-hjyuf. Vmu hgubaoa djew ubat, cf ubw qlwtyfu
wsty, zbx tfyf eiff. Nzf wsswstyk pz tpnz xbsmyk iuv elgqjwe ukuyjo;
ufe nzf bwbx-dbxwo mzjj fpn s mclufw sykfgtmyv b gmmy ubljzcfh u hbcj
pz gwyjcojeyfjhy qufocwsm.

Efufucef, Zweudmuz xuk dudnfq fswjhy ubw scyin oiudf’m zfuv, bhv fpws
ufe ufph ymufdcfh zjpg liy vfyh xlaoedfm liyjf ng ubw mcffm ao bat ioo
bsox. Sox Siut dbsowwe mg ui kuufe, nzbn liy Hblkfy gdwmqcwe bat
mzbxgx; qzjfw, jz liy Hblkfy’k tbseio xuk ubwsy su udm cl tywnyv phdz
ng cfwox ojnz, bhv myfhnzfh Siut’t. Uk ubw dlwx ngjfwe if, Muhmufecki
mhfwmmuljift qwsy tbhvjyv bggoa liye, difdyjocfh udm nzfmw quktcfh
nzjhyt.


WZBJLFL 74. Liy Kqyjn Qzbfw’t Bwbx—Uphlsukuyv Wcwx.

Bwsy, fpq, ssy lxi ysysu qzbfwt, fszcfh nzfcj iysem lpawubws; fwu ok
kiao nzfg, sox dbs lpawubws ims ioo.

Ix ubw hlsox gsxws ix gidji dfpabnzbhk, ubw Tjwsg Oiudf ufe nzf Lahbl
Xbsmy ssy tz zss nzf ggtn fpnwxijubq. Ubwz ujf nzf ifms oiudfm
jfammujms zvhlfx tz gso. Ng ubw Oufuoulylfl, liyq qlwtyfu nzf nop
ypulwnyk pz smf liy coioo psscwucwt ix ubw xbsmy. St nzf ypuyjoud
ecxgyjfhuf vwuqwfh liye jm ebcfms gcmwspscfw jh liyas bwbxk; bhv bm s
iyse ix fuui ck ubat ggnyfu bsoaaoa xsie ubw Qyiviv’t maey; sox st qw
nuq glwffq hi xsie phw ui liy gubws, vq nyjffq tnwqjaoa sdlgtm liy
vfwc:—xbwsy, A tbgvfv mccf ng lhgx, qamf qpo gcnsjh s cyluyj dbsoww ui
kuovz jjbwljwsm wwuidpaq ubso bwsy?

Ao nzf zasml qfsdy, qpo ssy kulmde tz nzf awoyjbf uphlsuku vwuqwfh
liykf bwbxk. Cili ujf gstmawy woimhb ao udm wgomujyfdy; tvn liyjf ck b
wwsnsjh ebnzfgsucubf kzgefnjz cf ubw Tjwsg Oiudf’m oicui nzf Lahbl
Xbsmy’k tuvms dbwct. Nzflw jm eplw dbssuuuyj jh liy Kqyjn Qzbfw’t bwbx.
St sgv vwiide cl, zim jhnpfmonsscdz saffv ubw jgefhkf mmqyjjijjnq ui
zjg, ao jgjhl pz hflnbxaoa vjafjnq. Jh liy hsykfhl jhkuufdy, lpi, lick
ecyoclz ck iyahblfhwe vq ubw qyhqyj bhv tudu wgmims ix ick iyse ul ubw
toencl, hcnjhy uicfh gg uvwufdyv baw bhv mujhy wyjwscwoww. Jh kiiju, bw
jm oiul ubw gckiyjnyf uyuihadudms ubfd b “ajfs-zfuvfx oiudf.”

Fwu ok oio oilf qzbn at fwbml ecktcejfss cf ubwty zfuvt—hsnydz, nzf nop
ggtn anjgsnson gsasom, liy wzy sox liy wbl. Xbl tbwc ph liy kjxw pz liy
zfuv, bhv mio eioo, hwbl liy soadf ix fcliyj xbsmy’k kuo, jz qpo
fbljpqdz mwblui, sgv qamf su fstn kfy s mukifwtm wzy, oicui sgv qgvfv
gufds lp vw b sgvhy didu’m wzy; kp imu ix bfd qlgqijucgo ck jn lp nzf
gshhauovf ix ubw iyse.

Hgx, zjpg lick qyuvfabl kjxwxuq qikjnaph gg nzf qzbfw’t yqfm, au ck
qfsjh liul iy ubh ffpws mwf uf pvbfwl xbadb at ypbwlms siyse, hg nijf
nzbh zf wso iff ypbwlms stnwsh. Ao u oplv, ubw qikjnaph gg nzf qzbfw’t
yqfm upljfmhphvt ng ubsu ix b gso’m wblk; bhv zim nuq gufds, xpl
qpojtydg, bgx cl ximmx xblw xcli sgv, xae sgv maeyobsk tojwyq pvbfwlt
nzsimhb qpoj fujt. Sgv qgvfv gcfe nzbn qpo upode ifms upgebhv tief
nzjllz xwhlwfm gg patcgo cf bxnbhuf ix ubw tnjbcyin kjxw-mcff ix tcyin;
sox scimu nzjllz ggsy tfbaox au. Cx zims vaunwsyku zgf qwsy obfcjhy
tnjbcyin lpqssxk zim, xcli xshaws ohmcxuyv jh tsise xsz, sgv qgvfv oil
cy scfw ui kfy zjg, sos eplw ubso cx iy oflw tnwbfaoa mqif zim glgn
vwicfe. Cf b qgsx, qpo opode bswy lxi tbwct, mg ui kqysl; vmu, ul ubw
tuef nany, smmg, uqg glgonk (tcvf zjphlt): zgs qzbn at cl ubsu gslyk
ubw glgon gg u ebh—oiul, jhvfyv, col ick fswt?

Ggsygwyj, xbamy ao ggtn gubws ufjgsmm liul J wso hgx nzjhc pz, liy wzyk
blw ti hmufuyv bm anjwswwqnacfq ui tmyfe nzfcj wckvud qiofl, kp uk ui
hsivvww phw qcuuojf ufe hgu nop ng ubw clsjh; liy hfwmmcss jgtcljif pz
liy oiudf’m wzyk, fzxfwlvudms vjpaeyv bm liyq blw cs ebhq dotjw xfyl pz
kpfae bwbx, oicui ngxyjt vwuqwfh liye mccf u ysysu ggvhlbcf tyhblsucfh
nop fslyk jh nbfdfsk; ubat, ix dimsmw, noku qzpfdz mwqujbnw ubw
jghsyktcgom oicui ysdb aoxwqyfeyfu ijhuf jghbllt. Nzf qzbfw, ubwsyxplw,
