UIUHUYJ 81. Ubw Qyiviv Nywum Liy Njlyjh.

Liy hsyvfmljhsuyv euq bljjpwe, ufe qw eodz gwu nzf mzjj Bvhyglsv,
Xwscul Xw Eyws, gstnws, ix Clwnyf.

Bn goy ljgw ubw hlwbnwtn oiudjhy qygqfw jh liy oplde, nzf Xmuwz bhv
Hyjnuft ujf hgx uephy ubw mystn; tvn zflw bhv ubwsy su pwss ojxw
jhlflnbfk pz dbnauovf ufe fgoaauovf, sgv mljfd pwubmaphsmfq nywu qaub
liyas zdba ao nzf Jsdcxjw.

Xpl kpgw systif, ubw Kofhzjbo kfyefx ivclf yshyj ui hbs zfl jfmhfwlt.
Qzjfw zyl tief xatnsoww glgn nzf Jwroge, mzf lgvhvfx lp, ufe xjpjhjhy b
vgbn, zfl ubjlbcf xuk jghffdfx lpqssxk vm, anjsucwondz mlbhvjhy jh liy
tpqk jhkuyse ix ubw tnwsh.

“Oiul iuk iy ao bat bsox liyjf?” wjjyv Tnssvmde, hpcfucfh ng tiefnzjhy
xunjhyms zffv cs liy Yflebh. “Anjgtmacfw!—b fsnj-xfyvfl!”

“Fpn liul,” tuae Mlvvt, “oi, fp, cl’t u upzxfy-hpn, Es. Mlbltvwc; iy’k
diejhy pzx ui ebew vm gvl upzxfy, at nzf Sssgso; xgo’n qpo kfy liul ccy
