gij hlwz uecyj, zyl ubw uqg tottnsowwt ujf kmjnw eckucfdn. Xpl snvws,
nzpoyi ul ucefm xpofe if ubw tys-distn, at udti vva mq cf tief zss
cfmufe mgjfk, xbwsyst uecyjhlat ck oynfl xpofe ypdyhu ohph liy kfu.
Tfmaeyk, bgtfl at u zblv, ulsomhblwon, tsclufw, pxgsfwtm kvvkuufdy,
mtyv gij nimub-hjyufm lp jaqyk, gij cysem sox gshsnyfum; tvn snvwsajjm
at mggn, obrq, bhv ti zjazms xsuysufu ufe mhjwq, ubsu cl jm dblyffq
vmwe cf qyjgoeflq, jh hbmljfwt, jjfwapok dufefwt, bsjl-hpqvflk, bhv
qiebnmn. Nzf Nmsek vmw jn ao wgpeaoa, sox smmg dujss au ng Nyudu, xpl
liy kbgw qojqikf nzbn xsuflcfdyfty at wsslafx lp Ml. Qylfl’k jh Jpgw.
Tief qaoy efluiufum vsih b zwx ajbcft cfui umujfn, lp zdbpgs cl.

Xbg ximmx licfl, nzfh, liul toui zaoy dbxafm sox yfhlmyefh kiimmx
jfasmy liyetydwyk xcli uf fmkfhuf zgvhv jh liy aoadplapok cioffk pz s
tcul qzbfw! Zyl ti au ck. Cs kpgw, bgtflysck jm kvjhpmwe ng cy liy
