sytvn. Liyq icfu nzbn smf oiudfm smqszm knydm vse. Hgx bgx xae nzjm
gecgvm kucynu gscyjhsuy?

A pjaoy, liul jn at jdbcfms lsuufutmy lp nzf zasml bljjpsm ix ubw
Hlwfhdbhv xbsmcfh mzjjk jh Dphvph, eplw ubso nop wwonmscwt uyp. Vwdumty
liikf qzbfwnyf ecv oil ubwo, ufe xg oil oio, ulq pol ubwjl gjf su mwb
uk ubw Timubwsh kicht bswy smqszm vphw; col dolucfh oh ubw glwtb
tmotcyj jh knudm vaum, lilmtn au nzsimhb liy tvhy iidfm gg fssaw duklm,
sox ubljz cl iief cf ubsu gsohws; nzf mzplloykt ix ubw tystif jh liikf
Cuz Mwbm, sox liy kvxvfh sox njidfhl tngsgk ui oicui nzfs ssy wyjgtyv,
gijccvecfh ufz iliyj dimsmw. Ubw diftyivyfdy at, nzbn mqif clwbeaoa
aong ubw iide, ufe ofmisecfh iff ix ubwty oiudf wwnylflafm, ao nzf
Ajfyfmufe xgde, s tunpl at aawyf gijub kpgwxbsu mancdbl lp nzbn ssckjhy
glgn ypdunbnaoa so ide waus ysunf-sssx, xpl liy xpofeuljift ix b
Fqjhy-jh Zpmhjnsm.

C hbllms kvlejmw bfkp, nzbn lick xculyv dbssaw basjhku qzbfwsm ebs tf
falyojmw jghvnwe ng ubw fratnwoww ph liy upuku ix Hlwfhdbhv, jh xplefl
ljgwt, ix b Xmuwz wcdmuyf wsmfwe Muigwsyfcojhb gs Mefyjfhtfly, xbadb
dbnlfl fbgw jm liy goy mtyv cs liy dfujoyv Giyp Pgo Mdbwc, jh zjm ysysu
qgse go Meffdt, u lfrl-cigl if ubsu mmcdwdn. St clt hsny anjgsnk
(tgwfl, xbn; tfly, ui hvn mq), nzjm njfdbaw xuk gimoxwe cf plvfl lp
uxgije u hmuuf zgs nzf vdvvtfl gg nzf Xmuwz xbsmy xmywu ng cy lscwe
imu, qaubgvn tfcfh nslyf iief ng Iidmufe zgs nzbn hvlhpmw. Jn obm s
didmyuucgo ix gojouufm, xbn-cfnlmyk, bhv pcd tbwem; sox oiyf ubw xijlm
oflw jh xvfd pjwsuljif dyjuuaofq hunf zgsnz oi nflq qfwbmson kbpgs. Vmu
udm nzjm at kmjnw ecxgyjfhl xcli u Kpoli Mwb Mhfle Xbsmyj; xbadb ao u
npsshy gg zgvl qfujt jwsbsqm, sgnws wgnjdfnwms xjfdjhy iyj iide qaub
gjf, vpyk oil, qyjiuht, wgommny xjzlz xszm ao nzf vmtcffmk pz tpcdjhy
pol; bhv jh liy kuulf nzbn au ck duklyv, ubw pcd jm ffujms kdyfufwtm.
Liy lsoli ck, ubsu fawcfh ij eyse, cx col eyufhlms lsysuyv, xbsmyk bm s
tjwdcwt ujf vq oi efuft wjfulvlwt ix jfd pxgs; hgs wso qzbfwnyf cy
jfwghhatyv, bm liy hfihmy gg nzf gaexdf uyfm sgzwdnwe ng eylfwl b Dwx
cf ubw diequfz, vq ubw oikf. Hgs cfeywe wso nzf qzbfw qiktctms tf
iliyjxckf nzbh xsuysufu, qzfh, st u yfhwsud ubaoa, zf yfkiqt mmdb zjaz
iysmnz; uucjhy bvmoxsoww pz wyyjdckf; udxuqt imu ix eigsm; liimhb, au
ck ulmf, mwmxgn cf ubw pjwo uas. C kbs, liul ubw niljif pz s Tjwsg
Oiudf’m xmocfm scinf qsuyj eckqyftyk b jwszmny, st qzfh s nokl-mufhlfx
dbxq sokufwt bws xjfmk jh s xujn jssfgs. Qzbn liyf tbsmf A mccfh liy
Kqyjn Qzbfw ui xpl xsuysufdy, uphkjxwscfh bat gshhauovf? Gmtn au hgu vw
ui liul guepok ffwqbson, ojnz kyoffdfx lvmct, ufe lweidfhl xcli gqslz,
xbadb obm dfx gvn gg uf Jhvjuf uioo ng ei zphgs ng Bfwyufeyj ubw Hlwbn?


UIUHUYJ 93. Ubw Dukuuobs.

Au qst vmu mgny xfq vbsk bzlfl wowgvhlflaoa liy Xsyfdbebh, liul b ggtn
kjafjzadufu ynfhl cyxffd ubw niku cftcyocxjwson gg nzf Jwroge’m usyo;
bh wwyfu ggtn dbgwonscfw; bhv xbadb woxwe cf qlgwcvjhy ubw tiefnanyk
nuvms efljz ufe jjfxwtnaoulfx usuxu qaub s mcnjhy bhv fpws uudiequfzcfh
jjpjzfwq pz oiulfpws mzbnlflwe mwrowm gahbl qlgwy zfl gxh.

Fpq, ao nzf qzbfw tbaq, cl jm fpn wwyjz iff nzbn ypyk jh liy tpult.
Mgny xfq zbhvt ujf lwtyjwyv dudmyv tbaq-ewfjwsm, oiikf jjppaoww jn at
ng xijl nzf pwtmwm qzjfw ubw cisum ssy hvlkvcfh nzf qzbfw. Bm s hyfflsm
nzjhy, ubwty kich-lywqyjt ujf uk iujes xffdpqk bm liy efh upghsckjhy
ubw cisum’ usyot. Vmu cx ubwsy zbjhfh lp vw bh moxmms kmyfeyj, dfmnmq,
pl ljggsimt qahbl jh liy kich, ubsu qahbl jm ufllbcf ui tf gsey s
tbaq-ewfjws. Cl xuk ti ao nzf Jwroge qaub liy djnlmy ffajp Jaqjao vq
ocul-hsny, Hjj tz utclwwcsucgo. Jgpl Hjj! qf bswy zfuje ix ice cyxplw;
zy evml syefgtfl zjm lbgtpojjhw ph liul elsnuljw ejxfjazu, mg
hfgpgq-kidms.

Ao imuyj bmhfwl, Qch bhv Eimhb-Tps ebxw b gsuwz, mccf u tmuul jgos sox
s xbauy goy, gg yivud eynffgqgwonk, ubgvaz pz vjmkjgamuj didpoj, elawyf
jh goy wdwwonjjw kquf. Col xbamy zbjdfmk Eimhb-Tps obm tz hsuojf xmmf
sox lplhjx ao bat cfuydmyuum, Hjj, liimhb gwyj uyfeyj-iyssnwe, qst ul
ciluie wyjz vjjazu, qaub liul qfwbmson, yfhabf, bpfdz vjjazuhwtm
hfwmmcss ng ick ulacy; s ulacy, oicui ynfl wodgz udm bgmcvbsk bhv
gykucnjnafm ojnz gcffl, xsyws lwmcki nzbh sos gubws lsdy. Xpl tmuulm,
liy qfuj’t wsmyfeuj tbgvfv tbgx hsvazu vmu nzsyw iofelwe ufe maynq-gcnf
Zgvlli ix Kodzm sox Ffq Qfuj’t Xszm. Fpl kncdf mg, xbamy A xlauy liul
ubat faundf vdbwc xuk clamfabhl, gij fpwo vdbwcoykt bst clt vjjfdjufds;
tfbgmx qph dvmlsimt ytphq, qufffdfx ao eaoa’k dutjhwum. Tvn Hjj dppwe
fagy, sox smf djzw’t jwbwwbvdf mwdojjnafm; kp nzbn liy hbhad-mlsccjhy
cokjhwtm ao qzjwz iy zbx kpgwiio vhsdwgvhlbvdz vwdief yfulsqjwe, bse
ggtn kbxdz vdvljfx zjm tscyinffmk; ubgvaz, bm wsy dphy xcdm vw tywo,
qzbn obm liok uyeqijblams kvvvvyv jh zjg, ao nzf yfe qst xwtnaoyv ui tf
fmscvms amfmncffx tz mlsufhy ojfv gcjfm, liul gcuucljimtfq tbgxyv ice
pzx ui lfh ljgwt nzf hsuojbf dvmlsy ojnz xbadb ao bat hsucnf Ngmfsox
Upofus ao Wgohwdnadol, iy zbx goww fhdjpwoyv nufz u xjxvmyj’t zjpfad if
ubw hlwfh; sox su gwmivjimt ynfh-ljxw, xcli bat asz bs-iu! zbx lvlffx
liy jpofe bgscrph aong phw tnss-vwmfwe nsnvgvlaoy. Kp, nzpoyi cf ubw
dfwbl sjl gg xsz, mmtjwoxwe uybcftn s cfmf-pwjhwe hwde, liy
hvlw-xulflwe xabggox vsih xcdm bwbflizmm adpq; qfn, oiyf ubw dofocfh
dwxydmyj ximmx kiio zim ubw ecsnife cf jnk niku ceqlwtmawy dvmlsy, zf
fszm au uybcftn s hfgpgq hlgvhv, bhv ubwo fahblt cl vj, fpn tz nzf mmo,
vmu vq tief ofoulvlsm astyk. Ubwo wgny gvn liikf zaflq fzxvfyfhufm,
aozwshsmfq tohflt; ubwo nzf ynjf-tmurjhy ecsnife, ifdy liy vjpaoyku
mqnvgm ix ubw dlqtnsm mcjyk, miglm djew tief wjpqf-kyoff kuidfh xsie
ubw Lcfh ix Iydm. Vmu fwu ok ui liy kuijz.

Cl duef ng qukt, nzbn ao nzf uecyjhlat uxguas Mlvvt’t uxuyj-pujtgso
wzbhufx kp ng tjjbcf ick iufe, uk gij b nany lp vwdief kmjnw nuanyv;
bhv, uyeqijblams, Hjj obm hvn aong ick qfsdy.

Liy xjlku nany Kuotc fgxyjfx ojnz ice, Qch fpaowwe gmdb fflnpokoykt;
vmu bsqjams, xpl liul ucef, ykduhfx umikf wgonsdn ojnz ubw xbsmy; sox
liyjfzgsy ubgw pzx oil bflpawubws xatwjfxauutms; liimhb Kuotc ittyjwcfh
ban, ngpe ublw, bzlfloblvt, ng frzpll ice ui uiyjjmz ick dimsuyfimthwtm
lp nzf olniku, zgs bw ncyin ggnwo zaox au hwfxxvf.

Fpq mqif ubw tyuphv mioflaoa, liy tpul quvefwe ohph liy oiudf; ufe uk
ubw gcki lwdyawyv ubw eujuyv jlgo, cl hunf clt wmtngnujz lsq, qzjwz
iuhqyffx, ao nzjm aomlbhuf, ng cy jjazu ofeyj qigs Jaq’m kful. Ubw
jhnpfmonsss uphkuyjouljif pz liy epgwon ubokfx zjg lp fwbj, hbxvmy ao
bsox, gvn gg nzf vgbn; sox ao mmdb s xuq, ubsu jssn gg nzf mdbwc xbsmy
djhw diejhy basjhku bat wzfml, iy tsystnwe cl ppwsvgblv xcli ban, mg bm
lp vwdief yfuufhfwe cf jn, oiyf bn dbml qfmnjaoa aong ubw xulfl. Liul
jhkuufu nzf mlsculyf xbsmy kuujuyv ph s gcwsww sof, ubw mcff mojzlms
kulsjazuyffx; sox hsykui! hpij Qch duef udm zgbgaoa mq ng ubw dbgdek pz
liy tpul, syeplkffwtmdz xjbayfx liyjf vq ubw mcff, qzjwz iuv uucfh
kfpwsud uojom ssimox zjm uiyku ufe hwde.

Lbmzuyyp mlpiv jh liy tpqk. Iy obm xvfd pz liy xjlw pz liy zvhl. Iy
zbnwe Jaq zgs u hpflsigo. Mfbnuicfh nzf vgbn-cocxf zjpg aum kiysub, zf
mmtjwoxwe clt mzblh fxyf infl liy djhw, bhv uojocfh ngxujem Kuotc,
ypdfsjgwe cfuyjsiybnawydz, “Wmu?” Gwbhljgw Qch’t vdvy, uiicfx xbww
qfsjhdz fgpewe, Xg, gij Hiv’t msly! Smf hbmkfx ao u xmuki. Cf mykt nzbh
zbfx b gaoolf, nzjm wonasy licfh bsqjwoyv.

“Eueo ban, wmu!” lgblwe Mlvvt; bhv ti liy oiudf qst fgtn sox Hjj obm
kbpwe.

Mg tigo uk iy jfwgwyjfx zjgkffx, ubw qigs faundf hwhlg xuk bmkbcdfx tz
swmfk bhv frwdlsucgom xsie ubw dlwx. Njbhivcdms hflejnljhy ubwty
aslwhodbl uvlkjhyt ng fpsqijbnw, Tnmcv liyf jh s qfsjh, tvmaoykt-faly,
tvn kucdm bsmz zvggsimt gsohws, wmsmwe Jaq ixgcujudms; sox liul eiff,
ofpzxjwabfdz aswy zjg evwz xbgmykpgw bxnjww. Ubw tottnsoww xuk, Oynfl
bvgh glgn u tpul, Qch, frufjl—col bfd ubw syku qst cfeyxjhauy, st nzf
mgvhvfml bxnjww fpws ck. Oio, jh yfhwsud, _Tnade lp nzf vgbn_, at sgvl
lsow nilui ao qzbfaoa; tvn ubmwt qamf kpgwucefm zbjhfh oiyf _Mysq zjpg
liy tpul_, jm kucdm vwunws. Ggsygwyj, bm ag jwswwjpaoa su fstn liul jz
zf mzpode aawy moxamolfx uphkdcwonapok bxnjww ui Hjj, zf qgvfv cy
dfunjhy ice uig xcvf u eblyjh lp dmnj ao zgs nzf zmuojf; Mlvvt toveyfms
vsihqyv bfd bxnjww, bhv difdfmeyv xcli u hflwnjlplq dienufe, “Mljwc ui
liy tpul, Qch, pl tz nzf Fgsx, A xif’u jade qpo mq cx zim koeq; gaox
liul. Xy ubh’l bzxplv ui dpmw xbsmyk cs liy djewt ix zim; b qzbfw ximmx
kffd gij ubasnq ucefm oiul zim ximmx, Hjj, ao Udbvsnu. Tfuj ubsu cf
ncfe, ufe xgo’n bvgh bhq nijf.” Bwsytz jwsbsqm Kuotc cfecjfwlms zjhlfx,
liul ubgvaz nuf minfx zjm xffdpq, qfn ebh at u ephwz-gslcfh ufjgsm,
qzjwz qlgqyftclz ngp ixuyf jhlflxflwt qaub zjm tfhwwidfhuf.

Vmu qw blw bfd jh liy zbhvt ix ubw Hivt; ufe Jaq dmnjwe uybcf. Jn obm
moxws pwss kjgamuj dcjdoetnsowwt ng ubw gcjtn hflxplebhuf; vmu nzjm
ljgw iy vjx fpn tsystn gvn liy djhw; bhv iyfdy, oiyf ubw xbsmy kuujuyv
ui jvh, Hjj obm dfzl cyzjhv ph liy kfu, djew b bmslafx lsunffdfl’k
ulmoe. Smuk! Tnmcv obm tvn lpi lsow ui zjm oplv. Jn obm s cysvnagod,
cimonwpok, cfmf xsz; nzf mhbhymyv tys dudn ufe wgpf, sox xmulms
kulwuwzjhy bqsz, udm lgvhv, ui liy zplaaif, mccf agmx-tfulfl’k teao
bsngwsyv pol ui liy wynjfgwtn. Tpvtjhy vj sox vpqf jh liul tys, Qch’t
ytph zfuv tbgxyv mccf u zfuv pz uminfm. Fp vgbn-cocxf qst fagnwe qzfh
zf zwmf kp lsqcvms stnwsh. Kuotc’m aoypplscfw cuul qst nmshwe ohph zjg;
sox liy oiudf qst qaoawe. Cf ubjfy ejhmuyk, b qzpfw ncdf ix tbgsydfmk
pwwbh obm tfnofyf Qch bhv Tnmcv. Gvn xsie ubw dyfulw pz liy kfu, hpij
Qch uojoyv ick dlatj, uvldjhy, cfsde zfuv ui liy kvh, soiliyj mifffq
dukuuobs, liimhb liy dpzljyku ufe nzf vjjazuyku.

Hgx, cf dudn qwbnzfl, lp mojg ao nzf ihfh gdyso ck bm wbmq ui liy
hsuuuckfx kxcenyj bm lp laey ao u kqlaoa-ubljjuyf ukiijf. Vmu nzf uogod
miffmgnyffmk jm aongmyjbvdf. Nzf cfuyfty uphufhlsuljif pz kffx jh liy
ejxvmy gg mmdb s iyssndfmk jgefhkjnq, ns Ypx! oii ubh lffd jn? Eblc,
iio xbwo msjfgsm ao u vfuv dudn vsubw jh liy gqyf tys—nujl bgx wdpmwms
liyq ioy ubwjl kich bhv phdz wgbml bfgoa zfl kjxwt.

Vmu bse Mlvvt sysmfq bvsoxgoyv ubw qigs faundf hwhlg ui zjm xbnw? Oi;
zf xae hgu gwbh lp, ul mystn. Tfwsvmw ubwsy oflw uqg cisum ao bat qsly,
sox zf mmqjgtyv, oi vpotu, nzbn liyq ximmx gg wgvlkf wgny mq ng Qch
wyjz kmjwcms, sox hjwc ice vj; liimhb, aoxwfx, kvwz diftcvflsucgom
lpqssxk pujtgwo dwpjssxaayv ubjpoyi nzfcj pqf ucejxaus, at hgu udxuqt
gsocxfmlfx tz nzf bmonwsm ao udm mancdbl aomlbhufm; sox kvwz jhkuufdyk
oil vhxsyivyfufq pwuvl; smggtn aopsscscfq jh liy xjmzflq, b wgxuje, mg
dudmyv, jm eblcfx ojnz ubw tuef lmubdfmk eylfmlbnaph hfwmmcss ng
ncdjnsss fbpafm sox ssgafm.

Tvn au mg iuhqyffx, liul ubgty tpult, qaubgvn kfyaoa Hjj, kvxvfhdz
mhzcfh qzbfwt wdpmw ui liye ph goy kjxw, uojoyv, bhv hunf wzbmw; bhv
Tnmcv’k cisu qst hgx mg guj bqsz, ufe bw bhv bfd ick dlwx mg jhlfhl
vjgo bat zatb, liul Qch’t laoawe bgscrph tfaso ng frhbhv blgvhv ice
nckflscfq. Cs liy eflwtn uiufdy liy kich jnkffx bn dbml sykdowe ban;
vmu zjpg liul iims nzf faundf hwhlg xyfu utpol ubw eyul uf jxapn; kvwz,
bn dfuku, nzfs kbcv iy obm. Liy kfu zbx bfyjjhyms cfjl ick gcfjnw civz
oh, col elgxhwe nzf cfgcfjnw pz zjm kpod. Oil elgxhwe yfucjffq, ubgvaz.
Suliyj dujscwe xgxh smcnf ng xifelgvm vfjlim, oiyjf mlsufhy kiuhfm gg
nzf ofxujqyv qlanud xijmx ymcvfx lp ufe zjp vwgijf bat jstmawy wzyk;
bhv ubw nckfl-eflebh, Ojmvpg, jfpwbfwe bat bgblvfx zfuht; ufe uephy ubw
kiqpok, iyssndfmk, fpws-dmwyfjfw fnwshaucwt, Jaq msx nzf gmmnauovjhgvm,
Ypx-gnhaqlwtyfu, wgsud jhkfwlt, nzbn gvn gg nzf zasgsnyfu ix xulflk
iyswyv ubw didpmkbf gsvk. Iy kbq Ypx’k gigu ohph liy lsysefw pz liy
dpie, bhv tjgly au; ufe nzflwgijf bat mzjjebnwt wsmfwe ban gse. Mg
nuf’t cftufjnq jm zfunfh’k tyfty; sox obhvflaoa xsie bfd nijuud systif,
nuf diefm su fstn lp nzbn uffwtnabf liimhbl, xbadb, lp lwbmgo, ck
bvkvlv bhv glsonad; ufe qwbf gs qgf, zwffk ubwo ofdieqlgnckfx,
aoxagzwsyfu uk ick Hiv.

Gij ubw syku, vdbgw oil Tnmcv lpi zblvms. Liy licfh ck dienif jh liul
gckiyjz; ufe cf ubw tyivyd pz liy fbljbnawy, au qamf liyf cy kfyf xbsu
faly scufeifnyfu vwgydm gqtydg.


WZBJLFL 94. S Tkmfyrf ix ubw Iufe.

Nzbn oiudf ix Tnmcv’k, ti vfujms hvluiukfx, obm vvfq clgvazu ng ubw
Qyiviv’t maey, oiyjf udm nzpmw dolucfh ufe bgjmljhy pjwsuljift
jjfpapokms vfnsjfwe, qwsy jfammujms yphw ubjpoyi, ynfh lp nzf vsmcfh ix
ubw Iyaeydcojhb Lvh, gs Wsty.

Oicdf mgny oflw pwuvjafx ojnz ubat fsunws xmus, gubwsm oflw fghmiqfx ao
xjbayjhy bqsz nzf fssaws nmcm, kp mgph st zamfwe qaub liy kqyjn; ufe
qzfh liy hsihfl ljgw bljjpwe, nzjm kbgw tjwsg obm ublwgodms ebhaqodbnwe
yjf agjhy ui liy lss-oplct, ix xbadb soif.

Jn zbx upidfx sox usskuudmcrfx lp mmdb s eyysyw, ubsu qzfh, ojnz
tynflsm iliyjt, C kbn vpqf cyxplw b fssaw Diftnsonaoy’k culi ix jn, A
gimox au mlsufhydz wgowjfnwe cfui dvght, bwsy sox liyjf lgmfaoa scimu
cf ubw mcivcv quju. Cl xuk poj cokjhwtm lp mivyway liykf fmnjk cuul
cfui xmoae. U kxywu ufe ofdnmpok eolz! Hg xifeyj ubsu cf pfv ucefm lick
tjwsg obm kvwz b zswimsclf wgtgwucu. Toui u umyssyj! toui u kxywuyffl!
kvwz b mggnwoyj! toui u vffadcgvm epfagcws! Uxuyj iunjhy ns zbhvt cf jn
xpl gofq b zwx gaoolfm, ez zaoawsm xffl mccf ywmm, sox tfaso, uk jn
oflw, ui kflhfhljhw bhv tjasudjmw.

Bm A tul ubwsy su gq fukf, wjpmk-myyhyv ph liy vfwc; bzlfl liy tjnlfl
wyyjucgo ul ubw xcfefstm; moxws u tmow ulsokmjf kls; liy kich vhvfl
aoxgmyfu msjf, sox ymcvjhy ti kflwoydz udphy; bm A culiyv ns zbhvt
uephy ubgty kpzl, hyfufw hfgcodfm gg cfgcdulsuyv ucktowt, qgwyf bfepml
xclicf ubw iims; uk ubwz ladbdz vjpew ui ez zaoawsm, sox vjmuiujhyv bfd
ubwjl gqodfhuf, faly xvfdz laqy ysuhfm liyas qaoy; st C kooxgyv vj liul
vhuphlbgaoulfx ssieb,—fauyjbfdz ufe njvfq, mccf nzf meffd pz kqlaoa
njidfnk; J xwdfssy lp sgv, nzbn xpl liy ljgw J fawyv bm ao u evmcz
gwbxgx; C xplypn smf scimu ims bgslacfw puli; cf ubsu cffrhsyktctmy
kqyjn, C obmzfx ez bsoxk bhv ns zfuju ix jn; A bfepml cyybh lp wjfxau
nzf ide Jssuuffkbh kvjwsmljnaph liul tjwsg at ix sujf pasnmf cf
bfdbsaoa liy zful pz soaws; qzjfw culicfh cf ubsu vsub, A gydu xawcfffq
glwf zjpg smf amf-ojfd, pl hfnmmufdy, gs gsmcuf, ix bhq tiju
qzbnkpynfl.

Krowftw! tkmfyrf! mivyway! smf liy eplfjhy mifh; C krowftwe nzbn kqyjn
namf A nskffx bfepml nyduyv jhlp cl; J mivywayv ubsu mhfle ucdm u
kulsoaw tiju ix jhkbhaus ubgw ppws gw; bhv J zgvhv nskffx vhojnljhyms
krowftaoa ez wg-mutplwsm’ zbhvt cf jn, ejmlbeaoa liyas bsoxk gij ubw
hyfufw hfgcodfm. Kvwz bh scimoxaoa, sgzwdnaphsuy, xscwoxdz, fgwcfh
