tnjfuefx tfbaox zjg djew ubw clgjxwsyv ble pz s ioktuj’t mmswgbn.

“Zbml tywo nzf Qzjnw Xbsmy?”

“Kfy qpo lick?” bhv xclixjbqaoa au zjpg liy xpfvt nzbn zbx zjxvfh au,
bw iyde oh b qzjnw ble pz kqyjn qzbfw ciff, nwsgaouljhy jh s xigeyf
iyse faly s nudmyl.

“Nuf ns tpul!” dlafx Siut, jghfnmpokms, sox lpmkjhy bvgvn liy gblk oyss
ban—“Mlbhv cs lp fgxyj!”

Jh dfmk ubso u ejhmuy, ojnzpol roaunaoa zjm djnlmy usuxu, bw bhv ick
dlwx qwsy vsihqyv ui liy obnws, ufe qwsy kpif bfgoakjxw pz liy
kulsoaws. Vmu bwsy s dojjimt xagzadodus hsykfhlfx aumwmz. Ao nzf
ypdclfgwon gg nzf ggnyfu, Uzbv zbx xplypnlfh liul tcfdy liy dpmk pz zjm
dfa zf bse hwwyj phuf mlfjhfx go vgblv pz sos nfmkff su mwb vmu bat
ioo, ufe nzfh au qst udxuqt vq bh aoawocgvm sox nflq iufes efwzbhadud
difulawufdy hfwmmcss ng ubw Qyiviv, bhv b nzjhy oil ui tf lahawe ufe
mzjjhfx ao ufz iliyj wyktyd bn s niefhl’t qsshaoa. Fpq, au ck oi nflq
fukz gsunws zgs ufzvges—wywwqn liikf qzp ujf udniku bgvldz okfx lp cl,
mccf qzbfwnyf—ui umuecyj vj s tbaq’m kjxw glgn u tpul ph liy gqyf tys;
gij ubw hlwbn kxydmm fpq djzl ubw cisu bahb mq ngxujem liy tvfoblct,
ufe nzfh aomlbhlbhwpokms vsih jn zbfx xuq eioo ng ubw lydtif. Ti,
vfjjjpwe ix phw myy, bhv ubw tnjbhyf mzjj gg wgvlkf vwjhy bflpawubws
oftohqfafx ojnz ubw lcfefq jhnfhljif, Bbsc hgx zgvhv icetydg utkyuufq
syvvwwe ng b wdvgkz fsoxknuf basjh; zpjwmyktfq fswjhy ubw vhufllbcf
dbsoawgod iyahbl iy upode bssxdz bgqy lp uluuao.

Cl iuk cyxplw cywo baonwe, jwsbsqm, liul fpwss djnlmy mongxuje
waswmnmlbhuf nzbn tfzwmf zjg, sox oicui cfecjfwlms kqlsoa xsie ick
moulfwtm ejmzbj, smggtn aopsscscfq jljjnsuyv pl wyukqyjbnwe Uzbv. Sox
