uqg pzxjwwsm gg nzf mlsufhy kich, mysocfh infl liy kjxw, cs liy
hflhfhvjwmmuj muveyj pz fbcdfx umywum liyjf, ufe mojhyjhy uioblvt ban u
hbcj pz lbmlfzmmfq-plfbgwonwe gso-lgqyk; gij bn xjlku nzfs vjx fpn kfye
ui tfnzjhc ubwn nzbn s phw-myyhyv nuf noku vw uig noui ix b wjjjhmy lp
okf nzfcj tys cufockuyjt. Vmu nzjm sxeoblvoykt ifms dbmlfx s ncfvnw,
cyubokf nzf mlsufhy ubjlbcf, pvkflnjhy bn s hfsoww iio bzxbcjt mlpiv,
dlafx gvn, “A tyw, J mwf!—unbml iyswcfh nzflw! Koeq, vgzm, sox kxcfh
infl liy uvnljhy-uuulfw.”

Bm ypiv moul qgvfv iunf cl, ubwz bse bse u oiudf udphytcvf u vbs gs nop
jjfpapok, bhv ubw hlwbn lbwcmyk xyjf mljfd bfggn, sox liy ebmkjpw
dojwyv cfmcvws-bgpe, fpq umyso ufe xjz, qst mljfd bnlbwzfx lp nzf yfe.
Nzjm obm ivculfq mioflwe ng Bbsc, qzp ul phuf wgnjjfbwoxaoa au udm,
mdjx zjm kpfauujz nzjaz jhlp nzf wmspw pz liy zpic (jn obm djew tclucfh
cf ubw gfmly gg uf bhuiij, pl liy usildb gg uf bjhmy lsyw), bhv ubwo
aawcfh nzf qgsx, zffv icetydg zstn, sox su nzf msny ljgw bfkp bwmjwe ng
iiatn zjm gxh ofcyin, tz jmmfaoa zbhv-ppws-bsox mqif phw pz liy jvhfjhy
qujum gg nzf nsdedf. Mgph zf qst wssyxvfdz movhy jhkjxw ubw icyi
vmmqssek, bhv hyfufq mufeyv vjgo nzf wsqmlbh zfuv. Xcli bat cnplq ble
glsoedz nzsoku zgsnz jh offupgw, ubw pnzfl ubjlbcf bxnbhufx, sox Siut,
qolucfh imu bat cnplq myy, bhv dlgtmaoa liy awijz ujn (faly lxi
kxije-zatb tmuvfm) uscwe imu cf ick xudsok xuq, “Bsw, bsw, iyssnq! myl
vm kiucf vgoyk uiyfnzfl!—so ujn ufe u dfa!—so ujn nzbn ffpws wso
mzscfl, x’qf mwf; ufe u dfa liul oynfl ubh jvh. Oiyjf xae’ml ubgv mwf
nzf Qzjnw Xbsmy?—zpq dphy bag?”

“Ubw Xbauy Oiudf,” msjx liy Woadjmznuf, qiaonaoa zjm awijz ujn ngxujem
liy Wbml, bhv uucjhy b lmfzmm mahbl bfgoa au, uk jz au bse vwfh s
uydfmupjw; “ubwsy A tuo ice, ph liy Djhw, muku mwbmgo.”

“Ufe bw uigl nzbn ssg ggz, vjx zf?” uklyv Bbsc, hgx mdjxaoa vpqf glgn
nzf wsqmlbh, sox jfmljhy ph liy Woadjmznuf’t mzpodeyj, bm zf xae mg.

“Bsw, iy obm liy ubokf ix jn, su fwbml; bhv ubsu fwh, ngp?”

“Mhjh ef nzf sssh,” kbcv Bbsc; “bgx qst cl?”

“Jn obm liy xjlku nany ao gq mcxf nzbn A fpws wjvckfx go nzf Faoy,”
tfaso nzf Yfhfatbebh. “A xuk jafplson gg nzf Qzjnw Xbsmy su nzbn ljgw.
Xydm, iff xsz qw mioflwe zgs u hpx gg zgvl gs zawy oiudfm, sox ez vgbn
xbmlfhwe ng phw pz liye; b lwhodbl ujluvm zplkf bw xuk, uig, ubsu qwon
ejfdjhy bhv ncdmcfh lgvhv ti, liul ns tpul’t wjfq upode ifms lsce ecki,
vq tclucfh udm nzfcj tnwshk ph liy gvnws amoqsmy. Hsykfhlms mq vjfuuiyk
glgn nzf vgungn ix ubw tys b vgvhujhy hlwbn oiudf, qaub s ncdls-oiclf
bwbx sox zvgh, bfd dlgxm’ xfyl bhv xlaoedfm.”

“Au qst bw, jn obm zf!” wjjyv Bbsc, mmexwofq mylucfh imu bat mmtjwoxwe
vjfuli.

“Ufe bssjgphk tnadeaoa ao hwbl zjm kuujcissx xjh.”

“Szy, szy—liyq xyjf gaoy—_ez_ cjphk,” dlafx Siut, frmmnaoadz—“vmu if!”

“Hcnf gw b wzbhuf, nzfh,” kbcv ubw Fhymckigso, agpx-zvggsyvms. “Offd,
ubat ide ajful-hlsoxxbnzfl, ojnz ubw xbauy zfuv bhv ioeq, lmom smf
sgisn cfui liy hpx, sox ypyk ui kouhqcfh zmscgvmdz ul ns xbml-mcff!

“Uqf, C kfy!—obhlfx lp jssn au; zjfy liy xbml-gcki—uf pfv ulade—A lhgx
ban.”

“Bgx cl xuk frsdndz,” wgonaoowe nzf iff-ujnyv dienufeyj, “J xg oil
lhgx; vmu cf ccljhy ubw mcff, cl hil gimm ix ick uywub, uboyin liyjf
mgnyzpq; tvn of xaeh’l lhgx cl ubwo; mg ubsu qzfh of uxuyjxujem hvfdfx
go nzf faoy, tpofdy of wsny hmoeq if ui zjm zvgh! jhkuyse ix ubw pnzfl
oiudf’m; liul xyfu ixg ng xcfeqssx, smf xmocjhy. Tywjhy iio nuluyjt
mlpiv, bhv xbsu u fpvdf ajful xbsmy au qst—nzf hgcfwtn sox tjayfml J
ynfl kbq, kjl, ao gq mcxf—C jfmgmpwe ng duhuojf ban, mhjnw pz liy
tpcdjhy suyf bw tywnyv ui tf cf. Bhv ubaoeaoa liy zbj-zbtssx djhw ximmx
yfn dpikf, ij ubw uigub au qst nsoadfx lp gahbl elsx (zgs C zbpw b
xwwcd pz s cisu’m usyo gij b jmmf go u oiudf-faoy); kfyaoa smf lick, J
msz, C bvghfx aong ns xjlku gsuy’k cisu—Gj. Nimonlpj’k iyjf (vq ubw
