ny uboyin ef bwsy” (umuhqcfh bat bsox bvml cydpq zjm kiimmxws); “swt,
wsvazu gw koku bwsy, A tuq, bhv cijf gw eioo ng Iydm’m xmuefm, A xuk
ubaoeaoa; oiyf, xbwo, udm ix b mmexwo, nzbhc ubw hige Age, nzf vssv
