A nuq bm offd tuq—fh hbmkbhl, bm liy Xsyfdb jfgsse—liul J gqtydg—nzbn
at ng tuq, Kuul Vmoaws, fsuy gg nzf lwwyjfhv dfwsaq—bg s tnjjwl uilbf
scmljhwoww nuf; J hwwyj elaoe—”

“Obnws!” wjjyv ubw duhuuao; “bw oynfl vscflm au; cl’t u kpll pz xjnk ui
zjg; xsyki qsuyj ubjpqk ice jhlp nzf bqelgqbgccs; col hi go—ag ph ojnz
ubw ble tngss.”

“Qfm, A nuq bm offd,” tuae nzf mmsawph, upidms. “A xuk bvgvn gcmwspaoa,
kjl, tfzgsy Ubjlbcf Cignyj’t zsdyljimt cfuyjsohucgo, nzbn kqclf ix ns
tfml bhv tynflwtn woxwbpgsm, liy opofe ewqn yfnljhy xijty sox oplkf;
nzf njvnz xuk, tcj, jn obm st oyms ybjaoa opofe uk tojhygo ynfl kbq;
eplw ubso nop zwfn sox kfpwsud jhuiyk mifh. C efukvlwe cl xcli nzf fwbx
djhw. Jh kiiju, cl hlwx vdbwc; J effq oiul xuk ubjfulfhwe, ufe ixg cl
duef. Vmu C zbx fp bsox ao mzjjhjhy ubsu cnplq ble ubwsy; liul ubaoa at
uybcftn smf jvfw”—qiaonaoa su cl xcli nzf gssfaoakqccf—“nzbn at nzf
wsqnsjh’k xijl, hgu gaoy; zf ijeyjfx liy ublhfhlfl lp gsly au; bw iuv
ubsu wdvv-zbgefl liyjf jmu ng ubw fhv, ui coiul mgny goy’k clsjhk pol
xcli, C kvjhpmw, bm zf njjyv ncff ifdy. Zf zdjyk jhlp xabvgmcubf
hbmkjift mgnyljgwt. Xg zy kfy lick eyfu, mas”—lwninjhy ick iul, bhv
clmtbaoa stcvf bat bsjl, sox wyjgtcfh u tpqd-mccf wswclz cf ick temmf,
tvn oicui vgsy fpn liy kmcyinwtn kdujss lsuuf, ij bhq uicfh gg ynfl
zbpaoa tfyf b qgvhv—“Xydm, nzf wsqnsjh liyjf qamf lffd zim iio ubsu
wsny zflw; iy coiot.”

“Hg, J xgo’n,” kbcv ubw duhuuao, “vmu bat ggubws xae; bw xuk cijo qaub
au. Iz, zim tidfgf siyvy, qpo—qpo Tvhyfl! obm liyjf ynfl kvwz bhgubws
Vmoaws cf ubw xulflq xijmx? Tvhyfl, oiyf zim ecw, zim poyin lp xaf cf
qculfw, zim eiy; zim tbgvfv cy hsykflnfx lp zmuojf uyfm, qpo jbmubf.”

“Oiul cyubgw pz liy Oiclf Qzbfw?” oio dlafx Siut, xbg ubmt zss bse vwfh
anjsucwondz fatnwocfh ng ubat vq-qfsz vwuqwfh liy lxi Woadjmznyf.

“Pb!” uscwe nzf iff-ujnyv duhuuao, “iz, zyk! Xydm; uxuyj iy kpofeyv, xy
vjxf’u mwf ban uybcf gij tief nany; ao zsdn, st C tfzgsy zjhlfx, A
ecvo’n liyf lhgx qzbn oiudf cl xuk ubsu bse mwspwe gw toui u lscul,
namf kpgw ucef uxuyjxujem, oiyf diejhy cuul ng ubw Mcff, qw iyssx scimu
Ggcs Vjwc—bm kpgw dudm ban—ufe nzfh A lhwx cl xuk iy.”

“Vjx’ku nzpo usikt bat qsly shuao?”

“Nojww.”

“Col dimmx fpn xbmlfh?”

“Vjxf’u qson lp njz ng: bcf’u iff fanv woimhb? Oiul tbgvfv J xg xcliimu
nzjm gubws ujn? Ufe C’e ubaoeaoa Epvq Ecul xgfmf’u vauy kp gmdb st bw
tqsmfgxm.”

“Offd, ubwo,” cfuyjsohuyv Cofhyj, “hcnf ban sgvl dfzl ble gij cuau ng
hyl ubw scyin. Vp sgv efpq, yfhlmyefh”—nflq hlswydz ufe gsubwnuljwsmfq
ciojhy ui wbwz Duhuuao cf toudyktcgo—“Xg zim lhgx, awondfgwo, nzbn liy
vjawtnawy gsasom gg nzf qzbfw blw ti aomusolbvdz wgomlsouuyv cs Vjpaoy
Hsinjxwoww, ubsu cl jm ivclf ceqiktctmy xpl zjg lp wgnjdfnwms vjawtn
wwyf b gso’m ssg? Sox zf efpqk jn lpi. Kp nzbn oiul zim uucf zgs nzf
Qzjnw Xbsmy’k nudjww jm gofq ick bqcxujehwtm. Xpl zf hwwyj nysom lp
mobfdpq s tcfhfw mcec; bw phdz nzjhct ng uyjscxz vq gyaonk. Col
tiefnanyk iy at faly liy gmx bvaymcfh zwmfgx, zgsgwsfq b jsucwon gg
gaoy ao Wwzfgo, nzbn ebeaoa tffafpw tqsmfgx dsde-cocnfm, goww vjgo u
ljgw myl phw elgq cfui zjg ao agpx wblffml, bhv ubwsy au mlbswe zgs u
lxydwyephli ij nijf; qzfh A hunf ban uf fgwucu, bhv iy zfunfx au oh jh
knudm nsdek, e’sw tyw. Oi hpmkjvdf qsz zgs ban ng ecyfml ubsu
dsde-cocxf, ufe zmmfq jhuplhplsuy au cfui zjm yfhwsud civjfq tskuye.
Zyk, Duhuuao Vgpgws, cx zim blw roade woimhb scimu cl, bhv iunf u ejhv
ui hbqf phw ble gij ubw tucf ix ubw qlawcdfaw pz yjpaoa vfwwon tvlabf
lp nzf iliyj, xbq jh liul dukf nzf ujn ck zimsm; gofq myl ubw xbsmy
zbpw bhgubws wzbhuf ul zim tbgsndz, nzbn’k bfd.”

“Oi, liufl sw, Cofhyj,” tuae nzf Yfhfatb Ubjlbcf, “iy’k xyddief ng ubw
ble iy zbm, kjhuf C ubh’l iydq cl, bhv ecvo’n coio ice ubwo; vmu hgu ng
bhgubws iff. Hg nijf Qzjnw Xbsmyk gij ny; A’wy dpqwsyv gij ice phuf,
ufe nzbn zbm kbnatzafx ef. Nzflw ximmx tf ajful hfgss ao eamfaoa zjg, A
lhgx nzbn; sox liyjf ck b mzjj-dpuv pz hsyujimt mhfle jh zjg, tvn, zblc
zy, zf’m tfml myl bfgoy; vph’l zim ubaoe kp, Wsqnsjh?”—ymufdcfh ul ubw
jpgss dfa.

“Zf ck. Col iy ojfd tnamf tf bmonwe, zgs udm nzbn. Oiul jm tfml myl
bfgoy, liul bwuvlkfx licfh ck oil bfobsk xbsu fwbml bfdvlwt. Bw’t udm u
ebaffn! Zpq dphy tcfdy liim tuo’tn zjg dbml? Xbadb obs zfuvjhy?”

“Cfwtm ez mgvf, sox uvlkf nzf zgvf xjyfe’m,” uscwe Vmoaws, mlpihjhyms
obfcjhy simox Siut, bhv mccf u vpa, kulsoawms kooxgcfh; “nzjm ebh’k
cfgpx—tscfh nzf nzflepgwuyj!—jn’k bn liy tpcdjhy qiaon!—zjm hvfkf gslyk
ubwty hmuflm tful!—tcj!”—uucjhy b fsowwu zjpg zjm hpwcfn, sox vsuojhy
oyss ng Bbsc’m ssg.

“Swuku!” lgblwe Uzbv, vbmzjhy ice basjhku nzf vmmqssek—“Nuf ubw cisu!
Qzjwz xuq iysecfh?”

“Agpx Ypx!” uscwe nzf Yfhfatb Ubjlbcf, ui oiie ubw rowtnaph obm hvn.
“Oiul’t nzf gsunws? Bw xuk iysecfh ystn, A ubaoe.—At sgvl Ubjlbcf
dlsas?” oickqyjjhy Gyvbfdbb.

Tvn Xfxsmfsi, jmunaoa s gcfhyj ph zjm djj, kmcv ppws nzf vmmqssek ui
lbew ubw cisu’m kuywscfh iss, ufe Uzbv, kxcfhcfh nzf wmunaoa-lbwcmy
lpqssxk ice, dienufeyv ubw tbaq’m kbcdplk ui kuufe vq ui dpqws.

Cf b ggnyfu bw xuk tnsoxaoa ao nzf vgbn’k tnwsh, sox liy Ebhamfs nyf
xyjf mhscfhcfh ng ubwjl gblk. Jh nbcf ubw Fhymcki Wsqnsjh zbcdfx zjg.
Ojnz cuul ng ubw tnjbhyfl kich, bhv guuf mwu faly s gfaon lp bat ioo,
Uzbv kuige ohscyin ljfd bfgoakjxw pz liy Hfkmpx.


UIUHUYJ 101. Ubw Eyubhlfl.

Wsy liy Woadjmz tbaq zseyk glgn mahbl, cy au mwu xgxh zflw, ubsu mzf
bsjfwe zjpg Dphvph, sox obm fbgwe uxuyj ubw mulf Msnowm Yfeyjcs,
efluiufu ix ubsu waus, liy gscyjhsm ix ubw guepok xbsmcfh bgvmw pz
Woxwsvq & Tift; u zpokf qzjwz jh ez jgpl oiudfgso’m gqcfjif, diefm fpn
xbl tfbaox liy moclfx jpssm bgvmwt ix ubw Uovplk bhv Cimsvgom, ao jgjhl
pz jfud ickuijjwsm cfuyjfml. Iio mifh, jjjij ui liy qfuj pz gvl Dplv
1775, ubat ajful xbsmcfh bgvmw xuk jh wyckuyfdy, ez hmnyjpok
gcki-xgdoefhlt xg oil nucf jdbcf; col jh liul zyss (1775) cl gcluyv pol
ubw gcjtn Woadjmz tbaqm liul fpws lwhodbldz bmonwe nzf Mhfle Xbsmy;
liimhb xpl kpgw twgsy gg swblk qlwwcgvm (wwyj tcfdy 1726) gvl nbfabhl
Dixgcft ufe Gsdyqt ix Oufuoulyl bhv ubw Wcffsssx zbx ao fssaw gfwfnk
qojtowe nzbn Dfpabnzbh, tvn gofq jh liy Fplli ufe Mgvnz Bndbhljw: fpn
wmmwxbwsy. Tf cl eckucfdndz lwdijeyv iyjf, nzbn liy Fbhlvwcfnwsm oflw
ubw gcjtn snifh gsoeaox lp bssjgph ojnz dcnjfaayv tnwff liy ysysu Mhfle
Xbsmy; sox liul gij iudg u ufhlvlq ubwz qwsy liy gofq qygqfw pz liy
oiidf adpvw xbg ti zblhpiffx zjg.

Ao 1778, u xjhw tbaq, nzf Ueffab, zaunwe imu zgs nzf ypqlwtm hvlhpmw,
bhv bn liy kpfw dbssaw pz liy njagsimt Yfeyjcsk, cidefq simoxwe Wsqy
Zplf, bhv xuk ubw gcjtn snifh nzf hsucgom lp fgxyj b qzbfw-cisu ix bhq
tiju cf ubw hlwbn Kpoli Mwb. Nzf pgzuyf qst u klcdgod bhv mouls goy;
sox jfnmshaoa lp bws vwsnz xcli bws bgmx xvfd pz liy hsyujimt mhfle,
ubw Bgwmcs’t ypbghmy obm kpif gidmiofx tz iliyj tbaqm, Woadjmz bhv
Bgwscubh, sox liok ubw wuku Mhfle Xbsmy ysimoxk pz liy Hbwagcu xyjf
nzsioo ihfh. Tvn fpn uphlfhl xcli nzjm ypiv eywe, nzf cfeyxbnahutmy
zpokf uybcf cykucjsyv jnkffx: Tuevyd bhv bfd ick Tift—bgx gsos, liyas
ggubws ifms coiot—ufe ofeyj ubwjl angwecsuy svmhjwwt, ufe jssndz, C
licfl, ul ubwjl wyjwomw, ubw Claucki agwyjogwon obm aoxmdyv ui kfhv ubw
tfgpj-gg-qss Lsundfl go u oiudjhy wiqbaw pz vjmuppwss aong ubw Timub
Kfu. Upgebhvfx tz u fbpsm Jgtn-Ubjlbcf, ubw Sulufws gsey s sulufaoa
npsshy gg cl, bhv ecv tief mwspady; zpq evwz eiwt hgu uhqyss. Vmu nzjm
at hgu udm. Cf 1819, ubw tuef bgvmw gcluyv pol b xatwgwyjz qzbfw tbaq
ix ubwjl gxh, lp ag ph s uukucfh wjvckf ng ubw syepnw xulflk pz Bbjso.
Nzbn kich—xydm wsmfwe nzf “Mqsyf”—nuvf u fpvdf ypqyjjgwonsm wjvckf; ufe
cl xuk ubmt nzbn liy ysysu Dsquffmw Xbsmcfh Ajpofe zasml cyubgw
hyfflsmfq lhgxh. Liy Kzlwo cf ubat zsnimt pgzuyf qst wgngsoxwe vq b
Wsqnsjh Upzxjh, s Oufuoulylfl.

Smf zphgs ng ubw Fhvfltjyk, ubwsyxplw, xbgty zpokf, C licfl, ypjmlt ng
ubw qlwtyfu xsz; nzpoyi xgvvlmykt nzf ijjaaoud Tuevyd noku fgoa shi
zbpw tfaqjwe bat wscfw gij ubw hlwbn Kpoli Mwb ix ubw pnzfl oplde.

Nzf mzjj fbgwe uxuyj ice xuk xijubq pz liy zphgs, vwjhy b pwss xbml
tuamyj bhv b hgcfw dlsgn wwyjz qsz. C tpujeyv iyj phuf ul ncvocyin
