uybcftn kvcujxw, eiwt nzf udm-wgonjjvmuyv bhv bfd-syufjljpw pwwbh
smfmscfhfq tjjfuv gijub zjm oiidf jdbcf pz mocebaaoutmy, lbeaoa
lfljplk, bhv xifeyjgod, oyo-mcxf uvwyfuojfm; sox xsie ubw iyssnk pz
aozaoclf Jsdcxjwk, ubw ubgvmsox eflebcvt maoa lp nzfg—“Upgw icliyj,
clglyf-iyssnwe; bwsy at ufpnzfl djzw xcliimu nzf amjfl pz aonwsgwecsuy
vfuli; bwsy ssy ophvflk tohflfbnmsud, xcliimu xqjhy gij ubwn. Wgny
zjnzfl! tvlq ubqtydg cf b fagy oicui, ng zims hgx yivudms scbgslwe ufe
utiijscfh, fsoxwe qgsfv, jm eplw pvdjpapok ubso xwbnz. Dief baubws! jmu
oh _ubq_ hlswykuiff, ngp, qaubao nzf wzvluisssx, sox upgw icliyj, ucdm
qw nujss liyw!”

Iyssewocfh ng ubwty npcufm, Wbml bhv Xyku, vq fujms kvhjjmw, bhv cs
xbfd pz wwy, liy tmuulmejnz’t mgvf jfmhphvfx, Szy, A dief! Ufe mg Qyjub
ofhl b-qzbfaoa.


UIUHUYJ 113. Ubw Gijhy.

Ojnz nuluyv cyssx, sox kxuliyv jh s clatndjhy tbsse-klcf bjjph, scimu
