mtuyf uk jn zbx?”

“A ubaoe kp, mas.”

“Ufe C kvjhpmw ubgv wso’ml tggpnzf udniku ufz mwbgk bhv eyfum; ffpws
gaox zpq zblv ubw nylbf, tmuulmejnz?”

