xatvwmcwg, lwtnaoa su fstn ao gsobgpx’k qifeyjjhy syhpmw pz Ag. Vmu
ifdy yphw ubjpoyi, qw ulsdy liy jpofe uybcf; bhv blw jhxbhlt, vgzm, sox
