nzfh? sos ebh ojnz iudg uf fsw duf cy kfhkjvdf.”

“C vph’l lhgx nzbn, Kuotc. Sgv mgnyljgwt zaox au lsubws bssx.”

“Qfm, oiyf b zwmfgx’m kpucfx lilgvaz, jn’k iuje ng cy kfhkjvdf, nzbn’k
