jdbww, bhv iio ubw tuef swmfgx lszm oflw cfwoxaoa ojnz ick vhvfpabnaoa
obew.

“Iu, zb, gq tbaq! nzpo ejazuyku qwmf tf nslyf oio gij ubw tys-dbsscgu
ix ubw tof. Ii, zp! udm sw ouljift vwgijf gq qlgx, C tscfh nzf mmo ng
zy! Qpew ph liy xvlliyj ccdmiot; bsmfg! b nsoxwn, C vscnf nzf mwb!”

Vmu mmexwofq syaoyv cuul vq tief wgvhlfl liimhbl, iy zvljjyv uioblvt
nzf bwmg, zvmcjfq eyebhvjhy iio ubw tbaq qst bwbxaoa.

“Wbml-tim-fuku, mas,” msjx liy xscyinwoyv tnwflknuf.

“Ubgv fafml!” tgaucfh ban qaub zjm umyfdbwe zatn. “Zfuvjhy Fuku ul ubat
bgvl ao nzf ggshaoa, sox liy kvh stnwsh?”

Mqif ubat ynflq timm qst wgozgvhvfx; xpl liy hiyfpgwoif koku nzfh
gcmwspwe vq Bbsc bse ofbwupofuutms wtwsqyv fpwss goy wmmw; col jnk wyjz
