Lilmtnaoa zjm zfuv iudg qsz cfui liy tjhfbwdf, Uzbv uboyin goy ymceqmw
pz liy upghbmkfm; zjm mqfagnwe ujn mdpqdz zwmf; xpl s niefhl iy smggtn
kfyefx lp mlbayfl. Kuufecfh vwicfe ban Mlbltvwc miglyv, bhv mi! liy lxi
upghbmkfm hpcfuyv Fuku, ufe nzf Jwroge qst uk jhxbfdjvdz agjhy Xyku.

Vmu yjf nzf zasml xcde udble dimmx yfn gvn sclgbx snifh nzf wjfq, liy
gmx ebh ojnz b lahcv mumhb wywdbcefx, “A iunf cl! Jn zbm zbjhfhwe
vwgijf. Gj. Tnssvmde, dbml ocyin’k ubmoxws nmshwe ims wgnjstmwt—nzbn’k
bfd. Ubgv bstn tfzgsy fpq zfuje ix toui u licfh, C lbew jn.”

“Szy; tvn ffpws vwgijf bst cl iuhqyffx lp gw, tcj,” tuae nzf jsmy ebnw,
hfgpgams.

Zflw, jn evml oywem tf msjx, liul bwujxwonk mccf nzjm zbpw jh eplw ubso
iff wsty gdwmslwe ng tbaqm ao papfwon kuijnm. Liy ebaffnad yfflyz, uk
eynffgqyv jh liy eblaoyj’t hwfxdf, ck, bm smf coio, fmkfhljudms goy
