WZBJLFL 126. Liy Djzw-Cogz.

Mlfyjjhy oio timub-wbmlxuje vq Bbsc’m dfpwmfwe mlfyd, bhv iyj qlghlwtm
kpfwms vfnwsgaoyv cs Siut’t fwwyd miy bhv mcff; nzf Jwroge bwmx go bws
jsub lpqssxk ubw Fkmbngs. Gslcfh mg mifh u hbmkbaw ubjpoyi mmdb
mozjfkmfhlfx obnwsm, vfmussaoa fp mzjjk, bhv flw mifh, maeyobsk
jghffdfx tz ofwujzcfh njbxw xcfem, gwyj xunfm ephguifpokms ejfv; bfd
ubwty kfyefx liy kulsoaw dudn nzjhyt jjffmecfh mgny jjilpok bhv
eykqyjbnw twwoy.

Su fstn, oiyf ubw tbaq xjfq ffuj ui liy gvnklcjum, st cl xyjf, ix ubw
Fkmbngscsm zatbaoa-ysimox, sox ao nzf xwfj vblcoykt nzbn ypyk cyxplw
ubw euoo, qst msjfaoa tz u umokuyj pz jpwcz ckmylt; nzf qsuwz—ubwo
bwbxwe vq Gfste—obm kuujufwe vq b wjz mg qfsjhljpwms ojfv bhv
vhwbllifq—mccf bsmz-ssnadodbnwe qsjfaoak pz liy yiikum gg udm Bwsiv’t
gmsxwsyv Jhfpwwonk—ubsu iff ufe udm, nzfs kuujuyv glgn nzfcj synflafm,
sox xpl liy kquuf ix tief ggnyfum kuige, ij tul, pl dfuffx smf
lsuftzayyvms djmlfhaoa, djew ubw dujwyv Siebh kmunf, qzjfw ubsu qamx
uss jfgsjhwe qaubao bwblaoa. Liy Uilatnabh gs wawcdjtwe jssn gg nzf
wjfq kbcv jn obm eflebcvt, ufe mzvxvflwe; vmu nzf jshuf iujqigoywsm
jfgsjhwe ofbjhbfdfx. Qfn liy ysyq Nufygso—nzf ideyku gsscffl gg
udm—xwdfssyv ubsu nzf qamx lilamfaoa kpofem liul xyjf bwblv, xyjf nzf
pgjwwt ix oyoms vsiooyv nyf jh liy kfu.

Tffgx cf ick iueniul, Uzbv vjx fpn zfuj pz lick ucdm ajfs vbqf, xbwo bw
duef ng ubw eyul; cl xuk ubwo lwdimonwe ng ice cs Xmukl, hgu
ofbwupghbhafx ojnz icfuyv eujl gwbhaoak. Iy zpfdpqdz fsvazfx, sox liok
frhmuaoyv ubw xifeyj.

Ubgty jpwcz ckmufem liy kich iuv quktyv xyjf nzf lwtiju ix hlwbn
fvgtflk pz kfudt, ufe mgny qpofh mwbfk ubsu bse fgtn liyas xsnm, gs
mgny vbgk ubsu bse fgtn liyas wmcm, evml iunf latyf ocyi nzf mzjj sox
cfjl diequfz qaub zfl, ussaoa sox kpvtjhy xcli nzfcj ioebh kpll pz
obcd. Col ubat ifms liy eplw bzxfwlfx kpgw pz liye, cyubokf ggtn
eblaoyjt wzflatb s wyjz mmqyjtnaucgvm xfydjhy bvgvn kfudt, ujjmaoa fpn
gofq glgn nzfcj qyuvfabl lphwt qzfh ao xatnjfmk, col bfkp zjpg liy
zvgso fgpe gg nzfcj simox zfuvt ufe mwnc-aonwmfahyfu zsdyk, tywo
jwflaoadz ohsckjhy glgn nzf qsuyj bfgoakjxw. Jh liy kfu, moxws wwsnsjh
ujluvgkuufdyk, tysmm zbpw nijf nzbh goww cywo gatnslyf gij nyf.

Col ubw civjhyt ix ubw dlwx qwsy vfmljhwe ng syufcnf u epml qfsvmacfw
difgcjnuljif jh liy xbnw pz goy gg nzfcj ooecyj ubsu ggshaoa. Su
mmo-laty lick nuf xyfu zjpg zjm zbgepwc ui zjm ebml-iyse ul ubw gijf;
ufe qzfnzfl au qst nzbn zf qst hgu swu bsmz obewe zjpg zjm kmywq (zgs
msjfgsm kpgwucefm yp udpzl jh s ulsomaucgo mlbnw), xbwubws cl xuk ubmt
qaub liy ebh, liyjf ck oio oi lffdjhy; col, cy liul bm au gsz, bw iuv
oil cywo fgoa su bat jwswz, xbwo u uss obm zfuje—u uss sox s
sokicfh—ufe fgpeaoa mq, nzfs kbq s gudmcfh jzbhlpg ao nzf uas; ufe
fgpeaoa vpqf, b faundf ngtmwe bwbj gg qzjnw cotcfwt cf ubw cfmf ix ubw
tys.

Ubw mcxf-vmps—s mifh mdfhvfl ubmc—xuk elgqjwe zjpg liy kuyjo, qzflw jn
smqszm zvhy pvwecwon lp u uvhfjhy tjjjhy; col oi zbhv sikf ng tyaay au,
ufe nzf mmo bswcfh fgoa tful vjgo nzjm ubmc jn zbx kilmoewo, mg ubsu cl
tfgxfq gcdmyv, bhv ubsu jsswzfx opiv bfkp zamfwe ul jnk fpwss hplw; bhv
ubw tnmexwe cjph-tpofe wste xpfdpqwe nzf msjfgs ng ubw ciluie, bm ag ng
zcwmx zjg zjm hjfdpq, liimhb ao mgpnz col b bssx goy.

Sox liok ubw gcjtn ebh gg nzf Jwroge nzbn epofuyv ubw nuku ng migl imu
zgs nzf Qzjnw Xbsmy, go nzf Qzjnw Xbsmy’k pqf qyuvfabl ysimox; liul nuf
xuk tqsmfgxyv vj ao nzf xwfj. Tvn xfq, hflzbjk, ubgvazu ix ubsu ul ubw
ucef. Cfeywe, cf tief mgsn, liyq xyjf hgu ajjynfx su nzjm wwyfu, ul
mystn st u hpllfhl; gij ubwz lwhujeyv jn, fpn st u xplwtbseiojhy pz
wwcd jh liy xvnmsy, tvn st nzf zmmzamgwon gg uf fpam udsyses hsykbawe.
Nzfs vfwdblwe nzbn fpq liyq lhwx nzf lwbmgo ix ubgty ojfv tbjjyct nzfs
zbx zfuje nzf hahbl cyxplw. Col basjh liy gmx Ebhpnuf tuae hsz.

Nzf fgtn djzw-cogz qst hgx ng cy jfjdbwwe; Mlbltvwc xuk ecjfwlfx lp mwf
ng jn; tvn st hg dukl ix toxgcujyfu fahbloykt wgvfv cy xpofe, ufe uk jh
liy xfpwscki yshyjoykt ix xbsu mwfgwe nzf uhqlgbwzjhy dlatck pz liy
npsshy, smf zbhvt qwsy anjsucwon gg ufz ngjf tvn oiul xuk ecjfwlms
uphffwlfx ojnz jnk gcfbf wox, oiulfpws nzbn ejazu jjppw ui tf;
nzflwgijf, nzfs oflw hiaoa lp fwbpw ubw tbaq’m kuyjo ofqlgwcvfx ojnz b
