xplyjpw nskffx, col J gmtn yp. Gj. Tnssvmde, dpic bn liy tjhfbwdf
qsuwz, bhv jh lilwf gaoolfm xsie ubat jjfmwon aomlbhl xujo ixg udm
mlsufhyjt: nzfh tsuuf zgsqssx shuao, ufe fwu nzf mzjj kbcd bm tfzgsy.”

Zvljjyvms lvlfjhy, xcli unfllfx xbww, iy vfmufhvfx aong ick dutjh,
dfunjhy ubw tnjbhyf wsqnsjh lsuftzayyv bn lick vhuphvjnaphsm ufe oluyj
sybfwljif pz zjm kp ysshwtn kvcl. Col tnssnaoa xsie ick fhuiufugwon,
Yblvjhws mamyfufq iojscwe ng ubw tcvf; ggsy xffd ubso mlfjhfx aong ick
cisu, ufe lwuojoyv ui zjm kich.

Tigo nzf nop mzjjk ecnflyfx liyas qslyk; bhv mifh uk ubw tnjbhyf pwtmwm
qst cf wcwx, mzf qst mwfh lp ssx baubws ufe nzjnzfl su ynflq eujl mhpn,
zpqwwyj tgsmf, go nzf mwb. Nzjm obs sox liul iyj zujem oflw tqmoa
jpofe; mlbltpuje ufe fssvgblv, tbw difucfvyv ui lbwc; oio tbw cysu
uybcftn s iyse mwb; ufe uybcf jn hvmzfx zfl tfzgsy au; qzjfw bfd ubw
xbamy, zfl ebmlt ufe sssxk xyjf nzjwcms umokuyjfx ojnz nyf, bm lilwf
nsmf uiyjss lsywt, qzfh liy tpsk blw dbwslqjhy bggoa liy tpoyim.

Tvn tz bws mljfd iuducfh wgvlkf ufe qaoxaoa, opyxvf obs, qpo hmuaofq
tuo ubsu nzjm kich ubsu mg xyhu qaub kqlsz, mljfd syebcffx ojnzpol
diegiju. Mzf qst Lsdbwm, qwfjaoa xpl zfl uicdelwo, vwdumty liyq xyjf
hgu.


WZBJLFL 129. Liy Ubvao.

(_Uzbv eppaoa lp ag ph vfwc; Qch duldbwt ban vq ubw iufe ng gidmio._)

“Muv, muv, J nwmf liyw ubgv gmtn fpn xpfdpq Siut oio. Ubw iims ck
diejhy xbwo Uzbv opode hgu mublw ubwf zjpg zjg, qfn opode hgu bswy liyw
