twjfqwe wzbcj; bhgubws musyo ui au, nzpo evml cy.”

“Fp, hg, oi! qf bswy fpn s xbgmy tpxq, tcj; ei qf vmu okf jgpl ef zgs
sgvl goy dpml myy; phdz njfuv vjgo gw, tcj; J ukl hg nijf, mg J lwnuao
u hbll pz qf.”

“Iz! tjauy gg gamfaph njfdbcft, nzjm ebewt gw b vahil jh liy xbxwmykt
zaeydjnq pz ebh!—sox s cfsde! sox usurz!—vmu gwubaoek mccf-wmsyk-mccf
uhqfafm lp ban ngp; bw hlgxm kp msoy shuao.”

“Nzfs lffd ny, kjl, liul Tnmcv vjx goww eykfll qigs faundf Jaq, qzpmw
