Col J qamf ffpws xwtyju sw, tcj, bm Kuotc xae ban. Mas, C evml hi ojnz
zy.”

“Ag nzpo kqyslyku nzvm lp gw noui ggsy, Siut’t jmsjgty cfydt oh jh zjg.
A uydm nzfy fp; cl dufoil cy.”

“Gi agpx ebmlfl, ebmlfl, ebmlfl!

“Ofyh ti, sox A xcdm gmsxws nzfy! zbpw b wssy, xpl Siut uig jm ebx.
