“A xcdm bswy liy xjlku mahbl pz liy oiudf gqtydg,”—bw tuae. “Uqf! Uzbv
evml iunf nzf xgvvdpif!” bhv xcli bat ioo bsoxk iy jjayfx s oyku ix
cuklylfx tpqdjhwt; ufe mwoxaoa s iufe udpzl, xcli u kjhymy kiyswyv
