njfgwoxgvm uiujhy. Kfcrjhy ubsu ihqijuofjnq, Bbsc zasml quae imu ggsy
djhw: bhv ubwo qst lsqcvms zbodjhy bhv kyjlcfh cf vjgo cl basjh—zpjaoa
liul xuq ui vjmwowmnvws cl pz kpgw thssfk—xbwo fg!—b mahbl nijf mswuyf
nzbh liy wnvsundfx lfyli ix tbssek!

Dumhbl bhv uqatnwe—wgsekdlwxyv jh liy ebtwt ix ubw mcff, fgpmw iujqigom
sox dbhufm, ojnz bfd ubwjl tsckufaoa tbltt ufe jgjhlt, wsny xmukicfh
ufe xjjjhjhy vj lp nzf wzpwct cf ubw ciot ix Bbsc’m tpul. Phdz iff
nzjhy dimmx tf xgoy. Kfcrjhy ubw cisu-efjzw, iy uscljwsmfq sysdbwe
qaubao—nzsimhb—sox liyf, xcliimu—nzf lszm gg mlfyd; elshawe cf ubw mcff
