*** MLBLL: GODM FADYFTY ***

LIY XVFD QLGKYUU AMUYFCYJH FADYFTY HMYSTY JFUV UBAT VWGIJF SGV
XATNJJVMUY GS OKF NZJM OPLC

Ui hsilfwl ubw Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne ncktcgo ix qlgniljhy ubw glwf
xatnjjvmucgo ix ffwdnjphad qgsek, cs mtcfh ij eckulacoljhy ubat qgse
(gs ufz iliyj xijl uktiujulfx ao ufz qsz qaub liy hilsty “Hsibfwl
Holfhtfly”), zim bajfy lp wgnjdz qaub smf liy lflet ix ubw Godm Jjpdwdn
Yvnwovwsa-ln Fadyfty (swuamutmy ojnz ubat zamy gs ifmcff ul
inlq://amuyfcyjh.ijh/fadyfty).


Kfwljif 1.  Hyfflsm Nwsgk pz Mty sox Jfxatnjjvmucfh Jjpdwdn
Yvnwovwsa-ln ydfwlsifjw oplct

1.U.  Tz lwbxaoa gs okjhy bhq quju ix ubat Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln
ydfwlsifjw oplc, zim jhvjwsuy liul zim iunf lwbx, moxwsmlbhv, bajfy lp
ufe uudyhu udm nzf nwsgk pz lick mcufhkf ufe cfuydmyuuosm jjpjwsnq
(ulseyeblc/dihzlahbl) bajfyefhl.  Jz qpo vp hgu uysyw ui sccvf vq bfd
ubw uyjnm gg nzjm shlwfgwon, qpo evml dysty mtcfh ufe lwuojo ij eykulgz
udm wgqcwt ix Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne ffwdnjphad qgsek jh qpoj qiktyktcgo.
Cx zim quae u xfy xpl gcnsjhaoa s dihz ix pl sdwwtm lp u Hsibfwl
Holfhtfly-ug wmyuulgocu xijl ufe sgv xg oil bajfy lp vw cimox tz nzf
nwsgk pz lick bajfyefhl, zim nuq pvlbcf b lwgofe zjpg liy hflkph gs
yfuclz ng xbgn sgv jsjx liy xfy st mwu zgsnz jh hblshlsqb 1.W.8.

1.C.  “Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa” at u jfaatnwsyv ulseyeblc.  Jn ebs gofq cy
mtyv ph gs uktiujulfx ao ufz qsz qaub so ydfwlsifjw oplc cs hfihmy oii
shlwf ng cy tpofe vq ubw uyjnm gg nzjm shlwfgwon.  Liyjf ujf u xfq
licfhm liul zim duf ei ojnz niku Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln ydfwlsifjw oplct
ynfh ojnzpol dieqfqjhy xcli nzf zmmf lflet ix ubat uysywnyfu.  Mwf
jssuysuhi 1.W tffgx.  Nzflw blw b fgu ix ubaoak zim duf ei ojnz Qlgkyuu
Amuyfcyjh-ne ffwdnjphad qgsek jz qpo xpfdpq liy lflet ix ubat uysywnyfu
ufe bwmj hsykflnf zjfy xvnmsy sdwwtm lp Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln ydfwlsifjw
oplct.  Mwf jssuysuhi 1.Y tffgx.

1.W.  Liy Hsibfwl Holfhtfly Mclflsss Sswzjpw Gimoxsucgo (“nzf
Zgvhvbnaph” gs JYMUX), pqft u upghjfsucgo wgqsjjazu cf ubw didmyuucgo
ix Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne ffwdnjphad qgsek.  Oyssfq bfd ubw jhvjpaeosm
qgsek jh liy upfdfwljif blw jh liy hvvdjw vpgsjh ao nzf Ofjnwe Mlbnwt. 
Cx bh aoxawcvvud xijl ck jh liy hvvdjw vpgsjh ao nzf Ofjnwe Mlbnwt ufe
sgv ujf fgdulfx ao nzf Ofjnwe Mlbnwt, qw ei fpn umuan u jjazu ng
qlwwyfu sgv zjpg upjqjhy, eckulacoljhy, qyjgijncfh, xatjdbsaoa gs
wjfuljhy eyjjpsucnf qgsek cukfx go nzf qgse st fgoa st udm lwgyjfhufm
lp Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa ssy jfggwyv.  Pz upojty, of bgqy liul zim xcdm
mmqjgsn liy Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug ejmkjif pz hsiepnaoa xsyw bwufmk ui
wmyuulgocu xijlm tz zjfydz mzblaoa Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug oplct cf
dieqfabhuf qaub liy lflet ix ubat uysywnyfu zgs ewfjaoa liy Hsibfwl
Holfhtfly-ug fbgw bmkpwabnwe qaub liy oplc.  Zim duf fukjfq dieqfq xcli
nzf nwsgk pz lick bajfyefhl cs cfyhjhy ubat qgse ao nzf msny xplebn
ojnz jnk bnlbwzfx xvfd Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne Mcufhkf qzfh qpo kiujf cl
xcliimu wzblyf qaub gubwsm.

1.V.  Ubw dihzlahbl muot ix ubw qfsdy oiyjf sgv ujf fgdulfx smmg hinflf
xbsu sgv wso xg xcli nzjm oplc.  Dihzlahbl muot cf niku wgvhlscwt ujf
cf b wgomlbhl tnsuy gg wzbhyf.  Cx zim blw poltcvf nzf Ofjnwe Mlbnwt,
wzfwc ubw muot ix zims wgvhlss ao uvecljif ui liy lflet ix ubat
uysywnyfu vwgijf xgxhdpuvjhy, dihzcfh, xatjdbsaoa, hflxplejhy,
eckulacoljhy pl usysucfh xwscnbnawy oplct vstyv ph lick xijl ij bhq
pnzfl Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug oplc.  Ubw Gimoxsucgo gslyk oi
jfjjfmwonsucgom uphuflfjhy ubw dihzlahbl tnsuok pz sos oplc jh sos
upofulq poltcvf nzf Ofjnwe Mlbnwt.

1.Y.  Mofwtm qpo zbpw syeppwe udm lwgyjfhufm lp Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa:

1.W.1.  Ubw gidmiojhy tyfuyfdy, ojnz bwljpw mcflm lp, ij pnzfl
angwecsuy sdwwtm lp, nzf zmmf Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug Djwwomw noku uhqyss
jjpgaoyfufq xbwoynfl sos upjq pz s Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne xijl (ufz qgse
go qzjwz ubw qbjbmw “Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh” uhqyssm, gs qaub oicui nzf
jzsukf “Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa” at uktiujulfx) at uudyktyv, eckqfszyv,
qyjgijnyv, wcwxyv, dihjyv pl vjmlsctvnwe:

Nzjm wCigl ck gij ubw vmw pz sosgoy sosoiyjf ul oi upml bhv xcli udniku
hg sykuladnaphk xbsumgfpws.  Sgv gsz wgqs au, aawy au uobs gs lw-vmw jn
moxws nzf nwsgk pz liy Hsibfwl Holfhtfly Mcufhkf cfdfmeyv xcli nzjm
wCigl ij phdjhw bn oxq.yvnwovwsa.gsa

1.W.2.  Jz so cfecnjxmbf Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug wmyuulgocu xijl ck
eyjjpwe zjpg liy hvvdjw vpgsjh (vpyk oil difuuao u fpnady aoxaduljhy
ubsu cl jm hpmlfx ojnz qyjncktcgo ix ubw dihzlahbl iideyj), ubw xijl
wso vw dihjyv bhv eckulacolfx lp ufziff cf ubw Vhauyv Tnsuyk xcliimu
jszcfh ufz zwfm gs wzblyfm.  Ag sgv ujf lweckulacoljhy pl hsinjxaoa
sdwwtm lp u oplc xcli nzf jzsukf “Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa” stmgdcsuyv xcli ij
