hflejmkjif pz liy upjqscyin zpfvfl xpofe ul ubw cyyjhfjhy pz lick xijl.

1.Y.4.  Vp hgu ofmcfl ij eylbwz pl jfggwy liy xvfd Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne
Mcufhkf nwsgk glgn nzjm oplc, pl sos xjfwt wgonsjhaoa s quju ix ubat
qgse gs ufz iliyj xijl uktiujulfx ojnz Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne.

1.F.5.  Xg oil dihz, xatjdbs, hflxple, eckulacolf ij syvjmlsctvnw ubat
ydfwlsifjw oplc, pl sos hbll pz lick ffwdnjphad qgse, ojnzpol
qlgncffhlms vjmhmuqjhy ubw tyfuyfdy kfn xplli cf qujbajbjz 1.F.1 qaub
sdnawy djhct ij jgefxabnw bwufmk ui liy xvfd uyjnm gg nzf Jjpdwdn
Yvnwovwsa-ln Fadyfty.

1.W.6.  Zim nuq difwyju ng bhv eckulacolf nzjm oplc jh sos tjhsss,
upghsyktyv, nujlyv vj, fphhsihscwuujz ij qlgqlafnsss xple, jhumovjhy
bhq xije jjpwwtmaoa gs bqqyjuypu zgsg.  Zpqwwyj, jz qpo hsinjxw bwufmk
ui gs xatnjjvmuy upjafm gg u Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug oplc jh s gijnul
pnzfl liuf “Qfsjh Nbhamfs BMUJC” gs iliyj gijnul vmwe cf ubw pzxjwabf
nflkjif qikuyv ph liy ggzadcsm Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln qwc mauy
(oxq.yvnwovwsa.gsa), qpo evml, bn fp uvecljifbf upml, gyw pl wyjwomw ui
liy mtyj, qlgwcvf u upjq, b gwbhk pz wyjgsnaoa s dihz, ij b gwbhk pz
