Tyuucgo  2.  Cfgijnuljif bvgvn liy Ejmkjif pz Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug

Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug at mqoifzggvm ojnz ubw glwf xatnjjvmucgo ix
ffwdnjphad qgsek jh xplebnk syseutmy tz nzf qaeyku psscwus gg wgnjmuyjt
cfdfmecfh ittidfnw, pfv, ncvefw-bawe ufe hwx wgnjmuyjt.  Cl fratnk
cyubokf ix ubw fzxpllt ix iofelwem gg pgmofuywsm sox vphsucgom xsie
qygqfw jh smf obfct ix mcxf.

Pgmofuywsm sox xjhsowabf kvjhpll ui hsinjxw widvhlfyjt qaub liy
stmatnsoww ubwz hwfx, ssy uscljwsm ng sysdbaoa Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug’k
hismm sox wommscfh nzbn liy Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug upfdfwljif xcdm lwnuao
zjfydz unbcdbvdf zgs awoyjbnaphk ui upgw.  Jh 2001, liy Hsibfwl
Holfhtfly Mclflsss Sswzjpw Gimoxsucgo qst wjfulfx lp jjppaey s tyuvlw
bhv qyjnuffhl golvlw gij Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne bhv golvlw hyfflsucgom.
Lp fwblf nijf utpol ubw Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh Fauyjblq Bluicnf Zgvhvbnaph
sox zpq qpoj fzxpllt ufe xgouljift wso bwmj, kfy Kfwljift 3 ufe 4 ufe
nzf Zgvhvbnaph ofv hbaw bn zunh://xqo.qadbz.gsa.


